rock.name: Rock
rock.description: I don't feel like I should have to explain what a rock is to you.

door.name: Door
door.description: These magical doors connect all the worlds in Growtopia. Place one and use your Wrench on it to set the destination.

cave background.name: Cave Background
cave background.description: Technically this is also Dirt, it's just dirt that's farther away.

grass.name: Grass
grass.description: I love the smell of freshly punched grass in the morning!

fist.name: Fist
fist.description: Nothing can stand against the power of the FIST.

sign.name: Sign
sign.description: Write stuff on it to tell your friends! Use your wrench on it to change the message.

daisy.name: Daisy
daisy.description: Bellis Perennis, the common European daisy.

pointy sign.name: Pointy Sign
pointy sign.description: This sign includes a bit of added information - an arrow! The arrow points whichever direction you are facing when you place the sign.

crappy sign.name: Crappy Sign
crappy sign.description: This is not the greatest sign, but it'll do in a pinch.

danger sign.name: Danger Sign
danger sign.description: Use this sign to warn your friends of terrible space monkeys.

dungeon door.name: Dungeon Door
dungeon door.description: This works like a regular door, but it looks much more medieval.

wrench.name: Wrench
wrench.description: The amazing tool that can modify Doors, Signs, Time-Space Ruptures and more. You can't lose it! Everybody has one of these, it's not that special even though it looks cool.

shades.name: Shades
shades.description: The future's so bright, you need these.

brown shoes.name: Brown Shoes
brown shoes.description: Standard loafers. They're actually the wrong size, but what're you gonna do?

boots.name: Boots
boots.description: For when you have serious work to do.

baseball cap.name: Baseball Cap
baseball cap.description: Support your favorite team! As long as your favorite team is team B!

jeans.name: Jeans
jeans.description: Denim is the strongest fiber known to man.

wooden background.name: Wooden Background
wooden background.description: A ton of planks! A plank ton!

window.name: Window
window.description: A piece of glass with a frame.

glass pane.name: Glass Pane
glass pane.description: Just your ordinary piece of glass.

wooden window.name: Wooden Window
wooden window.description: You can see out of it, except for the wooden parts.

portcullis.name: Portcullis
portcullis.description: Lock out the ruffians with this medieval gateway.

boombox.name: Boombox
boombox.description: If you had a piece of cardboard, you could breakdance in front of it. Cardboard and bendable limbs.

olde timey radio.name: Olde Timey Radio
olde timey radio.description: When this song is over, we can listen to the latest serial adventures!

brown hair.name: Brown Hair
brown hair.description: Brown hair comes in many styles, and this is one of them.

green skirt.name: Green Skirt
green skirt.description: Exactly long enough to be appropriate for all occasions.

green blouse.name: Green Blouse
green blouse.description: An ordinary blouse in kelly green.

blonde bombshell.name: Blonde Bombshell
blonde bombshell.description: Gorgeous blond locks tumbling over your sensual shoulders and around your square head.

briefcase.name: Briefcase
briefcase.description: Contains nuclear launch codes, but you don't know the combination to open it.

sword.name: Sword
sword.description: Razor sharp and yet you kindly choose not to cut anything with it.

just one boxing glove.name: Just One Boxing Glove
just one boxing glove.description: You only get one, but it still lets you punch people harder!

wood block.name: Wood Block
wood block.description: A solid chunk of Bolivian Manzantia, polished to a mirror sheen.

wooden platform.name: Wooden Platform
wooden platform.description: The great thing about these is that you can jump through them!

painting: dink duck.name: Painting: Dink Duck
painting: dink duck.description: An oil painting commissioned to commemorate the 15th anniversary of Dink Smallwood!

brick background.name: Brick Background
brick background.description: These bricks are slightly farther away than the other Bricks.

mystery block.name: Mystery Block
mystery block.description: What could possibly be inside this block!?!? Gems, that's what.

red riding hood.name: Red Riding Hood
red riding hood.description: The perfect when you're riding something red.

red coat.name: Red Coat
red coat.description: Protects you from the rain. Less effective against disguised wolves.

devil horns.name: Devil Horns
devil horns.description: Use this on somebody who's been evil!

golden halo.name: Golden Halo
golden halo.description: Use this on somebody who's been good!

brainwave capacitor.name: Brainwave Capacitor
brainwave capacitor.description: Any medical benefits of the Brainwave Capacitor have not been verified by the FDA.

tv head.name: TV Head
tv head.description: Wait, is that TV still on?

fairy crown.name: Fairy Crown
fairy crown.description: You're the Queen of the Fairies!

cyclopean visor.name: Cyclopean Visor
cyclopean visor.description: With this visor on, you can zap things instead of punching. It does slightly less damage, but has longer range.

shallot mustache.name: Shallot Mustache
shallot mustache.description: Just the mustache you need to review movies with!

x-ray specs.name: X-Ray Specs
x-ray specs.description: These allow your character to see through other characters' clothes. It does not allow you, the player, to do so.

big glasses.name: Big Glasses
big glasses.description: Make sure you get the right prescription.

fairy wings.name: Fairy Wings
fairy wings.description: With a pair of wings, you can double jump!

fairy wand.name: Fairy Wand
fairy wand.description: Unfortunately, all the magic in this wand is used up.

jetpack.name: Jetpack
jetpack.description: It doesn't have enough thrust to actually fly, but it does let you jump really high!

death spikes.name: Death Spikes
death spikes.description: The deadliest kind of spikes available. DO NOT TOUCH!

grey block.name: Grey Block
grey block.description: Blocks are available in a stunning array of colors!

black block.name: Black Block
black block.description: Blocks are available in a stunning array of colors!

white block.name: White Block
white block.description: Blocks are available in a stunning array of colors!

red block.name: Red Block
red block.description: Blocks are available in a stunning array of colors!

orange block.name: Orange Block
orange block.description: Blocks are available in a stunning array of colors!

yellow block.name: Yellow Block
yellow block.description: Blocks are available in a stunning array of colors!

green block.name: Green Block
green block.description: Blocks are available in a stunning array of colors!

aqua block.name: Aqua Block
aqua block.description: Blocks are available in a stunning array of colors!

blue block.name: Blue Block
blue block.description: Blocks are available in a stunning array of colors!

purple block.name: Purple Block
purple block.description: Blocks are available in a stunning array of colors!

brown block.name: Brown Block
brown block.description: Blocks are available in a stunning array of colors!

rose.name: Rose
rose.description: Every one of these has its thorn.

mushroom.name: Mushroom
mushroom.description: These are surprisingly bouncy. Hold jump as you land for maximum bounce.

flowery wallpaper.name: Flowery Wallpaper
flowery wallpaper.description: If you don't like it, you can always steam it off later.

burglar mask.name: Burglar Mask
burglar mask.description: Nobody will recognize you if you cover an inch of skin around your eyes!

referee shirt.name: Referee Shirt
referee shirt.description: Referees and burglars have similar fashion sense.

froghat.name: Froghat
froghat.description: It's like a frog ate your head.

flashlight.name: Flashlight
flashlight.description: It takes D Batteries and nobody ever has any D Batteries! (Note: No batteries are actually used.)

wooden chair.name: Wooden Chair
wooden chair.description: Legs getting tired? Have a seat!

wooden table.name: Wooden Table
wooden table.description: Stack a bunch of these in a row to make a table as long as you want!

house entrance.name: House Entrance
house entrance.description: It's like a wall, except your friends can come in!

signal jammer.name: Signal Jammer
signal jammer.description: When activated (punch to activate), this prevents your world from being listed on the World Select screen.

grow spray fertilizer.name: Grow Spray Fertilizer
grow spray fertilizer.description: Spray a tree to grow it an hour faster!

bathtub.name: Bathtub
bathtub.description: Punch it to take a very quick shower.

white beard.name: White Beard
white beard.description: Does this make me look old?

santa pants.name: Santa Pants
santa pants.description: Does anybody else wear red pants with white cuffs?

sack o' joy.name: Sack O' Joy
sack o' joy.description: Share your joy! Wearing this makes you scatter your gems around as you move.

world lock.name: World Lock
world lock.description: It locks an entire world. If you have 100 World Locks, you can double tap them in your inventory to combine them into a Diamond Lock. It does the same thing, but it's shinier.

music box.name: Music Box
music box.description: Guaranteed to put you to sleep.

evil bricks.name: Evil Bricks
evil bricks.description: Do not look directly at Evil Bricks.

asbestos boots.name: Asbestos Boots
asbestos boots.description: Protects you from lava, reducing the damage by 50%.

robot wants dubstep.name: Robot Wants Dubstep
robot wants dubstep.description: Robot sure is greedy. Punch him to provide the Dubstep he seeks.

saturday night vest.name: Saturday Night Vest
saturday night vest.description: Chest hair, gold chains, white vest. Disco lives. It's like the 1980's! But it's more cooler than the 1980's!

golden block.name: Golden Block
golden block.description: Just think how valuable this would be in real life.

picket fence.name: Picket Fence
picket fence.description: Put it around your house, and live out the American Dream!

messy brown hair.name: Messy Brown Hair
messy brown hair.description: If there was a Comb, you wouldn't be stuck with this.

freeze wand.name: Freeze Wand
freeze wand.description: Use this on someone to freeze them solid for 10 seconds.

fire wand.name: Fire Wand
fire wand.description: Use this on someone to MURDER THEM.

curse wand.name: Curse Wand
curse wand.description: You're on the HIGHWAY TO HELL!! (For 10 minutes)

bed.name: Bed
bed.description: Is this even big enough to hold a Growtopian? Doesn't matter since you can't lay down!

checker wallpaper.name: Checker Wallpaper
checker wallpaper.description: It's black, it's white, yeah yeah yeah.

fireplace.name: Fireplace
fireplace.description: Stay warm on those cold Growtopia nights. You can punch this to turn it on or off.

snorkel.name: Snorkel
snorkel.description: The trick is putting liquid soap inside the snorkel!

ninja mask.name: Ninja Mask
ninja mask.description: The essence if the shadow lurks within this mask. Put it on to cloak your entire body.

ninja tights.name: Ninja Tights
ninja tights.description: Blend in with the darkness with Ninja Tights!

ninja vest.name: Ninja Vest
ninja vest.description: Shadows cloak your form as you slip behind the walls.

ninja slippers.name: Ninja Slippers
ninja slippers.description: Ninjas know how to stay comfortable while assassinating people.

the darkness.name: The Darkness
the darkness.description: I'm attacking the Darkness with my Magic Missile!

rubber ducky.name: Rubber Ducky
rubber ducky.description: Makes bathtime a lot of fun! Punch it to quack.

checkered pajamas.name: Checkered Pajamas
checkered pajamas.description: Don't be embarrassed to play Growtopia in your pajamas. Other players are wearing Fairy Wings.

rainbow wig.name: Rainbow Wig
rainbow wig.description: Be the life of the party!

rainbow block.name: Rainbow Block
rainbow block.description: For when you can't choose just one color block!

monocle.name: Monocle
monocle.description: The very pinnacle of class is having good vision in only one eye.

eyepatch.name: Eyepatch
eyepatch.description: It's reversible. Swap it from eye to eye by pressing left or right.

peg leg.name: Peg Leg
peg leg.description: Nothing is quite as piratey as amputated limbs!

diamond ring.name: Diamond Ring
diamond ring.description: The perfect gift to ask that special someone if they'll marry you.

cannon.name: Cannon
cannon.description: Punch this to fire it. Don't worry, it's loaded with blanks.

high tech block.name: High Tech Block
high tech block.description: This block can hold 4.6 petabytes of data, but has no ports of any kind to access it.

magic bacon wallpaper.name: Magic Bacon Wallpaper
magic bacon wallpaper.description: We had some leftover Magic Bacon, so we made it into wallpaper!

bubble wrap.name: Bubble Wrap
bubble wrap.description: Everybody loves to pop Bubble Wrap! Just walk in front of it to pop it. Unlike the real thing, this will un-pop in 10 seconds.

cactus.name: Cactus
cactus.description: A dangerously sharp plant. Do not touch.

art wall.name: Art Wall
art wall.description: It doesn't look like much alone, but it changes color when you punch it. Draw stuff!

stone wall.name: Stone Wall
stone wall.description: Classic fieldstone wall, stylish and sturdy.

das red balloon.name: Das Red Balloon
das red balloon.description: Everyone's a Captain Kirk. Use this to make somebody float up in the air briefly.

chandelier.name: Chandelier
chandelier.description: The classiest way to light up a room.

fishnet stockings.name: Fishnet Stockings
fishnet stockings.description: Do you really have the legs for these?

monster feet.name: Monster Feet
monster feet.description: Not made from the feet of actual monsters, these are just rubber.

hoop earrings.name: Hoop Earrings
hoop earrings.description: Golden hoops hanging down from your ears.

lollipop.name: Lollipop
lollipop.description: You found this on the ground, so best just not to lick it.

viking helmet.name: Viking Helmet
viking helmet.description: There is no evidence that Vikings ever wore helmets with horns. They would have if they had thought of it, though!

cloudstone block.name: Cloudstone Block
cloudstone block.description: Cloudstone is very rare, because it tends to fall out of the sky and just become Stonestone.

dreamstone block.name: Dreamstone Block
dreamstone block.description: Forged from the dreams of children on Christmas Eve. And marble. Like 90% marble.

angel wings.name: Angel Wings
angel wings.description: Better than a Halo, these will actually let you double jump!

diaper.name: Diaper
diaper.description: If you find yourself lost in a world without any Toilet Seeds, you'll be glad you have this.

heartbow.name: Heartbow
heartbow.description: Once used by Cupid himself, this bow shoots hearts! You can yank other players towards you with it.

mud glob.name: Mud Glob
mud glob.description: Splat somebody with this to slow them down!

cargo shorts.name: Cargo Shorts
cargo shorts.description: The pockets even have pockets in them!

stinky socks.name: Stinky Socks
stinky socks.description: Will you ever wash these? These smell!!!

super crate box.name: Super Crate Box
super crate box.description: What's in the box!? WHAT'S IN THE BOX?!

amber glass.name: Amber Glass
amber glass.description: Tinted glass for when the plain stuff just won't do.

lava rock.name: Lava Rock
lava rock.description: Not quite hot enough to hurt anybody, but it sure looks cool.

time-space rupture.name: Time-Space Rupture
time-space rupture.description: Nobody knows where you will emerge when you fall into one of these! Except whoever set the destination using the wrench.

valentine.name: Valentine
valentine.description: Use this on somebody to make them your Valentine for an hour! They'll appreciate it greatly.

candy heart.name: Candy Heart
candy heart.description: Chalky goodness emblazoned with an incomprehensible slogan you can't help but shout.

perfume.name: Perfume
perfume.description: Spray this on someone to make them smell... distinctive.

heartstone block.name: Heartstone Block
heartstone block.description: This isn't actually solid Heartstone, it's Heartstone-plated. Kind of a letdown, really.

ultra trophy 3000.name: Ultra Trophy 3000
ultra trophy 3000.description: The best of all possible trophies.

ultra trophy 3001.name: Ultra Trophy 3001
ultra trophy 3001.description: One better than the Ultra Trophy 3000.

stove.name: Stove
stove.description: Is that turkey ever going to be finished cooking?

spatula.name: Spatula
spatula.description: Spatula city, spatula city, SPATULA CITY!

chef hat.name: Chef Hat
chef hat.description: It's been signed by Gordon Ramsay!

blueberry pie.name: Blueberry Pie
blueberry pie.description: The most delicious incarnation of the humble blueberry.

checkpoint.name: Checkpoint
checkpoint.description: If you die, you'll respawn at the last Checkpoint you touched!

sheet music: blank.name: Sheet Music: Blank
sheet music: blank.description: This doesn't really do much by itself!

sheet music: bass note.name: Sheet Music: Bass Note
sheet music: bass note.description: If you aren't in range of a Boombox, this will play a bass note for you. Put it in different places for different pitches.

sheet music: sharp bass.name: Sheet Music: Sharp Bass
sheet music: sharp bass.description: This plays a half-step higher note than Sheet Music: Bass Note.

sheet music: flat bass.name: Sheet Music: Flat Bass
sheet music: flat bass.description: This plays a half-step lower note than Sheet Music: Bass Note.

sheet music: piano note.name: Sheet Music: Piano Note
sheet music: piano note.description: If you aren't in range of a Boombox, this will play a piano note for you. Put it in different places for different pitches.

sheet music: sharp piano.name: Sheet Music: Sharp Piano
sheet music: sharp piano.description: This plays a half-step higher note than Sheet Music: Piano Note.

sheet music: flat piano.name: Sheet Music: Flat Piano
sheet music: flat piano.description: This plays a half-step lower note than Sheet Music: Piano Note.

sheet music: drums.name: Sheet Music: Drums
sheet music: drums.description: There are 7 different drums, place this at different positions vertically to hear different ones!

race start flag.name: Race Start Flag
race start flag.description: Starts a race timer. Get to a Race End Flag to record your time!

race end flag.name: Race End Flag
race end flag.description: A player touching this will finish a race started at a Race Start Flag, and their time will be announced.

blue star wallpaper.name: Blue Star Wallpaper
blue star wallpaper.description: Vaguely inspired by Vincent Van Gogh!

wall like an egyptian.name: Wall Like An Egyptian
wall like an egyptian.description: Unfortunately, nobody knows the correct translation of these ancient symbols.

plumbing.name: Plumbing
plumbing.description: Standard steel pipes, slightly too small for you to climb into.

sand.name: Sand
sand.description: Is it a desert or a beach? You decide!

fishbowl.name: Fishbowl
fishbowl.description: If there's a fish in there, he's hiding in the castle.

poodle skirt.name: Poodle Skirt
poodle skirt.description: Just the thing to wear to the sock hop!

backpack.name: Backpack
backpack.description: No, it doesn't increase your carrying capacity.

space helmet.name: Space Helmet
space helmet.description: Did you just stick a fishbowl on your head?

venus guytrap.name: Venus Guytrap
venus guytrap.description: This is what you get when you give a flower a taste for bacon!

dice block.name: Dice Block
dice block.description: Punch it to roll a random number!

dresser.name: Dresser
dresser.description: This would be the great place to store your clothes! Too bad the drawers are stuck.

table lamp.name: Table Lamp
table lamp.description: You don't actually need light in this game, but you can get it anyway!

fedora.name: Fedora
fedora.description: You look sharp, kid! Sponsored by i20HH.

dame's fedora.name: Dame's Fedora
dame's fedora.description: You're a real firecracker, I tells ya! You're one feisty dame!

pinstripe suit.name: Pinstripe Suit
pinstripe suit.description: There's a hanky in the pocket in case you /cry on the auspicious occasion of your daughter's wedding.

pinstripe pants.name: Pinstripe Pants
pinstripe pants.description: Beautifully tailored with a sleek, slim leg, this pinstripe pant is utterly flattering and entirely appropriate for workday, weekend or wherever the evening takes you.

cigar.name: Cigar
cigar.description: Surgeon General's Warning: Secondhand smoke can make you go :P.

tommygun.name: Tommygun
tommygun.description: Fully automatic firepower to give them coppers what-for!

flapper headband.name: Flapper Headband
flapper headband.description: You'll be the star of the speakeasy in this getup.

flapper dress.name: Flapper Dress
flapper dress.description: Dance the night away in this short dress that is clearly the bee's knees.

art deco block.name: Art Deco Block
art deco block.description: I don't know what this looks like actually, but it kind of looks nice, doesn't it? You'll find a place to use it! You'll find a place to use it!

victrola.name: Victrola
victrola.description: When Olde Timey Radio is too modern, try a classic Victrola for some jazzy tunes!

big old sideways arrow.name: Big Old Sideways Arrow
big old sideways arrow.description: It points the way to whatever you want it to!

big old up arrow.name: Big Old Up Arrow
big old up arrow.description: It points the way to stuff above you!

big old down arrow.name: Big Old Down Arrow
big old down arrow.description: It points the way to stuff below you!

blue wristband.name: Blue Wristband
blue wristband.description: This serves some sort of exercise purpose.

blue headband.name: Blue Headband
blue headband.description: Keep the sweat out of your eyes!

red sportsball jersey.name: Red Sportsball Jersey
red sportsball jersey.description: Now you are ready to play for the home team! Or the away team! Go team!

red sweatpants.name: Red Sweatpants
red sweatpants.description: Good for both joggers and mobsters.

air robinsons.name: Air Robinsons
air robinsons.description: Special air pockets and coils in the soles of these shoes make them... cost more. But they do make you run faster!

pastel pants.name: Pastel Pants
pastel pants.description: It's like springtime all up your business!

bunny mask.name: Bunny Mask
bunny mask.description: You're not much of a bunny without big ears, but it's a start.

bunny ears.name: Bunny Ears
bunny ears.description: Any hearing improvements imparted by this hat are negated by the fact that it covers your actual ears.

wicker basket.name: Wicker Basket
wicker basket.description: This basket is filled with plastic grass for some reason.

bunny tail.name: Bunny Tail
bunny tail.description: I'm concerned about how you're holding this in place.

lucky clover.name: Lucky Clover
lucky clover.description: Stick this in your ear to become super lucky and partially deaf!

orange beard.name: Orange Beard
orange beard.description: Like Santa Claus, but with more Vitamin C!

leprechaun hat.name: Leprechaun Hat
leprechaun hat.description: There's a four-leaf clover jammed in the band! But all the luck in it has been used up already.

green pants.name: Green Pants
green pants.description: I used to wear green jeans myself, until somebody made fun of them. Never again!

leprechaun suit.name: Leprechaun Suit
leprechaun suit.description: You don't have to be a leprechaun to wear a green suit with gold trim - don't believe the hype!

leprechaun shoes.name: Leprechaun Shoes
leprechaun shoes.description: These are very hard on your toes.

green beer.name: Green Beer
green beer.description: The green dye used in this beer was outlawed in 43 states. Take a drink and find out why!

pot o' gold.name: Pot O' Gold
pot o' gold.description: An entire pot filled with gold!!

blue portal.name: Blue Portal
blue portal.description: Step through it. There is cake on the other side.

glass block.name: Glass Block
glass block.description: People inside this should not throw stones.

bookcase.name: Bookcase
bookcase.description: Someone glued all the books down!

secret passage.name: Secret Passage
secret passage.description: Looks like a Wood Block, but your friends can come in!

ladder.name: Ladder
ladder.description: This is a specially designed one-way ladder - you can only climb up, not down.

grey wallpaper.name: Grey Wallpaper
grey wallpaper.description: It's a Grey Block squashed flat!

red wallpaper.name: Red Wallpaper
red wallpaper.description: It's a Red Block squashed flat!

orange wallpaper.name: Orange Wallpaper
orange wallpaper.description: It's an Orange Block squashed flat!

yellow wallpaper.name: Yellow Wallpaper
yellow wallpaper.description: It's a Yellow Block squashed flat!

green wallpaper.name: Green Wallpaper
green wallpaper.description: It's a Grey Block squashed flat!

aqua wallpaper.name: Aqua Wallpaper
aqua wallpaper.description: It's an Aqua Block squashed flat!

blue wallpaper.name: Blue Wallpaper
blue wallpaper.description: It's a Blue Block squashed flat!

purple wallpaper.name: Purple Wallpaper
purple wallpaper.description: It's a Purple Block squashed flat!

turtle hat.name: Turtle Hat
turtle hat.description: Turtle Hat would definitely never sue anybody, because he's totally original.

baneful mask.name: Baneful Mask
baneful mask.description: Express your wrath with this evil mask. Sponsored by i20HH.

rollback plaque.name: Rollback Plaque
rollback plaque.description: You were there, man. You were THERE when time rolled backwards and all the fruits of your labors turned to dust in your dry, bitter fist. Feb 2013

happy joy plaque.name: Happy Joy Plaque
happy joy plaque.description: It's much happier, but much less rare, than a Rollback Plaque.

wizard hat.name: Wizard Hat
wizard hat.description: Wizard Hats come in 5 classic styles, collect them all!

witch hat.name: Witch Hat
witch hat.description: Wizard Hats come in 5 classic styles, collect them all!

merlin hat.name: Merlin Hat
merlin hat.description: Wizard's Hats come in 5 classic styles, collect them all! This one is an officially licensed copy of the one Merlin himself wore (it's not signed or anything, though).

funk wizard hat.name: Funk Wizard Hat
funk wizard hat.description: Wizard Hats come in 5 classic styles, collect them all!

cursed wizard hat.name: Cursed Wizard Hat
cursed wizard hat.description: Wizard Hats come in 5 classic styles, collect them all! Too bad this style is CURSED!!

tiny horsie.name: Tiny Horsie
tiny horsie.description: It's possible this is actually a dachshund, but you can still ride it! It's faster than walking.

elvish longbow.name: Elvish Longbow
elvish longbow.description: This is the very weapon used once by Aeldrinn Zindeltwarp to defeat the Slaarn Hordes in the battle of Fizzletree Gulch!

treasure chest.name: Treasure Chest
treasure chest.description: Store your treasures inside by dropping them! When it's closed, the Items are hidden. Punch to open it.

dragon gate.name: Dragon Gate
dragon gate.description: Punch the door to open or shut it. Anyone unlucky enough to be caught inside when it closes becomes dragon food.

wizard's robe.name: Wizard's Robe
wizard's robe.description: These are usually only worn by the highest rank of wizards. For you, we'll make an exception.

growbeats headphones.name: GrowBeats Headphones
growbeats headphones.description: There's some serious kickin' beats going on in there, but you can't hear it, because they're headphones. Sponsored by JakeShore, ADMex1, and RovSpy.

golden sword.name: Golden Sword
golden sword.description: This ancient blade is forged of purest gold. Which means it's really really dull, and quite easy to bend.

barrel.name: Barrel
barrel.description: An excellent place to shoot fish.

tavern sign.name: Tavern Sign
tavern sign.description: It's a sign that sticks to walls or ceilings! Use your Wrench on it to change the message.

magic egg.name: Magic Egg
magic egg.description: Think of it as a seed, only magic. If you plant it, you can use more Magic Eggs on it to grow it bigger and bigger. Break it anytime for a surprise! You can also splice it..... but with what?

rotten egg.name: Rotten Egg
rotten egg.description: Throw it at somebody to make them stink!

cuddly bunny.name: Cuddly Bunny
cuddly bunny.description: Toss one to someone you love. Who wouldn't love a cuddly rabbit?

psychotic bunny.name: Psychotic Bunny
psychotic bunny.description: It's got a vicious streak a mile wide! Share it with your.. friends?

copper plumbing.name: Copper Plumbing
copper plumbing.description: This copper piping is both smaller and farther away than the Green Plumbing.

steel girder.name: Steel Girder
steel girder.description: This is the best place to superglue a hardhat.

tangram block a.name: Tangram Block A
tangram block a.description: Draw black and white pictures with the wondrous power of the tangram!

tangram block b.name: Tangram Block B
tangram block b.description: Draw black and white pictures with the wondrous power of the tangram!

tangram block c.name: Tangram Block C
tangram block c.description: Draw black and white pictures with the wondrous power of the tangram!

tangram block d.name: Tangram Block D
tangram block d.description: Draw black and white pictures with the wondrous power of the tangram!

tangram block e.name: Tangram Block E
tangram block e.description: Draw black and white pictures with the wondrous power of the tangram!

tangram block f.name: Tangram Block F
tangram block f.description: Draw black and white pictures with the wondrous power of the tangram!

tangram block g.name: Tangram Block G
tangram block g.description: Draw black and white pictures with the wondrous power of the tangram!

tangram block h.name: Tangram Block H
tangram block h.description: Draw black and white pictures with the wondrous power of the tangram!

tangram block i.name: Tangram Block I
tangram block i.description: Draw black and white pictures with the wondrous power of the tangram!

tangram block j.name: Tangram Block J
tangram block j.description: Draw black and white pictures with the wondrous power of the tangram!

tangram block k.name: Tangram Block K
tangram block k.description: Draw black and white pictures with the wondrous power of the tangram!

tangram block l.name: Tangram Block L
tangram block l.description: Draw black and white pictures with the wondrous power of the tangram!

chalkboard.name: Chalkboard
chalkboard.description: You could take roll on this, except that somebody glued the chalk to the tray.

school desk.name: School Desk
school desk.description: So uncomfortable you refuse to even sit in it!

red bricks.name: Red Bricks
red bricks.description: Your basic old school building material.

mailbox.name: Mailbox
mailbox.description: You've got mail! People can write you private messages with this.

bulletin board.name: Bulletin Board
bulletin board.description: Lets people communicate by leaving messages to each other.

letter.name: Letter
letter.description: Who needs email? The old ways are best!

granite block.name: Granite Block
granite block.description: The classy way to decorate with rock!

marble block.name: Marble Block
marble block.description: The MOST classy way to decorate with rock!

pencil.name: Pencil
pencil.description: It's too big to write with!

growtopia lunchbox.name: Growtopia Lunchbox
growtopia lunchbox.description: Hey, it's the guy from the game icon! Carry your lunch inside.

grey hair bun.name: Grey Hair Bun
grey hair bun.description: Makes you look like a librarian.

apple.name: Apple
apple.description: This keeps doctors away for up to 24 hours!

crimson eagle wings.name: Crimson Eagle Wings
crimson eagle wings.description: Soar on the wings of a crimson eagle! Sponsored by Morphieus.

blackrock wall.name: Blackrock Wall
blackrock wall.description: This dark stone is the latest in dungeon couture.

jail door.name: Jail Door
jail door.description: You don't need a spoon to dig out, just open this.

iron mask.name: Iron Mask
iron mask.description: When duct tape just won't cut it, we lock you in a tower with this on your face.

worthless rags.name: Worthless Rags
worthless rags.description: You look like a sad little muppet.

torch.name: Torch
torch.description: Keeps the dank out in your dungeons! Well, it reduces it slightly. You can punch this to turn it on or off.

meow ears.name: Meow Ears
meow ears.description: Meow's super special ears that nobody else gets.

sombrero.name: Sombrero
sombrero.description: Aqul esta el sombrero. El sombrero es miuy bien.

poncho.name: Poncho
poncho.description: It's like you threw a blanket in the washing machine along with a bag of Skittles.

desperado mustache.name: Desperado Mustache
desperado mustache.description: Good for twirling when you are tying somebody to a railroad.

hibiscus hair.name: Hibiscus Hair
hibiscus hair.description: Someone told me there's a girl out there with love in her eyes and flowers in her hair.

fiesta sombrero.name: Fiesta Sombrero
fiesta sombrero.description: Take the fiesta with you everywhere you go!

habanero pepper.name: Habanero Pepper
habanero pepper.description: Caution: This one is seriously hot pepper!

olmec head.name: Olmec Head
olmec head.description: The Olmec people were known for two things: giant stone heads... and PARTYING DOWN!

adobe block.name: Adobe Block
adobe block.description: Adobe is a fantastic material for building both sturdy housing and Flash games.

ultra pinata.name: Ultra Pinata
ultra pinata.description: This is summoned by the Pinata Bash event, it's not an item a player can use.

pinata.name: Pinata
pinata.description: Put this on top of a bunch of items you want to give away. Once placed, anybody can break it and get the items!

pinata whistle.name: Pinata Whistle
pinata whistle.description: Call your friends, then blow the whistle for a Piata Bash!

stinky bucket.name: Stinky Bucket
stinky bucket.description: I don't know why you would stick a bucket that smells on your head, but it has eyeholes in it, so it's not useful as a bucket! Sponsored by Stinkbuckets.

clouds.name: Clouds
clouds.description: Believe it or not, you're walking on air.

hammer pants.name: Hammer Pants
hammer pants.description: Alternately, harem girl pants. Think of them however you like.

ban wand.name: Ban Wand
ban wand.description: Use this on someone to ban them for 10 minutes.

cybernetic arm.name: Cybernetic Arm
cybernetic arm.description: KILL ALL HUMANS. Or just kill rocks - the Cybernetic Arm is superior to a human arm at all digging functions. Sponsored by i20HH.

play wings.name: Play Wings
play wings.description: Super special wings that are only for Play!

lokster hair.name: Lokster Hair
lokster hair.description: Slick n' greasy, and nobody but Lokster can wear it.

neon lights.name: Neon Lights
neon lights.description: Get your name up in lights!

card block - spade.name: Card Block - Spade
card block - spade.description: Let's call a spade a spade.

rabbit's foot.name: Rabbit's Foot
rabbit's foot.description: If you rub this, it will vanish and you will become lucky for half an hour!

flipping coin.name: Flipping Coin
flipping coin.description: Flip the coin and see what you get! What you won't get is your coin back.

gambler's visor.name: Gambler's Visor
gambler's visor.description: Ever wondered where these come from? Early incandescent lights were very harsh, so dim things for you a bit without impeding your vision.

slot machine.name: Slot Machine
slot machine.description: Big money, big money, no whammies.... (odds of pretend winning are 1 in 10).

roulette wheel.name: Roulette Wheel
roulette wheel.description: Spin the wheel and take your chances! Where she ends up, nobody knows!

pleiadian star ship.name: Pleiadian Star Ship
pleiadian star ship.description: Without a source of antimatter, all this ship can do is hover along the ground. Sponsored by Pleiadian.

password door.name: Password Door
password door.description: These doors only open if you know the magic word... which you do, because you set it.

g-virus.name: g-Virus
g-virus.description: It would be dangerous to throw this on someone, not to mention downright rude!

combover.name: Combover
combover.description: Don't worry, you've combed it so well that nobody can even tell you're bald!

lab coat.name: Lab Coat
lab coat.description: The perfect outfit for those occasions when you are zapping lightning through a corpse.

traffic barricade.name: Traffic Barricade
traffic barricade.description: Zombies usually respect all traffic laws, so these are handy to have around.

toxic waste barrel.name: Toxic Waste Barrel
toxic waste barrel.description: This barrel is filled with a highly unstoppable compound, well not filled exactly - some of it is dripping on the floor! Approach with your caution.

toxic waste.name: Toxic Waste
toxic waste.description: Usually safely stored in barrels, but currently stored ON YOUR FACE.

biohazard sign.name: Biohazard Sign
biohazard sign.description: Do not lick under any circumstances.

antidote.name: Antidote
antidote.description: This is THE antidote. To everything. Drink up, and you shall be cured!

tombstone.name: Tombstone
tombstone.description: Looks like somebody got too close to some Death Spikes.

military radio.name: Military Radio
military radio.description: This radio is your last link to the human race so why is it just playing spooky music?

zombie-stompin' boots.name: Zombie-Stompin' Boots
zombie-stompin' boots.description: These military surplus boots are steel-toed and spike-soled. Hey hey, do the zombie stomp!

jens beard.name: Jens Beard
jens beard.description: Nobody but Jens is so wise and ancient.

showgirl headdress.name: Showgirl Headdress
showgirl headdress.description: You're almost the Statue of Liberty.

zeta reticulant mask.name: Zeta Reticulant Mask
zeta reticulant mask.description: No one is ever going to trust you with a probe again. Sponsored by Pleiadian.

red growsaber.name: Red Growsaber
red growsaber.description: You really don't want to drop this on your toe. Sponsored by JakeShore.

black growsaber.name: Black Growsaber
black growsaber.description: You really don't want this to drop on your toe. Sponsored by PirateHunter.

green growsaber.name: Green Growsaber
green growsaber.description: You really don't want to drop this on your toe.

blue growsaber.name: Blue Growsaber
blue growsaber.description: You really don't want to drop this on your toe.

flamesaber.name: Flamesaber
flamesaber.description: The energies contained in this blade are struggling to burst free.

double growsaber.name: Double Growsaber
double growsaber.description: Twice the sabery goodness, with half the calories!

solorien on fire.name: Solorien On Fire
solorien on fire.description: She's the symbol of a revolution in moderating!

flaming skull mask.name: Flaming Skull Mask
flaming skull mask.description: If you had skin on your face, this would really be painful. Sponsored by Ticklehead.

ripper wings.name: Ripper Wings
ripper wings.description: Rippling bands of dark energy carry you aloft. Sponsored by Ripply.

seil's magic orbs.name: Seil's Magic Orbs
seil's magic orbs.description: Seil is some kind of evil wizard.

water bucket.name: Water Bucket
water bucket.description: Splash it around to make things wet. It can also scoop up water, though there's a good chance you'll just spill it. Butterfingers.

refrigerator.name: Refrigerator
refrigerator.description: Keep your best items cool so they don't spoil! When it's closed, the items are hidden. Punch to open it.

emerald block.name: Emerald Block
emerald block.description: Wow, you get 5 emeralds for the price of 1!

ruby block.name: Ruby Block
ruby block.description: Considering the size, this is the most valuable ruby in existence. But it's only a video game.

beach blast.name: Beach Blast
beach blast.description: This magical object requires 100 Fireworks to detonate. It will create a brand new pristine beach world!

coral.name: Coral
coral.description: This is a very special breed of coral that survives just as well in and out of water.

fireworks.name: Fireworks
fireworks.description: Use this for a splendid celebration! Or save it for more important things.

summer surprise.name: Summer Surprise
summer surprise.description: It's a box filled with summer excitement! Smash it with your friends.

women's swimsuit.name: Women's Swimsuit
women's swimsuit.description: Hop in the pool, it's warm!

men's swimsuit.name: Men's Swimsuit
men's swimsuit.description: Hop in the pool, it's warm!

swim fins.name: Swim Fins
swim fins.description: These aren't the best way to move on land, but they'll zoom you through water like a dolphin!

beach umbrella.name: Beach Umbrella
beach umbrella.description: If they had just let this palm tree live, you could've sat under that instead of a bunch of dead fronds.

ocean rock.name: Ocean Rock
ocean rock.description: It's the back side of the ocean! Or a lake, whatever.

barky's mask.name: Barky's Mask
barky's mask.description: A bit sweaty to wear during the dog days of summer. Sponsored by Barkbits.

palm tree.name: Palm Tree
palm tree.description: These seeds of course grow on a Palm Tree Tree. Which looks nothing like a Palm Tree.

garbage.name: Garbage
garbage.description: Yuck, man. I hope somebody cleans this up.

wrought-iron fence.name: Wrought-Iron Fence
wrought-iron fence.description: Whether you're making a classy manor or a haunted mansion, you can't go wrong with wrought-iron!

velvet rope.name: Velvet Rope
velvet rope.description: Show people where they need to go in style!

sproingy eyes.name: Sproingy Eyes
sproingy eyes.description: Don't worry, those aren't your real eyes, they'0072e just plastic.

cow.name: Cow
cow.description: Moooooo. You can milk a cow once a day or so!

milk.name: Milk
milk.description: It does they body okay, though there are lower-fat ways to get calcium.

calf leash.name: Calf Leash
calf leash.description: Moo! This little baby cow will follow you wherever you go! Mainly because it's tied to your wrist.

chicken.name: Chicken
chicken.description: BOK BOK BOK! Chickens will lay eggs for you about once a day!

egg.name: Egg
egg.description: Toss these all over, if you want to be a horrible vandal.

chick leash.name: Chick Leash
chick leash.description: Peep peep! This little baby chick will follow you everywhere you go! Mainly because it's tied to your wrist.

piglet leash.name: Piglet Leash
piglet leash.description: Oink oink! This little piglet will follow you everywhere you go! Mainly because it's tied to your wrist.

wheat.name: Wheat
wheat.description: You're not in Kansas anymore... but if you were, it'd pretty much look like this.

butterfly leash.name: Butterfly Leash
butterfly leash.description: Flap flap! This little butterfly will follow you everywhere you go! Mainly because it's tied to your wrist.

barn block.name: Barn Block
barn block.description: Tis a fine barn, but sure 'tis no pool, English.

barn door.name: Barn Door
barn door.description: Shut it! Were you raised in a barn?

red wood wall.name: Red Wood Wall
red wood wall.description: This wood is red, but it's not redwood, it's oak. It's just painted red.

straw hat.name: Straw Hat
straw hat.description: Keeps the sun off of you as you farm all the live-long day.

overalls.name: Overalls
overalls.description: You feel like you could whitewash fences all day in this getup, yes sir!

pitchfork.name: Pitchfork
pitchfork.description: Whether you're turning over hay, poking evildoers in the tukhus, or just eating incredibly large noodles, this is the tool for you.

farmgirl hair.name: Farmgirl Hair
farmgirl hair.description: Sorry to break the fourth wall, but I feel you should be informed: this hair is a "face item" like sunglasses, so you can wear hats over it!

dear john tractor.name: Dear John Tractor
dear john tractor.description: Too lazy to push buttons to farm? The tractor will do it for you!

dragon hand.name: Dragon Hand
dragon hand.description: Call forth the Dragons of Legend! Please be aware the legends may have been a bit exaggerated.

shockinator.name: Shockinator
shockinator.description: High Voltage can lead to severe trauma and even in extreme cases, frizzy hair.

ze goggles.name: Ze Goggles
ze goggles.description: Not recommended to protect your eyes from acid - Ze Goggles, they do nothing!

shocking hair.name: Shocking Hair
shocking hair.description: In the mad science business, electrocution is a constant hazard. The mad scientist Don King knows this well.

enhanced intellect.name: Enhanced Intellect
enhanced intellect.description: You're a serious show-off, you know that? Nobody needs to see this.

laboratory.name: Laboratory
laboratory.description: Drop three stacks of items on this, then punch it to attempt to process them into a fabulous new item! It can only mix exactly 3 stacks. Most combinations will do nothing, so experiment!

chemical g.name: Chemical G
chemical g.description: This is a highly toxic chemical. Do not ingest! Place carefully in a Laboratory to combine with other chemicals and create amazing new things.

chemical r.name: Chemical R
chemical r.description: This is a highly toxic chemical. Do not ingest! Place carefully in a Laboratory to combine with other chemicals and create amazing new things.

chemical p.name: Chemical P
chemical p.description: This is a highly toxic chemical. Do not ingest! Place carefully in a Laboratory to combine with other chemicals and create amazing new things.

chemical b.name: Chemical B
chemical b.description: This is a highly toxic chemical. Do not ingest! Place carefully in a Laboratory to combine with other chemicals and create amazing new things.

mysterious chemical.name: Mysterious Chemical
mysterious chemical.description: This recently-discovered formulation is incredibly dangerous. Do not even LOOK AT IT. Place carefully in a Laboratory to combine with other chemicals to create amazing new things.

chemical y.name: Chemical Y
chemical y.description: This is a highly toxic chemical. Do not ingest! Place carefully in a Laboratory to combine with other chemicals and create amazing new things.

steel table.name: Steel Table
steel table.description: Stack a bunch of these in a row to make a table as long as you want.

science station.name: Science Station
science station.description: The ideal station for performing SCIENCE! You can collect experimental results about twice a day.

death ray.name: Death Ray
death ray.description: For safety reasons, we've had to disable the "Death" portion of this device. It is pretty hard on blocks though.

weather machine - sunny.name: Weather Machine - Sunny
weather machine - sunny.description: Punch this to enjoy the most wonderful Growtopian weather. Not much use most of the time. This sensitive technology will not function while damaged.

weather machine - night.name: Weather Machine - Night
weather machine - night.description: Night is arguably the most common form of weather. Seems like every evening, a dark front just rolls right in. This sensitive technology will not function while damaged.

red bones.name: Red Bones
red bones.description: Oddly, Redbone's skull is bigger than his head.

desert blast.name: Desert Blast
desert blast.description: Use this astounding device to create an entirely new desert world. One free pyramid included.

boulder.name: Boulder
boulder.description: It's like a rock, but dirtier.

weather machine - arid.name: Weather Machine - Arid
weather machine - arid.description: It's amazing how a little change in the weather can completely reshape the mountains! This sensitive technology will not function while damaged.

scoreboard.name: Scoreboard
scoreboard.description: Punch it to see the top worlds of the day! This sensitive technology will not function while damaged.

e-z cook oven.name: E-Z Cook Oven
e-z cook oven.description: If science isn't pink enough for you, then mix your chemicals in here! For SCIENCE!

sugar cane.name: Sugar Cane
sugar cane.description: The sweetest stalk of grass you'll ever chew!

dough.name: Dough
dough.description: D'oh! This is raw! What can we do with it?

habanero cheese bread.name: Habanero Cheese Bread
habanero cheese bread.description: It's a spicy gooey treat! Watch out though, it's really hot.

tomato.name: Tomato
tomato.description: Express your displeasure with performance in vegetable form!

pizza.name: Pizza
pizza.description: I'll have the Supreme with Cheese!

apple pie.name: Apple Pie
apple pie.description: The most delicious incarnation of the humble apple.

cheeseburger.name: Cheeseburger
cheeseburger.description: You're really not using all the parts of the animal, are you?

silver idol.name: Silver Idol
silver idol.description: Some speak of an ancient curse placed on this idol. Others speak of a free frogurt. Who knows what to believe anymore?

ancient stone gate.name: Ancient Stone Gate
ancient stone gate.description: What could lurk behind such a barrier? Ancient secrets? Cursed mummies? Perhaps a stash of purple blocks.

obelisk.name: Obelisk
obelisk.description: Punching this mystical stone makes it pulse with dark energy...

sungate.name: Sungate
sungate.description: This alien artifact can teleport you to distant worlds, but only if it's charged with the power of 7 Obelisks first.

slime.name: Slime
slime.description: Yuck, this stuff is slippery and gross.

profile.name: Profile
profile.description: Tap this to check out your own personal info!

achievement block.name: Achievement Block
achievement block.description: Only usable in a world-locked world. Use your wrench to edit any achievement you've earned into it! Only the owner of the World Lock can edit it.

weather machine - rainy city.name: Weather Machine - Rainy City
weather machine - rainy city.description: It's just another rainy night... without you, jet city woman. This sensitive technology will not function while damaged.

street sign.name: Street Sign
street sign.description: The classic method of identifying streets. Use your Wrench on it to change the message.

gargoyle.name: Gargoyle
gargoyle.description: Gargoyles just love hanging out, man.

gothic building.name: Gothic Building
gothic building.description: The perfect perch for a gargoyle.

sidewalk.name: Sidewalk
sidewalk.description: Most of this is actually bricks, but there's a little bit of sidewalk at the top!

tenement building.name: Tenement Building
tenement building.description: It's not the nicest place to live, especially since you can't even enter it anyway.

fire escape.name: Fire Escape
fire escape.description: This meets all safety standards. I mean, you know, pretty much. Well, it looks safe to me at least. Maybe not safe exactly... more like non-lethal. Well, not always lethal. Lethal on occasion?

fire hydrant.name: Fire Hydrant
fire hydrant.description: These are surprisingly bouncy. Hold Jump as you land for a maximum bounce.

hedge.name: Hedge
hedge.description: Neatly trimmed, to keep the neighborhood tidy.

blue mailbox.name: Blue Mailbox
blue mailbox.description: You've got mail! People can write you private messages with this.

atm machine.name: ATM Machine
atm machine.description: Your very own Automated teller machine...machine. This device is not FDIC insured. It does, however, spit out a random number of gems about once a day!

destructo ray.name: Destructo Ray
destructo ray.description: Dr. Destructo's unstoppable beam of annihilation.

stick horse.name: Stick Horse
stick horse.description: Clop clop clop. Coconuts not included.

tumbleweed attractor.name: Tumbleweed Attractor
tumbleweed attractor.description: Static electricity in this bracelet draws tumbleweeds toward you. One, at least.

six shooter.name: Six Shooter
six shooter.description: Did I shoot five bullets or six? Doesn't much matter, since in Growtopia you can just keep shooting forever!

tiny appaloosa.name: Tiny Appaloosa
tiny appaloosa.description: It's possible this is actually a dalmation, but you can still ride it! It's faster than walking.

parasol.name: Parasol
parasol.description: The dainty way to slow your fall! Hold the jump button while falling to keep the parasol open.

cowboy hat.name: Cowboy Hat
cowboy hat.description: Yeehaw! Git along little horsies which may be doggies!

war paint.name: War Paint
war paint.description: Strike fear into the hearts of your enemies, until they realize you just put your lipstick on really badly.

face bandana.name: Face Bandana
face bandana.description: When you don't want anyone to recognize your chin, this is a perfect disguise.

sheriff's vest.name: Sheriff's Vest
sheriff's vest.description: Round up the badguys with this enduring symbol of authority. Comes with adorable kerchief.

cowboy boots.name: Cowboy Boots
cowboy boots.description: We've attached specialized Safety Spurs to these boots, so you don't hurt anybody. Please respect other peoples' ankles.

kansas curls.name: Kansas Curls
kansas curls.description: These lovely golden locks are a "face item" - feel free to wear a hat on top!

corset.name: Corset
corset.description: Feeling fat? You could exercise... or you could just cram your gut into one of these! Oh sure, you may end up with spinal deformities, but beauty demands pain!

layer cake dress.name: Layer Cake Dress
layer cake dress.description: Your girl. She's not very good. She made you a dress that looks like you bought it in a store.

western building.name: Western Building
western building.description: This isn't a real building, it's just a painted piece of plywood.

saloon doors.name: Saloon Doors
saloon doors.description: When you really need to make an entrance, you can slam these open. Just don't get shot doing it.

western banner.name: Western Banner
western banner.description: I don't know what language this is, but they spoke it in the old west.

buffalo.name: Buffalo
buffalo.description: You really don't want a home where these guys roam. You can milk a buffalo once a day or so!

rustic fence.name: Rustic Fence
rustic fence.description: This is an ideal place to lean while chewing on straw and saying "Yep." It also keeps animals in place.

campfire.name: Campfire
campfire.description: Gather round and sing songs of days of yore...

secret of growtopia.name: Secret Of Growtopia
secret of growtopia.description: On this paper is scrawled a deep secret of Growtopia. But to read the mystic scrawls, you must throw the paper to the winds! I don't know, that's just how it works. One of those secrets of Growtopia, I guess.

transmog crystal.name: Transmog Crystal
transmog crystal.description: This mysterious crystal has the power to transform one object into another, but only in the fiery furnace of a Laboratory or E-Z Cook Oven.

chinese lantern.name: Chinese Lantern
chinese lantern.description: A soothing dim light for evening festivities. You can punch this to turn it on or off.

songpyeon.name: Songpyeon
songpyeon.description: This sweet steamed rice cake is said to lead to a bright future for whoever eats it. Eat up! You can also mix it with Mooncakes in a Laboratory or E-Z Cook Oven to create special Harvest Festival items.

harmony mooncake.name: Harmony Mooncake
harmony mooncake.description: This pastry is filled with a sweet bean paste. "Harmony" is imprinted on the top in ancient Growtopian script. Mix this with other Mooncakes in a Laboratory or E-Z Cook Oven to create special Harvest Festival items.

harvest moon blast.name: Harvest Moon Blast
harvest moon blast.description: This amazing lunar device will create a new world with a unique harvest moon background, filled with random trees ready to harvest!

ultra grow spray.name: Ultra Grow Spray
ultra grow spray.description: Spray a tree to instantly grow it to full size! Can only grow 30 day's growth at the most, but that's longer than almost any item takes.

scarecrow.name: Scarecrow
scarecrow.description: Notice how there are NO crows around? This thing is working!

sky lantern.name: Sky Lantern
sky lantern.description: Release this lantern into the wind to celebrate the harvest!

hand scythe.name: Hand Scythe
hand scythe.description: This creepy blade can chop down trees with great precision - you'll get twice as much fruit! The only downside is that it's highly likely to break when used. It has no effect (but won't break either!) on trees of rarity 100 or more.

yellow hanbok top.name: Yellow Hanbok Top
yellow hanbok top.description: These Festival clothes are extra festive!

purple hanbok top.name: Purple Hanbok Top
purple hanbok top.description: These Festival clothes are extra festive!

green hanbok top.name: Green Hanbok Top
green hanbok top.description: These Festival clothes are extra festive!

pink hanbok skirt.name: Pink Hanbok Skirt
pink hanbok skirt.description: These Festival clothes are extra festive!

blue hanbok skirt.name: Blue Hanbok Skirt
blue hanbok skirt.description: These Festival clothes are extra festive!

orange hanbok skirt.name: Orange Hanbok Skirt
orange hanbok skirt.description: These Festival clothes are extra festive!

yellow hanbok pants.name: Yellow Hanbok Pants
yellow hanbok pants.description: These festival clothes are extra festive!

purple hanbok pants.name: Purple Hanbok Pants
purple hanbok pants.description: These Festival clothes are extra festive!

green hanbok pants.name: Green Hanbok Pants
green hanbok pants.description: These Festival clothes are extra festive!

festival hair bun.name: Festival Hair Bun
festival hair bun.description: Classy and festive at the same time.

gat.name: Gat
gat.description: This style of hat is cleverly strapped to your head so it won't blow away

peace mooncake.name: Peace Mooncake
peace mooncake.description: This pastry is filled with a sweet bean paste. "Peace" is imprinted on the top in ancient Growtopian script. Mix this with other Mooncakes in a Laboratory or E-Z Cook Oven to create special Harvest Festival items.

longevity mooncake.name: Longevity Mooncake
longevity mooncake.description: This pastry is filled with a sweet bean paste. "Longevity" is imprinted on the top in ancient Growtopian script. Mix this with other Mooncakes in a Laboratory or E-Z Cook Oven to create special Harvest Festival items.

prosperity mooncake.name: Prosperity Mooncake
prosperity mooncake.description: This pastry is filled with a sweet bean paste. "Prosperity" is imprinted on the top in ancient Growtopian script. Mix this with other Mooncakes in a Laboratory or E-Z Cook Oven to create special Harvest Festival items.

pillar.name: Pillar
pillar.description: Add a touch of class to your architecture! Also, keep it from falling down.

sequoia tree.name: Sequoia Tree
sequoia tree.description: These massive trees live for thousands of years. Please don't punch them.

foliage.name: Foliage
foliage.description: You can't see the forest for this stuff.

amphora.name: Amphora
amphora.description: This ancient greek vase could be filled with just about anything! But my bet is on gems and possibly a seed.

potted daisy.name: Potted Daisy
potted daisy.description: This daisy is in a pot. Pretty simple, really.

dragon tail.name: Dragon Tail
dragon tail.description: We warned you to stay away from the toxic waste barrels.

clown shoes.name: Clown Shoes
clown shoes.description: You want respect, you gotta EARN it. Or wear these shoes. BAM, instant respect.

clown pants.name: Clown Pants
clown pants.description: They come complete with suspenders! Which is a good thing, since they're a BIT big.

foam finger.name: Foam Finger
foam finger.description: If you wear this, then YOU'RE #1! YOU'RE #1! YOU'RE #1!

mars rock.name: Mars Rock
mars rock.description: This is a rock from Mars.

mars blast.name: Mars Blast
mars blast.description: This amazing device will create a new world... Mars, to be exact!

martian tree.name: Martian Tree
martian tree.description: I planted a tree, it grew up so big, it grew two sizes up from an extra-large Squig! The tree had blue puffs at the end of each branch, so under the puffs we did the Zorbity Dance!

astronaut pack.name: Astronaut Pack
astronaut pack.description: This contains all the essentials you need for a successful extravehicular activity trip, including a book of sudoku. It also makes you jump like you're on the moon.

space suit.name: Space Suit
space suit.description: Multiple layers offer protection against cold, vacuum, radiation, and parasitic alien infestation. Of course it's also sleeveless, so....?

space pants.name: Space Pants
space pants.description: A space suit isn't going to protect you very well if you don't put on pants too.

moon boots.name: Moon Boots
moon boots.description: It's just one small step for a Growtopian, one giant leap for Growtopia.

astronaut helmet.name: Astronaut Helmet
astronaut helmet.description: Now you can be one of those creepy astronauts with a chrome-plated face, where nobody knows who you are and what you're up to.

zorbnik leash.name: Zorbnik Leash
zorbnik leash.description: ZYERBLRB! This little zorbnik will follow you everywhere you go! Mainly because it's tied to your wrist.

zorbnik dna.name: Zorbnik DNA
zorbnik dna.description: You can't do much with just some Zorbnik DNA... unless you collect 10 Zorbnik DNA and use them all together, that is.

space connector.name: Space Connector
space connector.description: Got things in space you want to stick together? Nothing works better than a space connector.

white wallpaper.name: White Wallpaper
white wallpaper.description: It's a White Block squashed flat.

black wallpaper.name: Black Wallpaper
black wallpaper.description: It's a Black Block squashed flat.

porthole.name: Porthole
porthole.description: Wow, the view from up here is simply amazing!

forcefield.name: Forcefield
forcefield.description: This directed energy field has the power to function as solid matter for people who aren't invited, while being completely permeable to anyone else. I guess that makes it a door.

compu panel.name: Compu Panel
compu panel.description: This technology is incredibly advanced - you could run an entire starship on this Compu Panel! If you had any idea what any of the buttons do.

vampire cape.name: Vampire Cape
vampire cape.description: This cape imparts mystical powers upon its wearer.

slick black hair.name: Slick Black Hair
slick black hair.description: You must have a really greasy pillow.

vampire fangs.name: Vampire Fangs
vampire fangs.description: Wearing these impedes lip movement just enough to induce a Transylvanian accent.

vamp vest.name: Vamp Vest
vamp vest.description: Looks like you won the gold medal in bloodsucking.

rollback plaque ii.name: Rollback Plaque II
rollback plaque ii.description: You were there, man. You were THERE when time rolled backwards again and all the fruits of your labors turned to dust in your dry, bitter fist. Oct 2013

skeletal horsie.name: Skeletal Horsie
skeletal horsie.description: Did you forget to feed your horse again?

spiritual resonator.name: Spiritual Resonator
spiritual resonator.description: This miraculous device allows you to commune with spirits from the Other Side.

hockey mask.name: Hockey Mask
hockey mask.description: Surely you're just a big sports fan... right? Right?

mummy mask.name: Mummy Mask
mummy mask.description: It's hard to speak through these bandages!

wolfman mask.name: Wolfman Mask
wolfman mask.description: The fun bonus is that you can take this off, and then you're wearing your "daytime wolfman mask". It's almost 2 masks in one!

black cat leash.name: Black Cat Leash
black cat leash.description: Meow! The bad thing about wearing this leash is that you end up with a black cat constantly crossing your path.

creepy hair.name: Creepy Hair
creepy hair.description: Your hair's such a mess, you look like you just stepped out of a TV.

haunted house.name: Haunted House
haunted house.description: Is it just your imagination... or are the walls actually stretching?

jack o' lantern.name: Jack O' Lantern
jack o' lantern.description: I think this pumpkin is haunted... when you punch it, spooky music comes out!

pumpkin block.name: Pumpkin Block
pumpkin block.description: This pumpkin was grown inside a square box.

jack o' block.name: Jack O' Block
jack o' block.description: This pumpkin was grown inside a square box, and then carved up.

lit jack o' block.name: Lit Jack O' Block
lit jack o' block.description: This pumpkin was grown inside a square box, and then carved, and then had a lit candle put inside.

focused eyes.name: Focused Eyes
focused eyes.description: These eyes are a bit shocking.

devil wings.name: Devil Wings
devil wings.description: You don't jump higher than with normal wings, but man, you do look pretty cool.

candy corn.name: Candy Corn
candy corn.description: Every year, they collect all the uneaten Candy Corn and store it again, to be given out the next year.

weather machine - spooky.name: Weather Machine - Spooky
weather machine - spooky.description: Darkness falls across the land... The midnight hour is close at hand...

lock of black fur.name: Lock of Black Fur
lock of black fur.description: Not much by itself, but if you had 25 of these, I bet you could mush them together into something pretty good! Or a gross hairball.

familiar leash.name: Familiar Leash
familiar leash.description: Mrow HISS! This black cat contains the very essence of dark magic. Unfortunately, it's a cat, so you can't get it to use the magic for you.

cultist hood.name: Cultist Hood
cultist hood.description: You look a little shady in this thing...

cultist robe.name: Cultist Robe
cultist robe.description: Just the thing to worship Growganoth in!

sigil of k'tesh.name: Sigil Of K'Tesh
sigil of k'tesh.description: Unlike the Sigil of John Tesh, which is smooth and jazzy, this arcane emblem grants you favor with Growganoth. Sadly, that means it will teleport you directly into his gaping maw.

creepstone platform.name: Creepstone Platform
creepstone platform.description: These stones were mined in an alternate dimension where rocks float in the air.

disabled platform.name: Disabled Platform
disabled platform.description: A Creepstone Platform turned off. Not for players.

evil eye.name: Evil Eye
evil eye.description: Don't let it look at you! Luckily it is very near-sighted so you'd have to actually touch it for it to see. Which would kill you, by the way.

frankenhair.name: Frankenhair
frankenhair.description: Did you stick your finger in a light socket?

sonar bracelet.name: Sonar Bracelet
sonar bracelet.description: Meep meep! This bracelet attracts bats. Well, a bat.

devil wing fragment.name: Devil Wing Fragment
devil wing fragment.description: Collect 4 of these fragments and see what happens!

boney block.name: Boney Block
boney block.description: They're not fat, they're just big-boned.

heart monitor.name: Heart Monitor
heart monitor.description: Place this device and anybody can watch it to see if you are online! Or alive. Note: it can't actually tell if you're alive. But it will beep if you are online!

scrub cap.name: Scrub Cap
scrub cap.description: Keep your hair out of your eyes while performing surgery with this sterile cap.

scrub top.name: Scrub Top
scrub top.description: Special sterilized clothes, for chopping folks up!

scrub pants.name: Scrub Pants
scrub pants.description: Even your knees need to be kept sterile when you're operating.

magnifying glass.name: Magnifying Glass
magnifying glass.description: This has over 10,000,000x magnification, allowing you to clearly see the virus that is ... wait is that virus following you around? RUN!

retro magnifying glass.name: Retro Magnifying Glass
retro magnifying glass.description: This has over 10,000,000x magnification, allowing you to clearly see the retrovirus that is totally grooving on your vibes.

hospital bed.name: Hospital Bed
hospital bed.description: Lay in this bed and one of our doctors will see to you as soon as possible.

surgical sponge.name: Surgical Sponge
surgical sponge.description: Used only in surgery. If you make a mess, a sponge can suck it up easily!

surgical scalpel.name: Surgical Scalpel
surgical scalpel.description: Used only in surgery. Use this to cut people open!

surgical anesthetic.name: Surgical Anesthetic
surgical anesthetic.description: Used only in surgery. You probably don't want to operate on somebody unless they are unconscious. Use this to knock them out!

surgical antiseptic.name: Surgical Antiseptic
surgical antiseptic.description: Used only in surgery. Don't mix this up with the Anesthetic! This is used for cleaning an area before you cut it open.

surgical antibiotics.name: Surgical Antibiotics
surgical antibiotics.description: Used only in surgery. Use these to lower a patient's temperature.

surgical splint.name: Surgical Splint
surgical splint.description: Used only in surgery. If somebody has a broken bone, you better splint it up or it'll heal all crooked.

surgical stitches.name: Surgical Stitches
surgical stitches.description: Used only in surgery. Bandages are included too, for lesser injuries. Use these to close up after performing surgery, or to strap a splint on so it stays.

ambulance.name: Ambulance
ambulance.description: For the sake of your fellow Growtopians, we limited the siren. But you can still enjoy the flashing lights!

edison zoomster.name: Edison Zoomster
edison zoomster.description: Only the chief of surgery can afford a speedy electric car like this!

punch jammer.name: Punch Jammer
punch jammer.description: When activated (punch to activate), this prevents people from punching each other in your world.

zombie jammer.name: Zombie Jammer
zombie jammer.description: When activated (punch to activate), this prevents zombies from infecting anyone in your world.

birth certificate.name: Birth Certificate
birth certificate.description: A little white-out, a little scribbling, and voila, you'll have a new name! Use this item to change your GrowID permanently. Can only be used once every 30 days. Requires a GrowID. Is consumed when used.

candy striper cap.name: Candy Striper Cap
candy striper cap.description: Red wig included. And stapled on.

candy striper uniform.name: Candy Striper Uniform
candy striper uniform.description: I wonder where on earth this nurse's uniform gets its name from...

candy striper skirt.name: Candy Striper Skirt
candy striper skirt.description: This is also nice if you want to work at the kind of burger restaurant that requires Pieces of Flair from its wait staff.

hospital curtain.name: Hospital Curtain
hospital curtain.description: This helps maintain your privacy when you are undergoing delicate medical procedures.

hospital wall.name: Hospital Wall
hospital wall.description: The soothing pale yellow tone and complete lack of anything interesting helps speed healing and make people want to get out of there.

hospital window.name: Hospital Window
hospital window.description: Looking out at nature is supposed to help you recover.

hospital door.name: Hospital Door
hospital door.description: This door is designed to be easy to push open when you're rolling a body around on a cart. Place one and then use your Wrench on it to set the destination.

surgical gloves.name: Surgical Gloves
surgical gloves.description: This item doesn't really exist, just using its icon for surgery menu.

cutaway building.name: Cutaway Building
cutaway building.description: If you want to make an interior view of a building, you can use these blocks to show the walls and floors!!

roshambo block.name: Roshambo Block
roshambo block.description: Punch it to roll Rock, Paper, or Scissors. What you do with the resulting information is entirely up to you!

cow cube.name: Cow Cube
cow cube.description: This cow is squarer than most.

staircase.name: Staircase
staircase.description: Sometimes it's nice to climb a staircase instead of hopping up platforms. Unfortunately, you'll also have to hop up the staircase - Growtopians can't climb.

terracotta pot.name: Terracotta Pot
terracotta pot.description: You should plant your trees in these. It's just classier.

climbing vine.name: Climbing Vine
climbing vine.description: These vines can grow to extraordinary heights. Provided you place Climbing Vine blocks up to extraordinary heights.

thingamajig.name: Thingamajig
thingamajig.description: I have no idea what this thing does. It's something electronic? Maybe?

bushy beard.name: Bushy Beard
bushy beard.description: You look like you should be in charge of magical animals with this beard.

ponytail.name: Ponytail
ponytail.description: Unlike an actual pony, your tail grows out of the back of your head.

happy sun shirt.name: Happy Sun Shirt
happy sun shirt.description: Take joy in the great glowing orb that provides energy for all those toilet trees to grow!

blue sun shirt.name: Blue Sun Shirt
blue sun shirt.description: Well, what you plan and what takes place ain't ever exactly been similar.

riding raptor.name: Riding Raptor
riding raptor.description: I know, they're supposed to have feathers and stuff nowadays... well, this is an old-school raptor!

cliffside.name: Cliffside
cliffside.description: If your friends all jumped off of this, would you?

rock platform.name: Rock Platform
rock platform.description: It's like a Wooden Platform that's been sitting outside since prehistoric times.

cave entrance.name: Cave Entrance
cave entrance.description: Who knows what lurks inside? I guess whoever placed it and used a wrench on it to set the destination.

prehistoric palm.name: Prehistoric Palm
prehistoric palm.description: Much like people, palm trees started out short and squat before evolving to be tall and skinny. Unlike palm trees, people then ate Twinkies and watched TV until they were tubby again.

caveman club.name: Caveman Club
caveman club.description: We've come a long way in methods of settling disputes, but this technique still works.

sabertooth-skin toga.name: Sabertooth-Skin Toga
sabertooth-skin toga.description: Clothing so stylish it'll make you shout "Rabble Dabble Goo!" - you know, to make sure you don't get sued.

caveman hair.name: Caveman Hair
caveman hair.description: The chicken grease helps the bone stay in, and it adds luster.

cavewoman hair.name: Cavewoman Hair
cavewoman hair.description: The chicken grease helps the bone stay in, and it adds luster.

fuzzy bikini top.name: Fuzzy Bikini Top
fuzzy bikini top.description: Is it for cold weather or warm weather? Who knows! It's the world's smallest parka.

ice cube.name: Ice Cube
ice cube.description: This is very ancient ice, shipped from a glacier. Don't just use it to cool your drink!

frozen dna fragment a.name: Frozen DNA Fragment A
frozen dna fragment a.description: Hey, there's some prehistoric DNA stuck in this ice! Most likely you'd ruin it by punching it. But maybe there's a chance......

frozen dna fragment b.name: Frozen DNA Fragment B
frozen dna fragment b.description: Hey, there's some prehistoric DNA stuck in this ice! Most likely you'd ruin it by punching it. But maybe there's a chance......

mini mammoth leash.name: Mini Mammoth Leash
mini mammoth leash.description: The word "mammoth' has really lost all meaning at this point.

whatchamacallit.name: Whatchamacallit
whatchamacallit.description: I have no idea what this thing does. It's something electronic? Maybe?

kerjigger.name: Kerjigger
kerjigger.description: I have no idea what this thing does. It's something electronic? Maybe?

snowy rocks.name: Snowy Rocks
snowy rocks.description: Or is it Rocky Snow? It's not. The snow is on top.

winter gift.name: Winter Gift
winter gift.description: The joy of giving! You can use this on yourself to open it and get a surprise, or use it on another player to give it to them. If you are feeling extra cheerful, you can also give it to The Growch!

candy cane fence.name: Candy Cane Fence
candy cane fence.description: This fence is terrible for keeping kids off of your lawn.

weather machine - snowy.name: Weather Machine - Snowy
weather machine - snowy.description: Man, the weather outside is frightful.

dumb friend.name: Dumb Friend
dumb friend.description: not used, it's just an icon.

snowball.name: Snowball
snowball.description: Brrr! Toss this at a player to freeze them briefly.

festivus pole.name: Festivus Pole
festivus pole.description: Tinsel is so distracting. Celebrate with an unadorned aluminium pole.

giant candle.name: Giant Candle
giant candle.description: This candle is enormous, but not hot enough to do any real harm.

tangyuan.name: Tangyuan
tangyuan.description: This dumpling soup is warm and toasty to keep you punching, building, and growing during the winter.

yeonnalligi.name: Yeonnalligi
yeonnalligi.description: Fly this colorful kite to ring in the new year!

ice dragon hand.name: Ice Dragon Hand
ice dragon hand.description: Another of the Dragons of Legend! Please be aware the legends may have been a bit exaggerated.

antler hat.name: Antler Hat
antler hat.description: The red checkers alert other hunters not to shoot you, but the antlers make you a prime target. We've scientifically designed this hat to ensure that your odds of being shot remain precisely the same as if you weren't wearing it. Note: Wearing this also makes guns and bows kill you!

glowing nose.name: Glowing Nose
glowing nose.description: Warning: Wearing this could result in exclusion from reindeer games.

buckskin hood.name: Buckskin Hood
buckskin hood.description: So warm and toasty! It's like you sliced open a deer and crawled inside.

buckskin jacket.name: Buckskin Jacket
buckskin jacket.description: So warm and toasty! It's like you sliced open a deer and crawled inside.

holiday gift box.name: Holiday Gift Box
holiday gift box.description: People can drop gifts into this box for you to pickup later!

buckskin pants.name: Buckskin Pants
buckskin pants.description: So warm and toasty! It's like you sliced open a deer and crawled inside.

polar bear leash.name: Polar Bear Leash
polar bear leash.description: If you look out your window and see this guy, you are looking south. Or at a zoo. Or at somebody playing Growtopia.

doohickey.name: Doohickey
doohickey.description: I have no idea what this thing does. It's something electronic? Maybe?

inviso-block.name: Inviso-Block
inviso-block.description: These blocks cannot be seen. Thus they cannot be used by players because that would be a nightmare.

mini growtopian.name: Mini Growtopian
mini growtopian.description: Ah, he just wants to tag along!

thermonuclear blast.name: Thermonuclear Blast
thermonuclear blast.description: Use this fabulous device to create a brand new world that is completely empty, except for bedrock and a white door.

door mover.name: Door Mover
door mover.description: Use this fabulous device anywhere in a world you have world-locked to move the White Door to a new location. There must be an empty space where you tap and another empty space below it for this to work.

skyrocket.name: Skyrocket
skyrocket.description: Celebrate the holidays by firing off colorful rockets!

mannequin.name: Mannequin
mannequin.description: Dress up your mannequin with clothes! Use your wrench to change the sign on it.

display box.name: Display Box
display box.description: Drop items for sale in these handy boxes! Only players with access to the lock can pick them up!

world key.name: World Key
