world key.description: If you trade this to another player while in a world that you own, they will become the owner of your World Lock! Use it to trade worlds safely.

for sale sign.name: For Sale Sign
for sale sign.description: Tell people what you're selling! Use your wrench on it to change the message.

gem sign.name: Gem Sign
gem sign.description: Say something about Gems on this sign. I Guess? Use your Wrench on it to change the message.

shop sign.name: Shop Sign
shop sign.description: Let everyone know you're running a shop! Use your Wrench on it to change the message.

exclamation sign.name: Exclamation Sign
exclamation sign.description: Excited about something? Let people know! Use your Wrench on it to change the message.

cash register.name: Cash Register
cash register.description: Punch it to ring up a sale!

security camera.name: Security Camera
security camera.description: This camera will watch your world and keep a record of everybody who enters! You may have up to 8 of these in a world.

golden pickaxe.name: Golden Pickaxe
golden pickaxe.description: This tool, made to honor Diichaan's service as a moderator, is worth more than the stuff you mine for!

evil space helmet.name: Evil Space Helmet
evil space helmet.description: Zerkon commands a starship too small to actually board.

open sign.name: Open Sign
open sign.description: You can punch this to switch it between Open and Closed! Let people know if you're around.

television.name: Television
television.description: Yes kids, TVs really used to look like this! And they didn't have color screens! And they showed westerns! GET OFF OF MY LAWN!

couch.name: Couch
couch.description: Just the thing to watch your TV on. Except your TV can only face the opposite direction.

donation box.name: Donation Box
donation box.description: People can insert or put donations or gifts into the box for you to pickup later or keep it!

gold chain.name: Gold Chain
gold chain.description: I pity the fool who doesn't wear a set of these.

golden heart crystal.name: Golden Heart Crystal
golden heart crystal.description: This crystal can be combined with 200 Candy Hearts and any Valentine's Clothing in a Laboratory or E-Z Cook Oven to infuse the clothing with gold magic!

golden angel wings.name: Golden Angel Wings
golden angel wings.description: Better than a Halo, these will actually let you Double Jump! Plus they're shiny!

golden diaper.name: Golden Diaper
golden diaper.description: If you find yourself lost in a world without any Toilet Seeds, you'll be glad you have this. Plus it's shiny!

golden heartbow.name: Golden Heartbow
golden heartbow.description: Once used by Cupid himself, this bow shoots golden hearts! You can yank other players toward you with it. Plus it's shiny!

golden diamond necklace.name: Golden Diamond Necklace
golden diamond necklace.description: Sparkles with the undying light of eternal love. Plus it's shiny!

emerald necklace.name: Emerald Necklace
emerald necklace.description: Emeralds are May's birthstone. This particular one is lab-created, which you'd think is less classy, but they're much prettier.

ruby necklace.name: Ruby Necklace
ruby necklace.description: It's a red rock on a metal string. But I guess people like that!

microwave.name: Microwave
microwave.description: This is a quick and handy way to cook food. Or do SCIENCE!

eggs benedict.name: Eggs Benedict
eggs benedict.description: Eating these makes you smarter, so you can get more eggs-perience! Food Buff: 25% chance of double XP from all actions.

window curtains.name: Window Curtains
window curtains.description: It's curtains for these windows! Lacy, gently wafting curtains.

wall clock.name: Wall Clock
wall clock.description: Tell time in Growtopia! This clock displays the current Growtopia Time for you.

growtoken.name: Growtoken
growtoken.description: You can earn these from Crazy Jim and Sales-Man - try dialing 12345 or 53785 on your Telephone for details! Spend them in the store on special items!

experience potion.name: Experience Potion
experience potion.description: SNIFF' ahh. The smell of XP. "DRINKING" YACK! Omg! Yay Level Up!

weather machine - nothingness.name: Weather Machine - Nothingness
weather machine - nothingness.description: Punch this to eradicate all light from the universe. This sensitive technology will not function when damaged.

doodad.name: Doodad
doodad.description: I have no idea what this thing does. It's something electronic? Maybe?

thingamabob.name: Thingamabob
thingamabob.description: I have no idea what this thing does. It's something electronic? Maybe?

rushboard.name: Rushboard
rushboard.description: Just like they predicted, we finally have hoverboards in 2014! Well, virtual ones.

purple stuff.name: Purple Stuff
purple stuff.description: Yuck, purple stuff?! I rather drink imitation orange beverage.

orange stuff.name: Orange Stuff
orange stuff.description: On second thought, orange stuff seems kinda gross too. But you can freeze it into a lovely block.

winter scarf.name: Winter Scarf
winter scarf.description: This scarf is made of fuzzy aquamarine yarn with little sparklies on it. It's tres chic.

old-timey hat.name: Old-Timey Hat
old-timey hat.description: If you're a grizzled old prospector, this is surely the hat for you. Also useful for hard-boiled reporters who always get their story.

medical scarf.name: Medical Scarf
medical scarf.description: These elaborate scarves may only be worn by medical professionals (or anyone else with the title "Doctor").

blarney stone.name: Blarney Stone
blarney stone.description: Players that touch this get a Blarney Pebble.

blarney pebble.name: Blarney Pebble
blarney pebble.description: The legend goes that if you gather up ten of these pebbles, you can charm a leprechaun to be your friend!

pet leprechaun.name: Pet Leprechaun
pet leprechaun.description: He's hidden a pot of gold somewhere... but you'll never find it!

black-rimmed glasses.name: Black-Rimmed Glasses
black-rimmed glasses.description: These stylish glasses can be custom matched to any prescription.

diving bell.name: Diving Bell
diving bell.description: Protect yourself from the crushing pressures of the great deep in this steel helmet. Of course, if you wear a normal wetsuit, you could end up sucked up into the helmet and crushed to death. So, you know, watch for that.

great white shark.name: Great White Shark
great white shark.description: They say a shark can never stop swimming, but this particular shark can never stop swimming in place.

jellyfish.name: Jellyfish
jellyfish.description: Beware of the painful sting of this sea creature! Also beware of the folk remedies for fixing it...

wetsuit pants.name: Wetsuit Pants
wetsuit pants.description: Lay off the donuts, because these things are skin tight!

wetsuit top.name: Wetsuit Top
wetsuit top.description: Lay off the donuts, because these things are skin tight!

sunken anchor.name: Sunken Anchor
sunken anchor.description: I guess a ship somewhere is flying free, never to settle down in one place again.

giant clam.name: Giant Clam
giant clam.description: Store your treasures inside by dropping them! When it's closed, the items are hidden. Punch to open it.

undersea blast.name: Undersea Blast
undersea blast.description: Use this astounding device to create an entirely new undersea world. Water included!

cuddly piranha.name: Cuddly Piranha
cuddly piranha.description: He won't stay in his bowl because he LIKES you! This is one fish you'll never forget.

deep sand.name: Deep Sand
deep sand.description: This sand is all mucked up with gross deep ocean stuff.

deep rock.name: Deep Rock
deep rock.description: It's like a rock, but deeper.

mid-pacific owl.name: Mid-Pacific Owl
mid-pacific owl.description: This friendly pet owl will fall asleep on your head if you don't keep him entertained! Dedicated to the students of the Mid-Pacific Institute.

battle trout.name: Battle Trout
battle trout.description: Why, it's a dead fish. And you're holding it. Oooookayyyy.

green pageboy.name: Green Pageboy
green pageboy.description: This is NOT a helmet, don't call it a helmet! But if you want to use it as a helmet, go ahead. It's hair though.

easter bonnet.name: Easter Bonnet
easter bonnet.description: This fashionable accessory matches ANY outfit with style.

bubble wings.name: Bubble Wings
bubble wings.description: With a pair of wings, you can double-jump! With these wings, you can also bubble.

pet bunny.name: Pet Bunny
pet bunny.description: bunny bunny bunny bunny bunny bunny bunny bunny

lucky pinata hat.name: Lucky Pinata Hat
lucky pinata hat.description: Not only is this hat festive and suitable for formal occasions, but wearing it when you break an Ultra Pinata will reward you with a personal gift from The Great Burro!

mariachi guitar.name: Mariachi Guitar
mariachi guitar.description: When you /dance with this, you can perform for your friends!

churro block.name: Churro Block
churro block.description: The sweetest of blocks - crispy, chewy, cinnamony, delicious.

fiesta dragon.name: Fiesta Dragon
fiesta dragon.description: This ferocious beast spews deadly PARTY at your enemies.

party cactus.name: Party Cactus
party cactus.description: A dangerously happenin' plant! Do not touch.

burrito.name: Burrito
burrito.description: Mmmm, rolled up food. Who cares what's inside? There's a TORTILLA!

pink cadillac.name: Pink Cadillac
pink cadillac.description: There's nothing quite like cruising the Vegas strip in a pink Cadillac!

mystery pinata.name: Mystery Pinata
mystery pinata.description: Put this on top of a bunch of items you want to give away. Once placed, anybody can break it and get the items! The mystery is that certain items will transform into something more festive when it explodes...

pet burrito.name: Pet Burrito
pet burrito.description: So fuzzy! This is not to be eaten.

clapboard.name: Clapboard
clapboard.description: The loud clacking sound this can produce is useful for syncing up audio with video. We've silenced this particular one for the sake of the other players.

3d glasses.name: 3D Glasses
3d glasses.description: It's like Growtopia is COMING RIGHT AT YOU!

theater curtain.name: Theater Curtain
theater curtain.description: Raise it up and start the show! Note: You can't raise it up.

ghx speaker.name: GHX Speaker
ghx speaker.description: The audience is listening. And possibly being deafened.

marquee block.name: Marquee Block
marquee block.description: Put your name up in lights! Letters not included, but hey, there's lights.

director's chair.name: Director's Chair
director's chair.description: Sit down and tell everybody what to do.

mint julep.name: Mint Julep
mint julep.description: Mmm, minty! With a hint of julep. Go horsey go!!

movie screen.name: Movie Screen
movie screen.description: Today's movie is entitled "The polar bear in a snowstorm that found a piece of paper." It's an art film.

movie camera.name: Movie Camera
movie camera.description: Film your own youtube videos! By using some sort of screen capture program, that is. This completely fake camera isn't going to help at all.

red glass block.name: Red Glass Block
red glass block.description: People inside this should not throw stones, and they will be tinted red.

blue glass block.name: Blue Glass Block
blue glass block.description: People inside this should not throw stones, and they will be tinted blue.

growie award.name: Growie Award
growie award.description: Congratulations! Your film has been selected as the best picture of the week! Or you just bought this trophy from someone else like a common peasant.

staging platform.name: Staging Platform
staging platform.description: If a player stands on this, they have first priority on joining a Game. Use your wrench to set which team this platform will assign them to!

game block.name: Game Block
game block.description: Use your wrench to set which team this block belongs to! During a Game, the block can be smashed according to the Game rules, and it will rebuild after the game ends.

busted game block.name: Busted Game Block
busted game block.description: This Game Block has been smashed. It will rebuild when the Game is over.

game flag.name: Game Flag
game flag.description: Use your wrench to set which team this flag belongs to! During a Game, players can steal enemy flags and deliver them to their own Game Goals.

missing game flag.name: Missing Game Flag
missing game flag.description: This flag has been taken. It will return when the Game is over.

carried game flag.name: Carried Game Flag
carried game flag.description: A flag being carried by a player.

coffee maker.name: Coffee Maker
coffee maker.description: These special slow-roasted beans are roasted so slowly that you can only get a cup of coffee once a day!

coffee.name: Coffee
coffee.description: This'll put some pep in your step! And some verve in your nerve! But not that much pizzazz in your jazz.

awkward friendly unicorn.name: Awkward Friendly Unicorn
awkward friendly unicorn.description: This unicorn is going through an awkward stage right now, but it's happy to be your friend. It'll even give you a present about once a week!

unicorn horn.name: Unicorn Horn
unicorn horn.description: This pretty much rules out the possibility of hats, but it's so glowy!

very bad unicorn.name: Very Bad Unicorn
very bad unicorn.description: This is the kind of unicorn your parents warned you about.

horse mask.name: Horse Mask
horse mask.description: These things are just creepy. I don't get the appeal.

unicorn jumper.name: Unicorn Jumper
unicorn jumper.description: A gift from your friendly neighborhood unicorn!

happy unicorn block.name: Happy Unicorn Block
happy unicorn block.description: This block is happy, and prominently features a unicorn.

unicorn garland.name: Unicorn Garland
unicorn garland.description: This magical garland from the mystic land of Unicornopialandburg joins your soul with that of a unicorn. Great for you, but for the unicorn it's pretty much slavery. Not cool, dude.

pink hair.name: Pink Hair
pink hair.description: Oh, is that your natural color?

aqua hair.name: Aqua Hair
aqua hair.description: It takes a liberal dose of Aqua Net to make it look like this.

evil brick background.name: Evil Brick Background
evil brick background.description: Thankfully, these Evil Bricks are further away than the usual kind.

game grave.name: Game Grave
game grave.description: Use your wrench to set which team this block belongs to! During a Game, players of that team will respawn here.

game goal.name: Game Goal
game goal.description: Use your wrench to set which team this block belongs to! During a Game, you may want to bring Flags here, or just reach here yourself, depending on the rules.

game generator.name: Game Generator
game generator.description: This machine generates games for people to play! Use your wrench on it to set up the game rules and start the game.

spike juice.name: Spike Juice
spike juice.description: By carefully drinking small amounts of Death Spikes, you can build up a tolerance! Well, what you can actually do is be immune to Lava and Death Spikes for 5 seconds.

barbecue grill.name: Barbecue Grill
barbecue grill.description: It's summertime, why do your cooking indoors? Also, you can mix chemicals in here. I'm sure that's perfectly safe.

sea monster floatie.name: Sea Monster Floatie
sea monster floatie.description: Blow it up and take a swim!

water wings.name: Water Wings
water wings.description: Not a strong swimmer? Strap these on so at least your arms will stay above water as you drown.

summer kite.name: Summer Kite
summer kite.description: Fly this colorful kite to celebrate summertime!

rainbow wings.name: Rainbow Wings
rainbow wings.description: Somewhere over the rainbow is a Growtopian, flapping away. These let you double jump. Sponsored by Oricho and Oriche.

phoenix wings.name: Phoenix Wings
phoenix wings.description: Is it hot in here, or is it just you? These wings let you double jump! There are only 500 in existence! Don't throw them away!

squirt gun.name: Squirt Gun
squirt gun.description: Squirt your friends with this usually harmless weapon! Or load it with hydrochloric acid and use it to dissolve metal, it works equally well. Longer ranger than normal punches, but less damage.

sandcastle.name: Sandcastle
sandcastle.description: Enjoy it while you can, before the tide comes in.

super fireworks.name: Super Fireworks
super fireworks.description: This Omega-class firework is actually illegal in all countries. All of them. LAUNCH IT ANYWAY!!! Like cereal, it comes with a special prize inside. Note: it will use up 200 Fireworks from your inventory to ignite the Saturn V thruster it uses.

gateway to adventure.name: Gateway To Adventure
gateway to adventure.description: You can set this door up like a Choose Your Own Adventure story! Type up to 5 lines of story, and then add up to 5 buttons for players to choose from, with Door IDs that they lead to.

path marker.name: Path Marker
path marker.description: Use these sort of like Doors - They have IDs, so Doors can lead to them, though you can't travel from them. Use your wrench to set their ID.

safari jacket.name: Safari Jacket
safari jacket.description: The comfortable fit you need to run away from giant rolling boulders.

jodhpurs.name: Jodhpurs
jodhpurs.description: Does these pants make my butt look fat?

adventuring mustache.name: Adventuring Mustache
adventuring mustache.description: Wot wot too right tally ho jolly good ermf ermf.

adventure item - rope.name: Adventure Item - Rope
adventure item - rope.description: Place this in your world to be used in your Gateways To Adventure! Players can pick it up by punching it. They lose it if they leave your world.

adventure item - key.name: Adventure Item - Key
adventure item - key.description: Place this in your world to be used in your Gateways To Adventure! Players can pick it up by punching it. They lose it if they leave your world.

adventure item - golden idol.name: Adventure Item - Golden Idol
adventure item - golden idol.description: Place this in your world to be used in your Gateways To Adventure! Players can pick it up by punching it. They lose it if they leave your world.

adventure item - banana.name: Adventure Item - Banana
adventure item - banana.description: Place this in your world to be used in your Gateways To Adventure! Players can pick it up by punching it. They lose it if they leave your world.

adventure item - torch.name: Adventure Item - Torch
adventure item - torch.description: Place this in your world to be used in your Gateways To Adventure! Players can pick it up by punching it. They lose it if they leave your world.

explorer's ponytail.name: Explorer's Ponytail
explorer's ponytail.description: This sensible hairstyle minimizes the number of cobwebs that stick to you when exploring ancient tombs. The glasses also help you avoid them in the first place.

lazy cobra.name: Lazy Cobra
lazy cobra.description: This species features the deadliest venom of any snake in the world, capable of instantly killing a Growtopian. This is counterbalanced by the fact that it is too lazy to pursue prey at all, simply waiting for people to walk up and touch it.

explorer's shovel.name: Explorer's Shovel
explorer's shovel.description: This is not a whole lot different from a garden shovel, but holding it makes you feel adventurous. It also lets you dig faster than you can by punching dirt. I still don't get why punching dirt works at all.

keytar.name: Keytar
keytar.description: You can't punch when holding this, you're too busy ROCKING! Punch anywhere to play music. If you punch to your left or right, you can bend the note higher or lower. Punch in your own column to play the same notes that Sheet Music: Piano Note plays.

bass guitar.name: Bass Guitar
bass guitar.description: You can't punch when holding this, you're too busy ROCKING! Punch anywhere to play music. If you punch to your left or right, you can bend the note higher or lower. Punch in your own column to play the same notes that Sheet Music: Bass Note plays.

tambourine.name: Tambourine
tambourine.description: You can't punch when holding this, you're too busy ROCKING! Punch anywhere to play drums. If you punch to your left or right, you can play different drums. Punch in your own column to play the same drums that Sheet Music: Drums plays.

starchild makeup.name: Starchild Makeup
starchild makeup.description: You came down from a distant planet, to conquer the Earth with the power of ROCK.

shredded t-shirt.name: Shredded T-Shirt
shredded t-shirt.description: This shirt isn't ruined, it's COOL.

leopard leggings.name: Leopard Leggings
leopard leggings.description: These are the easiest pants to do leaping splits in, if that happens to be important to you. I mean, you might as well jump. Go ahead and jump.

drumkit.name: Drumkit
drumkit.description: You're a rock star. Smack this to pound out some sick beats.

rock n' roll wallpaper.name: Rock N' Roll Wallpaper
rock n' roll wallpaper.description: It's like your wallpaper is on fire, in the dark. WHOOOOOOOOOoooooo!

stage support.name: Stage Support
stage support.description: Use these to build your stage for the ultimate rock show.

mega rock speaker.name: Mega Rock Speaker
mega rock speaker.description: Your worlds doesn't have enough voltage to actually power speakers of this size, but they sure LOOK loud!

rockin' headband.name: Rockin' Headband
rockin' headband.description: When you rock, you sweat. Soak it up!

knight helmet.name: Knight Helmet
knight helmet.description: This helmet was forged by the awesome art god Hamumu. Sponsored by Knightmare.

crystal cape.name: Crystal Cape
crystal cape.description: Though less flexible than your average cape, this is a whole lot sparklier. Allows you to double jump off an imaginary Crystal Block. Sponsored by Edvoid20, Heme, and Aboge.

starboard.name: StarBoard
starboard.description: Just like they predicted, we finally have hoverboards in 2014! Well, virtual ones. Sponsored by Miwsky, Chudy, and Dawid.

puppy leash.name: Puppy Leash
puppy leash.description: Belf! This little puppy is modeled after Hamumu's dog Mia, and can also be found in the fabulous smash hit Flash game Mia's Happy Day! Go play it!

brown wallpaper.name: Brown Wallpaper
brown wallpaper.description: It's a Brown Block squashed flat at last!

fuel pack.name: Fuel Pack
fuel pack.description: This backpack contains volatile fuels you can use to power a flamethrower!

flamethrower.name: Flamethrower
flamethrower.description: The deadliest weapon in Growtopia! The downside is that you need to wear a Fuel Pack to use it, and it uses up 1 Fuel Pack every single punch. KILL IT WITH FIRE!

weather machine - warp speed.name: Weather Machine - Warp Speed
weather machine - warp speed.description: This machine will send your entire world hurtling through space at warp speed. This sensitive technology will not function while damaged.

guestbook.name: Guestbook
guestbook.description: Lets people communicate by leaving messages to each other.

flatscreen tv.name: Flatscreen TV
flatscreen tv.description: This tasteful TV hangs on your wall like a picture. A picture that moves and sings!

tiger block.name: Tiger Block
tiger block.description: Be sure to point out any protestors that this is faux tigerskin. You don't want to end up with Red Blocks instead!

growboard.name: Growboard
growboard.description: Just like they predicted, we finally have hoverboards in 2014! Well, virtual ones. This one spits fire. Sponsored by Coinman, iOliver, and Legomanz.

spiritfire mask.name: Spiritfire Mask
spiritfire mask.description: For the less technologically-inclined, this mask relies on black magic to raise an evil spirit.

soda jetpack.name: Soda Jetpack
soda jetpack.description: Use the power of carbonation to leap tall buildings in a single bound, and then drift gently to Earth. Comes with a lifetime supply of soda, connected via wormhole for continuous refueling.

dominatus moderateus.name: Dominatus Moderateus
dominatus moderateus.description: Could there be more than one cult in Growtopia? Sponsored by Moderate.

seagull.name: Seagull
seagull.description: These extra-strong seagulls can carry the full weight of a Growtopian! Hop on!

flower checkpoint.name: Flower Checkpoint
flower checkpoint.description: If you die, you'll respawn at the last Checkpoint you touched!

bubble gum.name: Bubble Gum
bubble gum.description: This isn't even wrapped, it probably has all kind of germs on it. Are you really gonna chew it?

diving board.name: Diving Board
diving board.description: These are surprisingly bouncy. Hold jump as you land for maximum bounce.

diving board support.name: Diving Board Support
diving board support.description: This part of the diving board is not bouncy at all. Go jump off the unsupported end!

deluxe grow spray.name: Deluxe Grow Spray
deluxe grow spray.description: Spray a tree to grow it 24 hours worth!

legendbot-009.name: Legendbot-009
legendbot-009.description: This legendary battle armor was the turning point in the war of the Growtopia Valley.

dragon of legend.name: Dragon of Legend
dragon of legend.description: This blade calls forth the Ancient Dragon of Unexaggerated Legends and binds it to your command. It's a biggun'.

legendary wings.name: Legendary Wings
legendary wings.description: Turns out you had to do a lot more than ring a bell to get these suckers.

legendary wizard.name: Legendary Wizard
legendary wizard.description: This wizard is legendary! Punch or wrench him to obtain Legendary Quests.

great legendary orb.name: Great Legendary Orb
great legendary orb.description: Players that touch this get a Legendary Orb.

legendary orb.name: Legendary Orb
legendary orb.description: This orb is legendary and filled with a great power. However, you don't have an adapter for it, so the power isn't any use to you. Perhaps a wizard could use it?

diamond lock.name: Diamond Lock
diamond lock.description: Locks an entire world. And it looks good doing it. Tap it in your inventory to break it down into 100 World Locks, if you have room in your inventory.

puzzle brick.name: Puzzle Brick
puzzle brick.description: This brick is just made out of puzzlingly shaped pieces. It's not much of a puzzle itself. Just a brick.

zeus' lightning bolt.name: Zeus' Lightning Bolt
zeus' lightning bolt.description: It's 1.21 gigawatts in the palm of your hands! Sponsored by Hercule, Dodoman11 and RTsoft Forumers.

chinese dragon head.name: Chinese Dragon Head
chinese dragon head.description: You're lucky, you get to be the head!

chinese dragon body.name: Chinese Dragon Body
chinese dragon body.description: This really adds a lot of body to your hair.

chinese dragon tail.name: Chinese Dragon Tail
chinese dragon tail.description: Looks like you got stuck with the tail end. Again.

ssireum shorts - red.name: Ssireum Shorts - Red
ssireum shorts - red.description: Wear these shorts when you are wrestling! If you play in a Game Pack game, your shorts will change color to match your team (Sorry, currently does the wrong color!).

ssireum shorts - blue.name: Ssireum Shorts - Blue
ssireum shorts - blue.description: Wear these shorts when you are wrestling! If you play in a Game Pack game, your shorts will change color to match your team (Sorry, currently does the wrong color!).

ssireum shorts - yellow.name: Ssireum Shorts - Yellow
ssireum shorts - yellow.description: Wear these shorts when you are wrestling! If you play in a Game Pack game, your shorts will change color to match your team (Sorry, currently does the wrong color!).

ssireum shorts - purple.name: Ssireum Shorts - Purple
ssireum shorts - purple.description: Wear these shorts when you are wrestling! If you play in a Game Pack game, your shorts will change color to match your team (Sorry, currently does the wrong color!).

ssireum shorts - grey.name: Ssireum Shorts - Grey
ssireum shorts - grey.description: Wear these shorts when you are wrestling! If you play in a Game Pack game, your shorts will change color to match your team (Sorry, currently does the wrong color!).

golden air robinsons.name: Golden Air Robinsons
golden air robinsons.description: These sporty shoes are coated with a layer of pure sparkling gold. Sponsored by Kubeti and Rooted.

autumn wings.name: Autumn Wings
autumn wings.description: A leaf falls still on a pond. These wings let you double jump, and contain an endless supply of dried leaves for some reason!

autumn bomb.name: Autumn Bomb
autumn bomb.description: I am become death, the destroyer of foliage, Toss this in the air to celebrate the fall!

balance mooncake.name: Balance Mooncake
balance mooncake.description: This pastry is filled with a sweet bean paste, in 4 flavors combined with a perfect balance. A random jumble of four symbols is imprinted on the top in ancient Growtopian script. Mix this with other Mooncakes in a Laboratory or E-Z Cook Oven to create special Harvest Festival items.

harvester.name: Harvester
harvester.description: This advanced harvesting machine will chop down trees as it runs them over. If you wear a Fuel Pack, it has a 10% chance of harvesting double fruit from each tree below rarity 100! This burns up one Fuel Pack.

sunflower checkpoint.name: Sunflower Checkpoint
sunflower checkpoint.description: If you die, you'll respawn at the last Checkpoint you touched!

moon block.name: Moon Block
moon block.description: With this this block, you can yell to the moon like Buzz Aldrin.

diamond flashaxe.name: Diamond Flashaxe
diamond flashaxe.description: I'm not sure why you're bothering to mine stuff when you already have an entire pickaxe made of diamonds, but at least you know this is harder than whatever you want to mine! Sponsored by Kloe, PartyFrog and xShaDo.

long black bangs.name: Long Black Bangs
long black bangs.description: This is the hair for people with flawed foreheads.

pink pageboy.name: Pink Pageboy
pink pageboy.description: This is NOT a helmet, don't call it a helmet! But if you want to use it as a helmet, go ahead. It's hair though.

long blonde bangs.name: Long Blonde Bangs
long blonde bangs.description: Cover your forehead and shoulders with one fell swoop.

messy auburn tresses.name: Messy Auburn Tresses
messy auburn tresses.description: It's messy and it's red, what more could you want for hair?

growbans.name: Growbans
growbans.description: These are some fierce designer sunglasses!

pink hair bow.name: Pink Hair Bow
pink hair bow.description: You're like Ms. Pac-Man without the eating disorder!

butterfly hair pin.name: Butterfly Hair Pin
butterfly hair pin.description: It looks like a real butterfly! A real robot butterfly.

bee hair pin.name: Bee Hair Pin
bee hair pin.description: Psst, I think there's a bee in your hair...

red sun dress.name: Red Sun Dress
red sun dress.description: It looks like a whole galaxy of suns.

blue skirt.name: Blue Skirt
blue skirt.description: This skirt is long, and thus classy.

checkered dress.name: Checkered Dress
checkered dress.description: You are now the referee of fashion.

cardboard box.name: Cardboard Box
cardboard box.description: The ultimate in stealth technology. Sponsored by JakeShore, ADmex1, and Bankai.

block glue.name: Block Glue
block glue.description: Squirt some of this on a block, and neighboring blocks will attach to it, visually. For example, if you glue a block, and there's a Dirt Block below it, the dirt block won't have a green top, because it will think there's a dirt above it! Use glue again to remove it.

violet protodrake leash.name: Violet Protodrake Leash
violet protodrake leash.description: Congratulations on completing all the holiday achievements! Have a lovely dragon!

hanging guytrap.name: Hanging Guytrap
hanging guytrap.description: This is also what happens when you give a flower a taste for magic bacon!

funhouse mirror.name: Funhouse Mirror
funhouse mirror.description: These mirrors make you look entirely wacky!

ring of force.name: Ring Of Force
ring of force.description: This ring replaces your punch with a devastating blast of energy that can shatter nearby blocks!

ring of winds.name: Ring Of Winds
ring of winds.description: This ring floats you on a cloud. Hold the jump button while falling to glide safely down to earth.

carnival wallpaper.name: Carnival Wallpaper
carnival wallpaper.description: Throw up some of these and you'll feel like you've run away to the circus!

carnival awning.name: Carnival Awning
carnival awning.description: Step right up and see this amazing square-headed person!

carnival block.name: Carnival Block
carnival block.description: Doot doot doo doo doodle doot doot doo doo...

red pennant.name: Red Pennant
red pennant.description: It's just flappin' in the breeze.

blue pennant.name: Blue Pennant
blue pennant.description: It's just flappin' in the breeze.

green pennant.name: Green Pennant
green pennant.description: It's just flappin' in the breeze.

yellow pennant.name: Yellow Pennant
yellow pennant.description: It's just flappin' in the breeze.

lion taming whip.name: Lion Taming Whip
lion taming whip.description: This is a cruel way to get somebody to do what you want. Keep it in video games only!

lion block.name: Lion Block
lion block.description: This lion does tricks! You can stand on its head, you can stick your head near its mouth, it can stand near hoops, it can sit, it can even play dead (it pretends that rigor mortis has set in, so it does so sitting up).

elephant block.name: Elephant Block
elephant block.description: This block never forgets anything, but since it has no method of communicating, that feature is completely useless.

golden ticket.name: Golden Ticket
golden ticket.description: You can spend these at any Carnival game in the world CARNIVAL, if the Carnival happens to be in town.

the ringmaster.name: The Ringmaster
the ringmaster.description: This is the master of all rings! Punch or wrench him to obtain Ring Quests.

golden ticket booth.name: Golden Ticket Booth
golden ticket booth.description: Drop items on this to buy Golden Tickets for 100 rarity worth of anything.

the one ring.name: The One Ring
the one ring.description: This ring is precious, and if you had pocketses you'd put the ring in them for safekeeping.

carnival sign.name: Carnival Sign
carnival sign.description: Write stuff on it to tell your friends! Use your Wrench on it to change the message.

bullseye.name: Bullseye
bullseye.description: Used in the carnival. When turned on, punch it for points.

carnival tent.name: Carnival Tent
carnival tent.description: This is like a regular door, except it won't work if the destination is occupied by another player!

carnival landing.name: Carnival Landing
carnival landing.description: Works the same as path marker.

carnival platform.name: Carnival Platform
carnival platform.description: A nice way to get up to a highwire to perform an aerial show!

card block - back.name: Card Block - Back
card block - back.description: What could be on the other side?

card block - pentagon.name: Card Block - Pentagon
card block - pentagon.description: This card is not so handy for playing games, but it's great for testing psychics.

card block - star.name: Card Block - Star
card block - star.description: This card is not so handy for playing games, but it's great for testing psychics.

card block - sizzle.name: Card Block - Sizzle
card block - sizzle.description: This card is not so handy for playing games, but it's great for testing psychics.

card block - plus.name: Card Block - Plus
card block - plus.description: This card is not so handy for playing games, but it's great for testing psychics.

mirror maze block.name: Mirror Maze Block
mirror maze block.description: Toggle this on to make it passable, not usable by players due to confusion madness.

ringmaster hat.name: Ringmaster Hat
ringmaster hat.description: This top hat is a bit rumpled, but it still has a certain rustic panache.

ringmaster suit.name: Ringmaster Suit
ringmaster suit.description: The classic burgundy suit - the essence of style.

fistful of rings.name: Fistful Of Rings
fistful of rings.description: None of these rings have any magical powers, but there sure are a lot of them!

orbs of elixir.name: Orbs Of Elixir
orbs of elixir.description: These orbs contain a dark elixir said to be the blood of Growganoth... but it's probably just grape juice. Sponsored by Cukuzz and PikaPi.

blazing electro wings.name: Blazing Electro Wings
blazing electro wings.description: It's shocking what they're doing with wings these days. Sponsored by Cukuzz, PikaPi and BigCream.

diamond wings.name: Diamond Wings
diamond wings.description: These things are insanely heavy, I have no idea how you can even walk, let alone jump, with them on. Sponsored by xBone, Paulius, and TheMrSkate.

diamond rocket shoes.name: Diamond Rocket Shoes
diamond rocket shoes.description: Shoes made of diamond? I guess you save money on ice skates. Sponsored by CrimsonSwag, Vitality, and Mitcho25.

calliope.name: Calliope
calliope.description: Get in the carnival mood with some circus music! Yes, circuses and carnivals are different things. But not really? I did some research on it, I'm still not sure.

diamond diaper.name: Diamond Diaper
diamond diaper.description: Well, they're easy to clean! Sponsored by Tiamwatt, Ardims, and Shesherbel.

ice calf leash.name: Ice Calf Leash
ice calf leash.description: Moo. This frosty baby cow will follow you everywhere you go! Mainly because its tied to your wrist. Sponsored by Orfeo and Destra.

electro magnifying glass.name: Electro Magnifying Glass
electro magnifying glass.description: This has over 10,000,000x magnification, allowing you to clearly see the virus that is totally shocking! Sponsored by xSpeedo, Jynttari and PEIJJE.

growley motorcycle.name: Growley Motorcycle
growley motorcycle.description: You look tough when you're riding a Growley Dennison motorcycle!

chaos cursed wand.name: Chaos Cursed Wand
chaos cursed wand.description: Not the same as a Curse Wand. This one sucks the souls out of blocks! Sponsored by LOL, dongju, and MUNGSUNG.

ecto pack.name: Ecto Pack
ecto pack.description: This backpack contains ghostly ectoplasm you can use to power a flamethrower in a spooky way!

haunted chemical.name: Haunted Chemical
haunted chemical.description: Something evil lurks inside this chemical. You get the chills just looking at it.

devilfruit.name: Devilfruit
devilfruit.description: This is evil, like the fru-its of the dev-il! It's recommended that you don't eat it, but it's not like you're going to listen to me.

harvester of sorrows.name: Harvester Of Sorrows
harvester of sorrows.description: This demonic harvesting machine will mangle trees as it runs them over. If you wear a Fuel pack, it has a 10% chance of harvesting double fruit from each tree below rarity 100! This burns one Fuel Pack.

death's scarf.name: Death's Scarf
death's scarf.description: Death has come to retrieve his scarf! He seeks revenge on you for wearing it, waiting behind you for the perfect time to strike. Sponsored by EasyE, Meeps, and Stealthy.

nightmare devil wings.name: Nightmare Devil Wings
nightmare devil wings.description: You don't jump higher than with Devil Wings, but man, you do look pretty scary. Sponsored by Cukuzz, Heme, and Seabreaze.

edvoid's mistake.name: Edvoid's Mistake
edvoid's mistake.description: This makes you look really disturbed. Sponsored by Edvoid20, TETRAFANG and Passed.

nightmare magnifying glass.name: Nightmare Magnifying Glass
nightmare magnifying glass.description: This has over 10,000,000x magnification, allowing you to clearly see a lethal doom virus! Sponsored by Pumuzutup.

teeny tiny skull.name: Teeny Tiny Skull
teeny tiny skull.description: This skull is so small! It would probably take 10 of these to do anything useful.

avenie golden horse.name: Avenie Golden Horse
avenie golden horse.description: This horse is the same thing as a Skeletal Horsie, but has such a shiny coat! Sponsored by Avenie.

claw glove.name: Claw Glove
claw glove.description: They slice, they dice, they chop, they julienne! Just don't pick your nose with them on.

creepy wallpaper.name: Creepy Wallpaper
creepy wallpaper.description: Pro-tip: build a haunted house from Haunted House blocks, then use Block Glue to add this into it, so you don't have to have windows everywhere!

haunted mausoleum.name: Haunted Mausoleum
haunted mausoleum.description: Every so often, a ghost will come spooking out of this place.

gemini ring.name: Gemini Ring
gemini ring.description: This ring is imbued with astrological power. It makes you a twin!

doppelganger potion.name: Doppelganger Potion
doppelganger potion.description: Toss this vile-smelling liquid on an impure soul and the darkest deeds of their past will return to haunt them for a while!

deadly spider.name: Deadly Spider
deadly spider.description: Nature makes things purple to tell you to STAY AWAY! Also if a spider is as big as you, that's another clue.

hanging thread.name: Hanging Thread
hanging thread.description: This is the perfect material for hanging spiders from. It has no effect on Growtopians.

muerto mask.name: Muerto Mask
muerto mask.description: Tired of Halloween? Celebrate Dia De Los Muertos instead!

ring of wisdom.name: Ring of Wisdom
ring of wisdom.description: This ring makes you feel a whole lot smarter. So smart, in fact, that you can tell that it gives you a 10% chance of getting double XP!

skeletal dragon claw.name: Skeletal Dragon Claw
skeletal dragon claw.description: Did you forget to feed your dragon again?

dragon bone.name: Dragon Bone
dragon bone.description: I bet if you had twenty of these, you could build a whole new dragon out of them! Still, it's kind of icky.

golden apple.name: Golden Apple
golden apple.description: This apple is a bit more crunchy than usual, but it's fortified with lots of minerals!

leather jacket.name: Leather Jacket
leather jacket.description: Look cool as you wear this jacket over whatever shirt makes you feel tough.

puffy orange jacket.name: Puffy Orange Jacket
puffy orange jacket.description: Rappers get cold very easily, so this style of jacket is available for them.

twisted spikes.name: Twisted Spikes
twisted spikes.description: The evilest kind of spikes available. Do not touch!

glowy block.name: Glowy Block
glowy block.description: It's like living inside a computer!

dark grey block.name: Dark Grey Block
dark grey block.description: Dark blocks are available in a stunning array of colors!

dark red block.name: Dark Red Block
dark red block.description: Dark blocks are available in a stunning array of colors!

dark orange block.name: Dark Orange Block
dark orange block.description: Dark blocks are available in a stunning array of colors!

dark yellow block.description: Dark blocks are available in a stunning array of colors!

dark aqua block.description: Dark blocks are available in a stunning array of colors!

dark blue block.description: Dark blocks are available in a stunning array of colors!

dark purple block.description: Dark blocks are available in a stunning array of colors!

dark brown block.name: Dark Brown Block
dark brown block.description: Dark blocks are available in a stunning array of colors!

special cultist hood.name: Special Cultist Hood
special cultist hood.description: You look a little shady in this thing...

puddy leash.name: Puddy Leash
puddy leash.description: Mew! This is Puddy, Fredi's kitten! Sponsored by Fredi, Fynx and Ludo.

comet dust.name: Comet Dust
comet dust.description: It seems to whirl around like a tiny galaxy. Perhaps if you collected enough of it, it would merge into a solid mass!

antimatter dust.name: Antimatter Dust
antimatter dust.description: This is the exact opposite of sparkly dust from a passing comet. It seems to whirl backwards like a tiny galaxy. Perhaps if you collected enough of it, it would merge into an astonishingly valuable solid mass!

unearthly chemical.name: Unearthly Chemical
unearthly chemical.description: This is a strange chemical from outer space. It glows with cosmic energy.

comet pants.name: Comet Pants
comet pants.description: These extremely classy pants are emblazoned with the image of comets streaking by.

comet shirt.name: Comet Shirt
comet shirt.description: Express your love for celestial phenomena with this informative T-shirt!

comet beanie.name: Comet Beanie
comet beanie.description: The Night of the Comet never ends for you - there's always a comet soaring above your head! Or boinging anyways.

weather machine - comet.name: Weather Machine - Comet
weather machine - comet.description: Fill your world with the cosmic rays of a comet all month long with this weather machine! Note: this is only a situation of a comet, it does not actually generate any cosmic rays. Good thing too, since that would fry your organs. This sensitive technology will not function when damaged.

riding comet.name: Riding Comet
riding comet.description: You're probably never going to have kids after this, but come on, it's a COMET! That you can ride!

rocket pack.name: Rocket Pack
rocket pack.description: Powered by cosmic energy, this jetpack will notably increase your jump height!

cosmic lenses.name: Cosmic Lenses
cosmic lenses.description: The only glasses certified safe for staring at comets!

cosmic hair.name: Cosmic Hair
cosmic hair.description: What did the cosmic rays do to your head?!

alien block.name: Alien Block
alien block.description: This block is made from elements that don't even occur in our galaxy.

xenoid block.name: Xenoid Block
xenoid block.description: This block is made from elements that don't even occur in our galaxy.

cosmic skirt.name: Cosmic Skirt
cosmic skirt.description: Micrometeors have shredded the bottom end of this skirt, but that is the latest style on Zarkon 9!

riding meteor.name: Riding Meteor
riding meteor.description: You're probably never going to have kids after this, but come on, it's a METEOR! That you can ride!

cosmic unicorn bracelet.name: Cosmic Unicorn Bracelet
cosmic unicorn bracelet.description: This unicorn looks even more Like, whoa man. I'm dreaming a dream of what dreaming is like, and my hands are like, not my hands, man under a blacklight.

space command seat.name: Space Command Seat
space command seat.description: You could take your spaceship from here! If you had a spaceship.

ion conduit.name: Ion Conduit
ion conduit.description: Transfer more power to the warp core!! This is a background block, by the way.

xenonite crystal.name: Xenonite Crystal
xenonite crystal.description: This alien crystal has the power to grant or remove superpowers from all the Growtopians in your world! Use the wrench to set what powers it affects. Only one is allowed per world.

super logo - skull.name: Super Logo - Skull
super logo - skull.description: Emblazon this logo on your super costume to fight crime as Skull Boy? The Boney Avenger? Mrs. Death? It's up to you!

super logo - heart.name: Super Logo - Heart
super logo - heart.description: Emblazon this logo on your super costume to fight crime as Loverboy? Captain Cuddles? Dr. Cupid? It's up to you!

super logo - lightning.name: Super Logo - Lightning
super logo - lightning.description: Emblazon this logo on your super costume to fight crime as Shock-o? The Lightning Kid? Electrina? It's up to you!

super logo - eye.name: Super Logo - Eye
super logo - eye.description: Emblazon this logo on your super costume to fight crime as Oculus? Lookey-Loo? The Illuminati? It's up to you!

super logo - echo.name: Super Logo - Echo
super logo - echo.description: Emblazon this logo on your super costume to fight crime as Well, okay I don't even know what this logo is. So you can be anybody you want with this one! It's up to you!

geiger counter.name: Geiger Counter
geiger counter.description: With this handy device, you can detect radiation. As you get closer to the source, the device will ping red, then yellow, then green for the closest. Stand still where you think the source is and you just might find it!

radioactive chemical.name: Radioactive Chemical
radioactive chemical.description: This is a dangerous chemical that emits radiation. You probably shouldn't keep it in your pants pocket.

phone booth.name: Phone Booth
phone booth.description: Hop inside with a punch to swap your entire outfit with the outfit stored inside. Presto-Change-o! You can use your Wrench to empty it out as well.

action hero stubble.name: Action Hero Stubble
action hero stubble.description: Nothing says tough like not bothering with basic hygiene.

ice horse.name: Ice Horse
ice horse.description: You're probably gonna wish you had spent extra for the seat heater option with this particular ride. But it's faster than walking. Sponsored by @Aimster.

edvoid's fire-nado.name: Edvoid's Fire-Nado
edvoid's fire-nado.description: Stay warm this winter by setting your pants on fire! You liar. Sponsored by Edvoid20, NewRay, and Heme.

mighty snow rod.name: Mighty Snow Rod
mighty snow rod.description: Gloves are highly recommended while holding this mystical artifact. Sponsored by iiStyloMilo, Bambam46, and MartinMan007's subscribers.

tiny tank.name: Tiny Tank
tiny tank.description: Why don't you just play Tanked instead? Sponsored by Liammagoo, Nelsonmandel and Krampus.

reindeer bell.name: Reindeer Bell
reindeer bell.description: This is a perfectly ordinary animal, not anything related to flying, magic, or gifts. There are, however, only 1500 of this endangered animal in existence!

magic reindeer bell.name: Magic Reindeer Bell
magic reindeer bell.description: This guy has been sorely depressed ever since he got banned from gaming. Take him out on a flight to cheer him up!

icicles.name: Icicles
icicles.description: As ice thaws, it drips down and refreezes into these razor sharp blades of agony.

siberian tiger block.name: Siberian Tiger Block
siberian tiger block.description: It's so cold in Siberia that this tiger is frozen solid.

candy cane platform.name: Candy Cane Platform
candy cane platform.description: This is one sweet way to hold yourself aloft.

yeti hat.name: Yeti Hat
yeti hat.description: What you think yetis don't have ram horns? Prove it.

holiday cheer bomb.name: Holiday Cheer Bomb
holiday cheer bomb.description: Nothing speaks of peace, love, and joy more than a bomb. Throw it at your friends!

carnival pipe.name: Carnival Pipe
carnival pipe.description: This is the most festive way to get water around your house.

winter flu vaccine.name: Winter Flu Vaccine
winter flu vaccine.description: It's really safest to use killed virii in vaccines, but come on, who would kill this cuddly guy?

red crystal.name: Red Crystal
red crystal.description: This crystal is not yet in balance. Perhaps if you place it in the bosom of its Earth Mother, and then join it with 4 other crystals, it can achieve harmony.

green crystal.name: Green Crystal
green crystal.description: This crystal is not yet in balance. Perhaps if you place it in the bosom of its Earth Mother, and then join it with 4 other crystals, it can achieve harmony.

blue crystal.description: This crystal is not yet in balance. Perhaps if you place it in the bosom of its Earth Mother, and then join it with 4 other crystals, it can achieve harmony.

black crystal.name: Black Crystal
black crystal.description: This crystal is not yet in balance. Perhaps if you place it in the bosom of its Earth Mother, and then join it with 4 other crystals, it can achieve harmony.

crystal clock.name: Crystal Clock
crystal clock.description: Tell time in Growtopia! This clock displays the current Growtopia time for you.

red crystal wings.name: Red Crystal Wings
red crystal wings.description: These amazing lightweight hollow crystals actually allow you to jump in mid-air!

blue crystal wings.name: Blue Crystal Wings
blue crystal wings.description: These amazing lightweight hollow crystals actually allow you to jump in mid-air!

green crystal wings.name: Green Crystal Wings
green crystal wings.description: These amazing lightweight hollow crystals actually allow you to jump in mid-air!

purple crystal wings.name: Purple Crystal Wings
purple crystal wings.description: These amazing lightweight hollow crystals actually allow you to jump in mid-air!

golden crystal wings.name: Golden Crystal Wings
golden crystal wings.description: These amazing lightweight hollow crystals actually allow you to jump in mid-air!

aqua crystal wings.name: Aqua Crystal Wings
aqua crystal wings.description: These amazing lightweight hollow crystals actually allow you to jump in mid-air!

crystal glaive.name: Crystal Glaive
crystal glaive.description: Careful of the pointy bits. This thing is tough to hold, but look how cool it is when you throw it!

crystal skull.name: Crystal Skull
crystal skull.description: You could run your own kingdom with a mask like this!

crystal tree.name: Crystal Tree
crystal tree.description: Everyone knows crystals don't grow on trees, so this is just a lovely decorative element.

crystal gate.name: Crystal Gate
crystal gate.description: These magical doors connect all the worlds in Growtopia. Place one and then use your Wrench on it to set the destination.

crystal spikes.name: Crystal Spikes
crystal spikes.description: These crystals have fragmented into razor sharp points. Do not touch!

mini-you.name: Mini-You
mini-you.description: This Mini Growtopian looks strangely familiar...

party block.name: Party Block
party block.description: You can't have a block party without a Party Block!

party boombox.name: Party Boombox
party boombox.description: Rock some tunes to really kick the party into gear.

weather machine - party.name: Weather Machine - Party
weather machine - party.description: Bring the party with you everywhere you go! This sensitive technology will not function while damaged.

dead geiger counter.name: Dead Geiger Counter
dead geiger counter.description: This Geiger Counter is out of battery power. It will charge up from the static electricity you generate by moving around, so just hold it in your hand until it's charged. You'd think they would have added a wall plug too, but they didn't!

party confetti.name: Party Confetti
party confetti.description: Ohh, it's gonna take a LOT of this to get the party started...

party tunes.name: Party Tunes
party tunes.description: 3 notes? Pop songs just keep getting shorter! Maybe if we collect up a pile of these, we can get this party started!

superpower - heat vision.name: Superpower - Heat Vision
superpower - heat vision.description: This is a Fire Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: Inflict 1 damage.

superpower - incinerate.name: Superpower - Incinerate
superpower - incinerate.description: This is a Fire Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: Inflict 1 damage, but if opponent uses a Muscle power, it inflicts 2 damage.

superpower - flame on!.name: Superpower - Flame On!
superpower - flame on!.description: This is a Fire Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: Ignite yourself, healing 1 damage, and your opponent takes 1 damage if they hit you in the next 3 turns.

superpower - liquify.name: Superpower - Liquify
superpower - liquify.description: This is a Fire Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: Inflicts 1 damage and melts the card your opponent plays, removing it from play permanently. If you Liquify another card, the first one returns.

superpower - overheat.name: Superpower - Overheat
superpower - overheat.description: This is a Fire Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: Your Fire cards are not countered by Ice on your next turn, and they do +1 damage.

crime in progress.name: Crime In Progress
crime in progress.description: Oh no! A villainous scalliwag lurks here, perpetrating CRIME on an unsuspecting populace! Smack him in the face to set him straight with your superpowers.

superpower - death ray.name: Superpower - Death Ray
superpower - death ray.description: This is a Rare Fire Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: Obliterates your opponent for 3 damage.

party-in-a-box.name: Party-In-A-Box
party-in-a-box.description: You can just barely hear techno music deep inside the box. Maybe you should open it and see if a party comes out?

superpower - ice shards.name: Superpower - Ice Shards
superpower - ice shards.description: This is an Ice Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: Inflict 1 damage.

superpower - frost breath.name: Superpower - Frost Breath
superpower - frost breath.description: This is an Ice Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: Freeze your opponent, so they can't use any cards except Fire cards next turn.

superpower - ice barrier.name: Superpower - Ice Barrier
superpower - ice barrier.description: This is an Ice Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: Protects you from the next hit you would take, including this turn. Lightning pierces it.

superpower - puddle.name: Superpower - Puddle
superpower - puddle.description: This is an Ice Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: For the next 3 turns, the opponent takes 1 damage if they use Lightning. They shouldn't do that standing in water!

superpower - frozen mirror.name: Superpower - Frozen Mirror
superpower - frozen mirror.description: This is an Ice Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: Inflict 1 damage. If the opponent uses Fire, their card isn't countered, it's reflected back at them!

superpower - ban hammer.name: Superpower - Ban Hammer
superpower - ban hammer.description: This is a Rare Ice Superpower Card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: Give the opponent a warning on their 3rd warning they get banned from the game.

superpower - super strength.name: Superpower - Super Strength
superpower - super strength.description: This is a Muscle Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: Inflict 1 damage.

superpower - super speed.name: Superpower - Super Speed
superpower - super speed.description: This is a Muscle Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: Inflict 1 damage, and on the next turn, you see which card your opponent will choose before you choose yours. This card takes 2 turns to recharge.

superpower - enrage.name: Superpower - Enrage
superpower - enrage.description: This is a Muscle Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: Block 1 damage, this turn, and your next attack that hits will do +1 damage.

superpower - crush.name: Superpower - Crush
superpower - crush.description: This is a Muscle Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: If your opponent uses Lightning this turn, they take *3* damage! Sadly if they don't this has no effect at all.

superpower - regeneration.name: Superpower - Regeneration
superpower - regeneration.description: This is a Muscle Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: Recover 1 Life this turn and the next turn.

superpower - g-virus.name: Superpower - g-Virus
superpower - g-virus.description: This is a Rare Muscle Superpower Card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: Summon a zombie to gnaw on your opponent for 1 damage per turn, forever. Each point of damage you take kills a zombie instead of hurting you.

superpower - shocking fist.name: Superpower - Shocking Fist
superpower - shocking fist.description: This is a Lightning Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: Inflict 1 damage.

superpower - thunderstorm.name: Superpower - Thunderstorm
superpower - thunderstorm.description: This is a Lightning Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: No damage now, but for the next 2 turns, your opponent takes 1 damage each turn. If you take damage from a Muscle card, the storm ends.

superpower - overcharge.name: Superpower - Overcharge
superpower - overcharge.description: This is a Lightning Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: Charge up your Lightning cards to do +1 damage permanently. Getting hit by Muscle cards removes this effect.

superpower - megawatt pulse.name: Superpower - Megawatt Pulse
superpower - megawatt pulse.description: This is a Lightning Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: Does 2 damage, but takes 2 turns to recharge.

superpower - resuscitate.name: Superpower - Resuscitate
superpower - resuscitate.description: This is a Lightning Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: If an attack would kill you in the next 3 turns, you recover with 1 Life.

superpower - duct tape.name: Superpower - Duct Tape
superpower - duct tape.description: This is a Rare Lightning Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: Prevent your opponent from using the element they used this turn for 3 turns.

villain portrait - the firebug.name: Villain Portrait - The Firebug

super logo - z.description: This is the logo of the supervillain (or philanthropist) Z. Everett Koop. Are you sure you want to wear it?

super logo - yerfdog.description: This is the logo of the supervillain Devil Ham. Or it's just the logo of Hamumu Games. Are you sure you want to wear it?

super logo - d.description: This is the logo of the supervillain Dr. Destructo. Or at least it's his first initial. His name's Dennis. Are you sure you want to wear it?

henchman.name: Henchman
henchman.description: Looks like you captured one of that villain's henchmen Of course, you COULD let him loose somewhere to cause a little havoc! Note: Henchmen take 24 hours to complete their crime, then they disappear!

crime wave.name: Crime Wave
crime wave.description: Good heavens, where'd you find such an unsavoury bunch of miscreants?! I suppose you could let them loose in your world to commit crimes. If you were EVIL. Note: They take 24 hours to complete their crime, after which they disappear!

heavenly scythe.name: Heavenly Scythe
heavenly scythe.description: This scythe contains the fury of the heavens! Sponsored by Edvoid20, iKrideez, and Anfinity.

heartbreaker hammer.name: Heartbreaker Hammer
heartbreaker hammer.description: Seriously, if this hits your chest, your heart will break. Also, it's good for smashing pumpkins.

teeny angel wings.name: Teeny Angel Wings
teeny angel wings.description: Even as tiny as they are, these wings allow you to jump in mid-air!

teeny golden wings.name: Teeny Golden Wings
teeny golden wings.description: Even as tiny as they are, these wings will allow you to jump in mid-air!

valensign.name: Valensign
valensign.description: Write Messages to your loved ones on it!

locke the salesman.name: Locke The Salesman
locke the salesman.description: This guy loves locks. He'll trade you fabulous items for them!

lucky horseshoe.name: Lucky Horseshoe
lucky horseshoe.description: Lucky you! You've been awarded this golden horseshoe by the Leprechaun's Guild in honor of your Blarney achievements. Of course, one horseshoe isn't much good. Why don't you get four of them together and shoe a horse? (Note: horse not actually required, just get 4 horseshoes and tap them anywhere)

irish sport horsie.name: Irish Sport Horsie
irish sport horsie.description: The Irish Sport Horsie is traditionally used for all purposes from transportation to riding to working the land, and it is so popular as a competition riding horsie. It also wears a silly hat.

kilt.name: Kilt
kilt.description: Wait a minute, this is Scottish.

corncob pipe.name: Corncob Pipe
corncob pipe.description: This is a bad habit, you should stop it.

emerald lock.name: Emerald Lock
emerald lock.description: Locks an entire world. And looks blarney good doing it. Now, this lock is no Lucky Clover, but you just might feel a little luckier in a world locked by it...

emerald shard.name: Emerald Shard
emerald shard.description: Watch out, this is a really sharp fragment of Emerald. It seems strangely magnetic attracted to other shards like it. Maybe if you got 200 of them together, they'd fuse into something! Yeah, that's how reality works!

cloverleaf.name: Cloverleaf
cloverleaf.description: This is only one leaf of a clover! Clearly you need four of them if you want to be lucky.

shamrock sign.name: Shamrock Sign
shamrock sign.description: Write stuff on it to tell your friends! Use the Wrench on it to change the message.

slimy green hair.name: Slimy Green Hair
slimy green hair.description: Wanna be a witch but tired of hat-head? This is the hairstyle for you.

possessed witch hat.name: Possessed Witch Hat
possessed witch hat.description: I think Chudy's brain is being eaten right now.

super logo - mightyboosh.name: Super Logo - MightyBOOSH
super logo - mightyboosh.description: Emblazon this logo on your super costume to fight crime as MIGHTYBOOSH, with his trademark lightning shield!

super shirt - emerald.description: Fight crime in this mighty Irish leotard!

muscle shirt - emerald.description: Flex your muscles in this mighty Irish leotard!

heroic tights - emerald.name: Heroic Tights - Emerald
heroic tights - emerald.description: To be an Irish superhero, you really need to wear tights of some sort.

super tights - emerald.description: To be an Irish superhero, you really need to wear tights of some sort.

super logo - shamrock.description: Emblazon this logo on your super costume to fight crime as... Saint Patrick? O'Superman? Lucky Lass? It's up to you!

superpower - lucky shot.description: This is a Rare Muscle Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: Take a chance! This card's element when played is totally random, and it will inflict from 0-4 damage!

egg-hunting basket.description: With this basket, you can track down Easter Eggs hidden all around Growtopia! Once your basket is full, it somehow takes you half an hour to get the egg out of it. Clumsy. Easter Eggs can only be found during Easter Week.

full egg-hunting basket.name: Full Egg-Hunting Basket
full egg-hunting basket.description: You found an egg and dropped it in this basket! Now it's buried under all the fake grass. Keep digging at it, you'll re-find it eventually.

egghead.name: Egghead
egghead.description: This hat always cracks me up.

carnival spikeball.name: Carnival Spikeball
carnival spikeball.description: There's always fun times at the carnival, even when your organs are being impaled on steel spikes.

carny vest.name: Carny Vest
carny vest.description: Step right up! Sell popcorn and candy to rubes as you run nigh-unwinnable games!

flame scythe.name: Flame Scythe
flame scythe.description: The flame represents all of the fallen heroes that served in the Armed Forces. Sponsored by iFlySolo and GhostEgo.

ride'o'gold.name: Ride'O'Gold
ride'o'gold.description: A lot of people bling out their cars to show their wealth, but it just seems easier to ride around in a bucket of gold to start with, right?

ginger hair bun.name: Ginger Hair Bun
ginger hair bun.description: Tie up those unruly red locks.

change of address.name: Change of Address
change of address.description: If you own two worlds, you can use this handy form to swap their names permanently. See a new name you want that nobody wants? Lock it up, and do a name swap! Requires a World Lock in both worlds.

teddy bear.name: Teddy Bear
teddy bear.description: You can't go off punching, building, and growing without Mr. Blinky!

muddy pants.name: Muddy Pants
muddy pants.description: Where have you been playing?! What did you do to these? I just washed them! And wait a minute, what is that following you around!?!? Sponsored by @Hamumu since nobody else had the guts.

holographic sign.name: Holographic Sign
holographic sign.description: Program messages into it to tell your friends! Use your Wrench on it to change the message.

sassy boots.name: Sassy Boots
sassy boots.description: It's not possible to be any sassier than somebody wearing this boots. So put 'em on and get SASSY, Girlfriend!

shifty block.name: Shifty Block
shifty block.description: This block constantly shifts through the colors of the rainbow. It's mesmerizing.

legendary katana.name: Legendary Katana
legendary katana.description: This legendary blade was said to have sliced through 3 tomatoes AND a tin can during the course of a single informercial! Nobody knows if that's really true, but it's certainly a big sword.

unlucky pinata hat.name: Unlucky Pinata Hat
unlucky pinata hat.description: This hat is still festive and suitable for formal occasions, but all the luck has been sucked out of it.

nacho block.name: Nacho Block
nacho block.description: Mmm nachos. Watch out, that cheese is slippery.

fashion purse - pink.name: Fashion Purse - Pink
fashion purse - pink.description: You can store all your stuff in here - dirt, toilets, cows, devil wings, whatever a girl needs.

fashion purse - green.name: Fashion Purse - Green
fashion purse - green.description: You can store all your stuff in here - dirt, toilets, cows, devil wings, whatever a girl needs.

fashion purse - purple.name: Fashion Purse - Purple
fashion purse - purple.description: You can store all your stuff in here - dirt, toilets, cows, devil wings, whatever a girl needs.

fashion purse - yellow.name: Fashion Purse - Yellow
fashion purse - yellow.description: You can store all your stuff in here - dirt, toilets, cows, devil wings, whatever a girl needs.

purse dog.name: Purse Dog
purse dog.description: You can't store all your stuff in here - there's already a dog inside!

makeup.name: Makeup
makeup.description: Slap on a little lipstick and eyeshadow before you hit the town tonight!

kansas pigtails.name: Kansas Pigtails
kansas pigtails.description: This strange two-toned hair is all the fashion rage in Growtopia. I don't know why, but by popular demand, here it is!

mickeymay leash.name: MickeyMay Leash
mickeymay leash.description: Mickey and May are Werkon and Compulsory's real life puppies! This puppy represents them both. Sponsored by Werkon and Compulsory.

gold choker.name: Gold Choker
gold choker.description: Be careful with this necklace, they don't call it a choker for nothing.

emerald choker.name: Emerald Choker
emerald choker.description: Be careful with this necklace, they don't call it a choker for nothing. Now with a giant emerald!

jade block.name: Jade Block
jade block.description: This is a finely carved block of jade. How much more elegant could you get?

filigreed jade block.name: Filigreed Jade Block
filigreed jade block.description: This jade block is inlaid with a delicate gold filigree. How much more elegant could you get?

draped filigreed jade block.name: Draped Filigreed Jade Block
draped filigreed jade block.description: Now there's pink silk draped on top. How much more elegant could you get?

diamond-encrusted draped filigreed jade.name: Diamond-Encrusted Draped Filigreed Jade Block
diamond-encrusted draped filigreed jade.description: Okay, covering the block with diamonds has to be the height of elegance.

googly-eyed diamond-encrusted draped fil.name: Googly-Eyed Diamond-Encrusted Draped Filigreed Jade Block
googly-eyed diamond-encrusted draped fil.description: Yep. You just went a step too far. This is not elegant.

platinum blonde hair.name: Platinum Blonde Hair
platinum blonde hair.description: On average, blondes tend to have more fun, but live 20% shorter lives. That sounds like science, but luckily it's not!

electric bow.name: Electric Bow
electric bow.description: This crossbow is mounted to a glove, so nobody can steal it from you. It shoots electric bolts! Why not? Sponsored by iNoodles.

golden aura.name: Golden Aura
golden aura.description: You are burning with furious energy! And double-jump power. Sponsored by Palestinian, Signle, and StardusJr.

basic blue block.name: Basic Blue Block
basic blue block.description: This is a block. It is blue.

superpower - pineapple spear.name: Superpower - Pineapple Spear
superpower - pineapple spear.description: This is a Rare Lightning Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Card effect: Impale your opponent for 3 damage. This exhausts you for a turn, but you can use a Lightning card to get a second wind. Even if countered, the spear still does 1 damage!

villain portrait - pine-fresh.name: Villain Portrait - Pine-Fresh
villain portrait - pine-fresh.description: Just before knocking him unconscious, you snapped a pine-fresh photo of Pine-Fresh for posterity. Put it up on the wall, show off your achievement!

pineapple air freshener.name: Pineapple Air Freshener
pineapple air freshener.description: This brings a fresh pine(apple) scent to the area.....a dangerous scent.

pineapple block.name: Pineapple Block
pineapple block.description: By growing pineapples inside cubical molds, they can be forced to grow in a block shape! There's no real reason to do this, but it is fun.

pineapple.name: Pineapple
pineapple.description: Yummy, it's a pineapple! You should just keep eating these nonstop!

pineapple head.name: Pineapple Head
pineapple head.description: Here's a useful tip; if you find a pineapple big enough, you can hollow it out and jam it on your head! Wait a minute, that's not useful at all.

fruity hat.name: Fruity Hat
fruity hat.description: Similar to the classic Beer Hat, this hat presents you with a movable fest! You'll never go hungry with this on. Note: fruit is made with wax.

hawaiian shirt.name: Hawaiian Shirt
hawaiian shirt.description: The stylish classic is adorned with pineapples and tropical flowers. Suitable for any pineapple occasion.

pineapple pants.name: Pineapple Pants
pineapple pants.description: Though hard to distinguish from Clay Brick Pants by appearance, the key here is soft, squishy, and juicy lining, Yeah, they're kinda gross to wear.

weather machine - pineapples.name: Weather Machine - Pineapples
weather machine - pineapples.description: It is rare, but sometimes you'll see the little pineapple alert on your weather app. When you do, be sure to get undercover - an umbrella is not going to protect you! This sensitive technology will not function while damaged.

sugarloaf pineapple block.name: Sugarloaf Pineapple Block
sugarloaf pineapple block.description: This block is sweeter than a normal Pineapple Block. Since you can't eat Pineapple Blocks, that doesn't matter much.

roasted pineapple block.name: Roasted Pineapple Block
roasted pineapple block.description: Be careful, this came out of the oven piping hot!

frozen pineapple block.name: Frozen Pineapple Block
frozen pineapple block.description: The problem with frozen pineapple is it gets mushy when it thaws. So this one has a built-in liquid nitrogen tank to keep it from ever thawing!

pineapple launcher.name: Pineapple Launcher
pineapple launcher.description: This pistol provides the power to pelt people with perilously pointy pineapples.

demonic arm.name: Demonic Arm
demonic arm.description: It got into your arm and it went bad, so you have to lap it off at the shoulder. Sponsored by Edvoid20, SpamG and CrimsonSwag.

the gungnir.name: The Gungnir
the gungnir.description: The legendary spear of Odin is yours! Sponsored by ZeroRarity, CoffeeGuy, and xAzureHKF.

pineapple juice.name: Pineapple Juice
pineapple juice.description: This backpack contains pineapple juice you can use to power a flamethrower or Harvester!

pineapple earrings.name: Pineapple Earrings
pineapple earrings.description: A bit of tropics hanging from your earlobes.

pineapple kite.name: Pineapple Kite
pineapple kite.description: Fly this colorful kite to celebrate your love of pineapples!

super shirt - pineapple.name: Super Shirt - Pineapple
super shirt - pineapple.description: Fight crime in this mighty tropical leotard!

muscle shirt - pineapple.name: Muscle Shirt - Pineapple
muscle shirt - pineapple.description: Flex your muscles in this mighty tropical leotard!

heroic tights - pineapple.name: Heroic Tights - Pineapple
heroic tights - pineapple.description: To be a tropical superhero, you really need to wear tights of some sort.

super tights - pineapple.name: Super Tights - Pineapple
super tights - pineapple.description: To be a tropical superhero, you really need to wear tights of some sort.

heroic boots - pineapple.name: Heroic Boots - Pineapple
heroic boots - pineapple.description: These tropical boots add nothing to your crimefighting skills except to protect you from stray Legos.

super cape - pineapple.name: Super Cape - Pineapple
super cape - pineapple.description: You're no Heroman, but still, it's pretty swell.

superheroine top - pineapple.name: Superheroine Top - Pineapple
superheroine top - pineapple.description: Flex your muscles in this mighty tropical leotard!

super eye mask - pineapple.name: Super Eye Mask - Pineapple
super eye mask - pineapple.description: Protect you secret identity by hiding the inch of skin around your eyes. Who could possibly recognize you?

super logo - pineapple.name: Super Logo - Pineapple
super logo - pineapple.description: Emblazon this logo on your super costume to fight crime as... Power Pineapple? Tropicanus? Dr. Pineapple? It's up to you!

viney block.name: Viney Block
viney block.description: It may seem obvious, but I'll say it anyway: this block is viney.

viney wallpaper.name: Viney Wallpaper
viney wallpaper.description: It's like you're lost in the jungle!

leaf block.name: Leaf Block
leaf block.description: If you don't like it, you can make like this block and leaf.

mission block.name: Mission Block
mission block.description: Mission style is a design that emphasizes simple horizontal and vertical lines and flat panels that accentuate the grain of the wood (often oak, especially quartersawn oak).

air conditioner.name: Air Conditioner
air conditioner.description: Keep cool! It's hot out there.

air duct.name: Air Duct
air duct.description: Sneak around in these to find the secret documents. Nobody knows why they build them human-sized!

well.name: Well
well.description: Dip a bucket in! You can collect one bucket of water from here everyday.

penguin leash.name: Penguin Leash
penguin leash.description: Waddle waddle. Sponsored by TypoPig and IcyMeltz.

poseidon's trident.name: Poseidon's Trident
poseidon's trident.description: This trident has been blessed by Poseidon, God of the seas. The glowy blue signifies all of the servants who served under Poseidon in his battles. What Poseidon left along with this trident is unknown - that's for you to figure out. Sponsored by mythicdawn and angel42.

green stuff.name: Green Stuff
green stuff.description: Hmm, Green stuff. What IS this stuff?

blue stuff.name: Blue Stuff
blue stuff.description: Now stuff comes in blue too! It's a veritable rainbow of stuff.

texas limestone.name: Texas Limestone
