texas limestone.description: In Texas, when you build a house, you just take all the rocks you end up digging up and slap them on the walls. It looks nice.

air vent.name: Air Vent
air vent.description: How else are you going to get into the air ducts?

sapphire block.name: Sapphire Block
sapphire block.description: Flawlessly cut by out master gemologists, enjoy this transcendent jewel, an heirloom to last a lifetime.

number block 0.name: Number Block 0
number block 0.description: It's a number on a block! YAY!

number block 1.name: Number Block 1
number block 1.description: It's a number on a block! YAY!

number block 2.name: Number Block 2
number block 2.description: It's a number on a block! YAY!

number block 3.name: Number Block 3
number block 3.description: It's a number on a block! YAY!

number block 4.name: Number Block 4
number block 4.description: It's a number on a block! YAY!

number block 5.name: Number Block 5
number block 5.description: It's a number on a block! YAY!

number block 6.name: Number Block 6
number block 6.description: It's a number on a block! YAY!

number block 7.name: Number Block 7
number block 7.description: It's a number on a block! YAY!

number block 8.name: Number Block 8
number block 8.description: It's a number on a block! YAY!

number block 9.name: Number Block 9
number block 9.description: It's a number on a block! YAY!

number 0.name: Number 0
number 0.description: It's a number floating in the sky! YAY!

number 1.name: Number 1
number 1.description: It's a number floating in the sky! YAY!

number 2.name: Number 2
number 2.description: It's a number floating in the sky! YAY!

number 3.name: Number 3
number 3.description: It's a number floating in the sky! YAY!

number 4.name: Number 4
number 4.description: It's a number floating in the sky! YAY!

number 5.name: Number 5
number 5.description: It's a number floating in the sky! YAY!

number 6.name: Number 6
number 6.description: It's a number floating in the sky! YAY!

number 7.name: Number 7
number 7.description: It's a number floating in the sky! YAY!

number 8.name: Number 8
number 8.description: It's a number floating in the sky! YAY!

number 9.name: Number 9
number 9.description: It's a number floating in the sky! YAY!

phoenix pacifier.name: Phoenix Pacifier
phoenix pacifier.description: Aww, so cute you just wanna snuggle him all day! But you should really pace yourself on that, with a trip to the burn ward in between each snuggle. No more than 500 of these little guys exist in all of Growtopia.

sun block.name: Sun Block
sun block.description: Don't rub this on your face.

tiki torch.name: Tiki Torch
tiki torch.description: How you feelin'? Hot hot hot? Well, you can punch this to turn it on or off.

cow skull.name: Cow Skull
cow skull.description: This bovine has moooved on to greener pastures.

flamingo.name: Flamingo
flamingo.description: This bird's got legs that go allll the way up.

summer breeze.name: Summer Breeze
summer breeze.description: These gentle breezes like freshly mown grass. They also blow with great ferocity!

wizard's staff.name: Wizard's Staff
wizard's staff.description: Congratulations on solving the Wizard's Riddle (or just googling what somebody else figured out). Since you're not legendary enough to obtain an actual Legendary Item, here's a replica of the great Wizard's Staff. (Be careful, the winds might hurt you.) Sponsored by Devinn and PonyGarYelow.

white fury.name: White Fury
white fury.description: This thoroughbred steed is burning with furious power. Sponsored by Hercule, PRONGS and HERMIUS.

seafoam beard.name: Seafoam Beard
seafoam beard.description: You're looking a little green around the gills.

seafoam hair.name: Seafoam Hair
seafoam hair.description: You've got that windblown chlorinated surfer look. It either makes you cool or a filthy beach bum. It's a fine line.

oceanic crown.name: Oceanic Crown
oceanic crown.description: You are the KING OF THE SEAS!... It's whats written on the tag of this cheap plastic knock-off.

blyoshi's free dirt.name: BLYoshi's Free Dirt
blyoshi's free dirt.description: It's an unlimited supply of free dirt blocks! Unfortunately, it spews them at high velocity so they splatter at impact. Sponsored by BLYoshi.

fc cleats.name: FC Cleats
fc cleats.description: Every pair of cleats comes with a new high-tech soccer ball capable of returning to you automatically! These cleats come from Funtimes College, the #1 party school on Earth. Sponsored by the admins of FC.

man u cleats.name: Man U Cleats
man u cleats.description: Every pair of cleats comes with a new high-tech soccer ball capable of returning to you automatically! These cleats come from Man University, the school for manly men of masculinity.

fc jersey.name: FC Jersey
fc jersey.description: Represent Funtimes College in this stylish jersey! PARTY ON!

man u jersey.name: Man U Jersey
man u jersey.description: Represent Man University in this stylish jersey! Hallelujah, it's rainin' men! Notice of non-descrimination: Man University does not discriminate on the basis of gender identity, unless you're not a man. HOO HOO HOO MAN U!

baseball glove.name: Baseball Glove
baseball glove.description: Hidden inside this glove is a wormhole to a dimension filled with nothing but baseballs. Baseballs and popcorn Shrimp. But the wormhole's at the baseball end of the dimension.

pigskin.name: Pigskin
pigskin.description: Don't worry, this isn't actually the skin of a pig. It's plastic. It's an American football! Also known as a hand-egg. Throw it to somebody!

stadium.name: Stadium
stadium.description: Nobody showed up for the big game!

crowded stadium.name: Crowded Stadium
crowded stadium.description: Everybody showed up for the big game!

basketball hoop.name: Basketball Hoop
basketball hoop.description: Dunk it!! The more of these you stack up, the better the challenge.

monkey on your back.name: Monkey On Your Back
monkey on your back.description: This is not a metaphor. Sponsored by SweGamerHD' subscribers, Kizashi, and Inforced.

football helmet.name: Football Helmet
football helmet.description: Keep in mind that while headgear is necessary for dangerous sports, it doesn't eliminate brain damage. Keep your brain safe - play Growtopia instead.

growies cap.name: Growies Cap
growies cap.description: Show your pride in the Growtopia Growies with their cap! Root for the home team!

tennis racquet.name: Tennis Racquet
tennis racquet.description: Serve up an ace! Lifetime subscription to Rapidly Biodegradable Tennis Ball Supply is included.

carrot sword.name: Carrot Sword
carrot sword.description: This carrot is rather sharp. I wouldn't recommend eating it, especially if it's a sword or if you're a bunny. Sponsored by MrMehMeh.

emerald staff.name: Emerald Staff
emerald staff.description: The Orb Of Ajanti is mounted atop this staff, held by a silver hand - just make sure you never touch it with your human hand, or you will be incinerated. Sponsored by Deliberate, COMBUSTION, and jason747.

fishing rod.name: Fishing Rod
fishing rod.description: Equip this and then use bait on water next to you to go fishing! All you have to do is wait for a bite, and then punch the fish before it escapes! If you miss, your bait is wasted, so punch fast.

wiggly worm.name: Wiggly Worm
wiggly worm.description: This is bait for fishing. Equip a fishing rod and then use this bait on water that you are standing next to in order to start fishing. Wiggly Worms can only catch the smallest fish.

shifting scroll.name: Shifting Scroll
shifting scroll.description: Strange letters swirl about on this scroll. It seems to shimmer before your eyes." The only think you can make out consistently is "18.IT", whatever that means.

cryptic scroll.name: Cryptic Scroll
cryptic scroll.description: Incomprehensible words scrawl across this parchment: SNWISS CAGITE TET PLDOL

really cryptic scroll.name: Really Cryptic Scroll
really cryptic scroll.description: Incomprehensible words scrawl across this parchment: EG TAC DESLI UREN HAI IB

exceedingly cryptic scroll.name: Exceedingly Cryptic Scroll
exceedingly cryptic scroll.description: Incomprehensible words scrawl across this parchment: VROMO AOI ELN WREAR NSA

needlessly cryptic scroll.name: Needlessly Cryptic Scroll
needlessly cryptic scroll.description: Incomprehensible words scrawl across this parchment: PAT NNN TED A BASK GCL

smarty pants.name: Smarty Pants
smarty pants.description: These pants are colorful and tasty! But they do not enhance intelligence in any way.

camo pants.name: Camo Pants
camo pants.description: Put these pants on and people will think you're just a floating torso! With some shoes underneath.

carrot pants.name: Carrot Pants
carrot pants.description: It's the latest fashion! I guess...

golf pants.name: Golf Pants
golf pants.description: It's a mystery as to why golfers have to wear ugly pants, but they really do. Have some!

acid-washed skinny jeans.name: Acid-Washed Skinny Jeans
acid-washed skinny jeans.description: You need skinny legs to put in the skinny jeans, or perhaps just let the acid slim you down a bit.

tiny red skirt.name: Tiny Red Skirt
tiny red skirt.description: YOUNG LADY, you are NOT going out in that skirt. In my day, people couldn't even see our ankles.

flower sarong.name: Flower Sarong
flower sarong.description: This delicate flower print works both as a swimsuit cover-up, or an elegant skirt for a night on the town.

purple crystal skirt.name: Purple Crystal Skirt
purple crystal skirt.description: As long as you don't mind clinking as you walk around, this is a beautifully sparkly style.

golden crystal skirt.name: Golden Crystal Skirt
golden crystal skirt.description: As long as you don't mind clinking as you walk around, this is a beautifully sparkly style.

aqua crystal skirt.name: Aqua Crystal Skirt
aqua crystal skirt.description: As long as you don't mind clinking as you walk around, this is a beautifully sparkly style.

display block.name: Display Block
display block.description: Use nearly any item on this block to store it inside on display. Destroying the block will spit out the item, or you can wrench the block to remove it.

ruined sign.name: Ruined Sign
ruined sign.description: Write stuff on it and tell your friends! Use your Wrench on it to change the message.

robotic lock.name: Robotic Lock
robotic lock.description: This robotic guardian keeps your world safe by not allowing anybody without access to break or place blocks. Just like a world lock, only scarier!

digger's spade.name: Digger's Spade
digger's spade.description: This shovel is very specifically designed for one purpose: to shovel dirt. It is pretty useless at digging anywhere else, but dang if it doesn't rip dirt apart (and Cave Background).

disguise glasses.name: Disguise Glasses
disguise glasses.description: Wait a second... WHO ARE YOU!?!? How did you get in here?!

growch cultist robe.name: Growch Cultist Robe
growch cultist robe.description: Just the thing to worship The Growch in.

wedding dress.name: Wedding Dress
wedding dress.description: You look radiant on this special day!

bridal veil.name: Bridal Veil
bridal veil.description: Today's modern bride doesn't want to conceal her face, so we've swept the veil aside for you.

dark red wallpaper.name: Dark Red Wallpaper
dark red wallpaper.description: This is kinda creepy, like the walls are bleeding.

fountain.name: Fountain
fountain.description: Relax by the soothing tinkle of water. You can punch this to turn it on or off.

enchanted spatula.name: Enchanted Spatula
enchanted spatula.description: This mythical artifact, possibly from the future, has an unparalleled magical power: you can slap objects with it to turn them around. Use it on chairs, beds, whatever you find facing the wrong way! Note: Because the spatula is crystal, it shatters when used.

sink.name: Sink
sink.description: Punch to wash your hands! Be clean, please. As of this item, Growtopia now includes everything but the kitchen sink (this is the bathroom sink, unfortunately).

ring of water.name: Ring Of Water
ring of water.description: This mystical ring encases you in a bubble, allowing you to swim at high velocity. The cool bubble also protects you from dangerous burns like lava.

spikey anime hair.name: Spikey Anime Hair
spikey anime hair.description: The great thing about this hairstyle is you just wake up with it every morning! Sure, some people use a comb to fix that, but you just call it anime!

red bicycle.name: Red Bicycle
red bicycle.description: It's easy to remember how to ride it, because it's like riding a bike!

cybernetic eye.name: Cybernetic Eye
cybernetic eye.description: We've rebuilt you - better, faster, stronger than before.

vending machine.name: Vending Machine
vending machine.description: Shopping without the hassle of human beings! Use your wrench on this item to stock it with an item and set a price in World Locks. Other players will be able to buy from it! Only works in World-Locked worlds.

jester's cap.name: Jester's Cap
jester's cap.description: Bring joy to Growtopia in this classically designed headwear!

blanket cape.name: Blanket Cape
blanket cape.description: If you can't afford a real one, just fake it with a blanket!

riding war wolf.name: Riding War Wolf
riding war wolf.description: It's just like a horse... except you MAY want to avoid kicking it with your heels.

wolf tamer's glove.name: Wolf Tamer's Glove
wolf tamer's glove.description: When you stare into a wolf's eyes, you're staring into the untameable heart of nature itself. But you can tame it anyway if you've got the right fashion accessories!

wolf whistle.name: Wolf Whistle
wolf whistle.description: Beware! Blowing this whistle will send you off the Wolfworld! When you are there, you will have only 10 minutes before the power of the wolf wears off and you return to the real world. Can you conquer the Wolfworld in time?

great wolf totem.name: Great Wolf Totem
great wolf totem.description: Players that touch this get a wolf prize, and kicked out of the wolfworld.

wolf totem.name: Wolf Totem
wolf totem.description: Now you can play Wolfworld: The Home Game with your own handy wooden totem!

dire wolf mask.name: Dire Wolf Mask
dire wolf mask.description: This mask is usually kept in a glass case, with a tiny hammer and a sign that says Break glass only in case of dire emergency!

goldfish.name: Goldfish
goldfish.description: These are named for their orange coloration, they're not actually made of any precious metals.

fish tank port.name: Fish Tank Port
fish tank port.description: This is a handy hole in a fish tank, through which you can insert or remove fish! Use your wrench to manage the fish, just like real fish. You can only place this on a fish tank.

fish tank.name: Fish Tank
fish tank.description: Fish can swim around in here! However, you need to put them in through a Fish Tank Port, sold separately.

rollback plaque iii.name: Rollback Plaque III
rollback plaque iii.description: You were there, man. You were THERE when time rolled backwards again, the server burned to bits, and all the fruits of your labors turned to dust in your dry, bitter fist. August 2015

e-z rod.name: E-Z Rod
e-z rod.description: Equip this and then use bait on water next to you and go fishing! All you have to do is wait for a bait, and then punch the fish before it escapes! If you miss, your bait is wasted, so punch fast. This is a beginner's fishing rod - it keeps fish on the line twice as long as other rods, so it's easy as pie.

licorice rod.name: Licorice Rod
licorice rod.description: Equip this and then use bait on water next to you to go fishing! All you have to do is wait for a bite, and then punch the fish before it escapes! If you miss, your bait is wasted, so punch fast. This delicious rod gets bites twice as often as other rods.

shiny flashy thing.name: Shiny Flashy Thing
shiny flashy thing.description: This is bait for fishing. Equip a fishing rod and then use this bait on water that you are standing next to in order to start fishing. The shiny stuff appeals to larger fish then Wiggly Worms do.

salmon eggs.name: Salmon Eggs
salmon eggs.description: This is bait for fishing. Equip a fishing rod and then use this bait on water that you are standing next to in order to start fishing. These eggs catch mid-sized fish.

fishing fly.name: Fishing Fly
fishing fly.description: This is bait for fishing. Equip a fishing rod and then use this bait on water that you are standing next to in order to start fishing. The dancing action of these lures can even attract large fish.

shrimp lure.name: Shrimp Lure
shrimp lure.description: This is bait for fishing. Equip a fishing rod and then use this bait on water that you are standing next to in order to start fishing. There is no fish too big to enjoy a shrimp lure.

whizmo gizmo.name: Whizmo Gizmo
whizmo gizmo.description: This is bait for fishing with three high-tech features: it appeals to all sizes and types of fish, it homes in on the largest fish around, and special filtering fins keep it from hooking on anything other than a fish!

electric eel.name: Electric Eel
electric eel.description: It's always a shock to find you've caught one of these on your line. Place it in your world to share the feeling with others.

whale.name: Whale
whale.description: Don't be fooled just because you caught this whale while fishing - this giant of the ocean is mammal. And shame on you for catching it! They're endangered!

catfish.name: Catfish
catfish.description: I really don't know why they call these fish catfish. Weird.

perch.name: Perch
perch.description: These fish are named for the strange way that they tend to hang in mid-air, like solid objects you can stand on. Try it, you can't knock one down no matter how hard you jump on it!

dogfish.name: Dogfish
dogfish.description: Dogfish are a type of shark, and they are so named because they hunt in packs, like dogs do. It has nothing to do with their appearance, which is entirely fishlike and not canine at all.

gar.name: Gar
gar.description: That doesn't even sound like a real word.

mahi mahi.name: Mahi Mahi
mahi mahi.description: This fish is so nice they named it twice.

sunfish.name: Sunfish
sunfish.description: If there's one fish that can brighten your day, this is it.

bass.name: Bass
bass.description: Don't drop the bass. You'd hurt it.

goldenrod.name: Goldenrod
goldenrod.description: Equip this and then use bait in water next to you to go fishing! All you have to do is wait for a bite, and then punch the fish before it escapes! If you miss, your bait is wasted, so punch fast! This enchanted rod will catch 25% bigger fish than normal!

fishing hat.name: Fishing Hat
fishing hat.description: Congratulations on winning the Fishing Frenzy Daily Challenge! With this hat on, there's a 5% chance to not use up your bait when you fish (I mean, there's a bunch of extra bait right there on the hat!).

tackle box.name: Tackle Box
tackle box.description: You keep all your bait for fishing in here. Unfortunately, it's on a timed lock, so it can only be opened once every two days.

firefighter helmet - red.name: Firefighter Helmet - Red
firefighter helmet - red.description: Protect your head from falling embers, or occasionally falling buildings!

firefighter helmet - yellow.name: Firefighter Helmet - Yellow
firefighter helmet - yellow.description: Protect your head from falling embers, or occasionally falling buildings!

oxygen mask.name: Oxygen Mask
oxygen mask.description: Strap this on when people start tossing rotten eggs. You'll be much happier.

firefighter boots.name: Firefighter Boots
firefighter boots.description: Finally, the technology exists to protect your feet from fire without exposing them to dangerous asbestos! Wear these for fire safety.

firefighter pants - red.name: Firefighter Pants - Red
firefighter pants - red.description: These pants are made of stylish rubber to ensure you are as overheated as possible while standing in a burning building.

firefighter pants - yellow.name: Firefighter Pants - Yellow
firefighter pants - yellow.description: These pants are made of stylish rubber to ensure you are as overheated as possible while standing in a burning building.

firefighter jacket - red.name: Firefighter Jacket - Red
firefighter jacket - red.description: Is it hot in here? Throw on a jacket!

firefighter jacket - yellow.name: Firefighter Jacket - Yellow
firefighter jacket - yellow.description: Is it hot in here? Throw on a jacket!

pocket lighter.name: Pocket Lighter
pocket lighter.description: You just want to watch the world burn. Use this on any tile, whether you own it or not, to set it on fire.

water balloon.name: Water Balloon
water balloon.description: Throw this to splash water over a wide area, putting out fires.

fire hose.name: Fire Hose
fire hose.description: Where is the other end of this hose plugged in? I don't know, but it has an infinite supply of water! This does no damage to blocks at all, but it puts out fires with great ease!

fire truck.name: Fire Truck
fire truck.description: For the sake of your fellow Growtopians, we limited the siren. But you can still enjoy the flashing lights!

fire ax.name: Fire Ax
fire ax.description: Chop your way into burning buildings to rescue puppies! This device is not licensed for any other use.

firehouse.name: Firehouse
firehouse.description: This building provides protections against all fires! It can put out any fire in your world in seconds.

floating leaf.name: Floating Leaf
floating leaf.description: This magic leaf can float you around. Just cuz.

solar collector.name: Solar Collector
solar collector.description: This biomechanical device accumulates solar energy all day long. Then, when you plant a tree in your world, the stored energy is pumped into the tree, growing it to 25% of full growth instantly!

autumn viney block.name: Autumn Viney Block
autumn viney block.description: It may seem obvious, but I'll say it anyway: this block is viney, but turning red and gold.

autumn viney wallpaper.name: Autumn Viney Wallpaper
autumn viney wallpaper.description: It's like you're lost in the jungle! In the middle of October!

autumn leaf block.name: Autumn Leaf Block
autumn leaf block.description: If you don't like it, you can make like this block and leaf. In the fall.

dried leaf crown.name: Dried Leaf Crown
dried leaf crown.description: Handle with care or you're gonna end up with potpourri instead of the Heralded Crown Of Autumn.

musical gong.name: Musical Gong
musical gong.description: If somebody bangs this while you are performing, it means your act is bad and you should feel bad. On the other hand, it plays a nifty tune!

highly combustible box.name: Highly Combustible Box
highly combustible box.description: This box is made of gasoline-soaked balsa wood. It's a really bad design. If it gets lit on fire, it will burn up instantly. A few selected items can be tempered by fire though. Perhaps you could store them inside and see what happens when it burns?

skeletal shark.name: Skeletal Shark
skeletal shark.description: This is what happens when you don't feed your fish.

ghost fish.name: Ghost Fish
ghost fish.description: There's nothing spooky about this fish, it's just the kind where you can see through it a bit. Kinda weird though.

demon angler.name: Demon Angler
demon angler.description: This is a demonic fish, not a fish that angles for demons. I figured the teeth and eyes made that obvious.

otherworldly bait.name: Otherworldly Bait
otherworldly bait.description: This is bait for fishing. Equip a fishing rod and then use this bait on water that you are standing next to in order to start fishing. This bait actually travels through a wormhole into a dark dimension and catches things there, instead of in the water. Bad things.

cursed fishing rod.name: Cursed Fishing Rod
cursed fishing rod.description: Equip this and then use bait on water next to you to go fishing! All you have to do is wait for a bite, and then punch the fish before it escapes! If you miss, your bait is wasted, so punch fast. You will suffer mysterious effects when catching fish with this rod. Beware the curse!

eldritch flame.name: Eldritch Flame
eldritch flame.description: The seething fires of the underworld are at your command! Throw this in somebody's world to start a bunch of fires and really annoy them.

flaming cape.name: Flaming Cape
flaming cape.description: This cape burns eternally with eldritch fire. It's also lined with asbestos, so you're all good. Probably.

ghost costume.name: Ghost Costume
ghost costume.description: Nothing spookier than a bedsheet with two holes cut in it!

chainsaw hand.name: Chainsaw Hand
chainsaw hand.description: If you ever get a possessed hand and have to lop it off at the wrist, here's a handy replacement for it! Also good for ice sculpture.

cape tatters.name: Cape Tatters
cape tatters.description: This bit of cloth is black on one side and blood-red on the other. If you had 25 of these, you might be able to make a really spooky cape!

inside-out vampire cape.name: Inside-Out Vampire Cape
inside-out vampire cape.description: You accidentally made your cape inside-out!

black aura.name: Black Aura
black aura.description: I'm pretty sure it's a bad sign when your aura is this color.

hellgate.name: Hellgate
hellgate.description: It seems like the destination of this portal is obvious, but actually you can choose any place you like with your Wrench.

riding demon dog.name: Riding Demon Dog
riding demon dog.description: It's just like a horse... except PURE EVIL.

teeny devil wings.name: Teeny Devil Wings
teeny devil wings.description: Even as tiny as they are, these wings allow you to jump in mid-air!

teeny wing fragment.name: Teeny Wing Fragment
teeny wing fragment.description: This is about an eighth of a Teeny Devil Wing. So if you had 16 of these, you could make a pair of Teeny Devil Wings!

soul orb.name: Soul Orb
soul orb.description: This orb devours the soul of anything it touches - Growtopians, Blocks Trees, whatever!

dark magic barrier.name: Dark Magic Barrier
dark magic barrier.description: This demonic energy field only lets the right people through.

stethoscope.name: Stethoscope
stethoscope.description: Congratulations on winning the Doctor's Duel Daily Challenge! With this Stethoscope on, you are half as likely to make mistakes in surgery!

super logo - crown.name: Super Logo - Crown
super logo - crown.description: Emblazon this logo on your super costume since you won the Card Clash Daily Challenge! With this logo on, you get +2 heath during card battles!

wolf spirit.name: Wolf Spirit
wolf spirit.description: Congratulations on winning the War of Wolves Daily Challenge! With this spirit equipped (it is a back item, by the way), you can double jump, and the guidance of the Wolf Spirit will improve your Wolfworld rewards (usually).

wolfy block.name: Wolfy Block
wolfy block.description: This is the wolfiest block available with current technology.

challenge crown.name: Challenge Crown
challenge crown.description: Congratulations! You were #1 in a Daily Challenge! Show off with a shiny crown.

ring of savings.name: Ring Of Savings
ring of savings.description: Congratulations on winning the Carnie Contest Daily Challenge! With this ring equipped, you save 10% on Golden Ticket prices (pay 90 rarity per ticket, or get 33 per World Lock).

challenge board.name: Challenge Board
challenge board.description: Wrench this board to see the situation with the Daily Challenge!

cosmic cape.name: Cosmic Cape
cosmic cape.description: Congratulations on winning the Cosmic Crown Daily Challenge! You don't get a crown, you get a cape that sparkles and very very rarely finds leftover Comet Dust in blocks you break when it's not The Night Of The Comet!

rainbow crystal block.name: Rainbow Crystal Block
rainbow crystal block.description: Congratulations on winning the Crystal Crusher Daily Challenge! Enjoy this rainbowlicious block. Don't you just wanna lick it? Also, if you smash a Harmonic Crystal that is sitting on this block, there's a 20% chance of getting back one of the crystals you put into it.

cosmic power - comet strike.name: Cosmic Power - Comet Strike
cosmic power - comet strike.description: This is a Cosmic Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Cosmic cards aren't used, they just have an effect as long as they are in your hand. Card effect: 25% chance of doing 1 extra damage whenever you card counters the opponents.

cosmic power - star burst.name: Cosmic Power - Star Burst
cosmic power - star burst.description: This is a Cosmic Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Cosmic Cards aren't used, they just have an effect as long as they are in your hand. Card effect: When you are hit for more than 1 damage at once, the opponent is blasted for 1 damage.

cosmic power - lunar barrier.name: Cosmic Power - Lunar Barrier
cosmic power - lunar barrier.description: This is a Cosmic Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Cosmic cards aren't used, they just have an effect as long as they are in your hand. Card effect: When you are at or below 25% life, there's a chance to deflect damage done to you.

cosmic power - nebula gas.name: Cosmic Power - Nebula Gas
cosmic power - nebula gas.description: This is a Cosmic Superpower card for use in fighting crime. You can also place it as a block! Cosmic Cards aren't used, they just have an effect as long as they are in your hand. Card effect: When you cards are countered, there's a 25% chance that your card works anyways.

transdimensional vaporizer ray.name: Transdimensional Vaporizer Ray
transdimensional vaporizer ray.description: This is a highly advanced alien device with one purpose: it can fire right through solid matter to vaporize background without doing any harm to the foreground blocks. It uses alien batteries which we can't replace, so each Vaporizer can only be used once.

carnival pinwheel.name: Carnival Pinwheel
carnival pinwheel.description: Enjoy the beauty of this spinny pinwheel.

sword and shield.name: Sword And Shield
sword and shield.description: This is a classic warrior's combo - a nice cutlass for your main hand, and a shield in the other. This shield makes you harder to knock back!

twin swords.name: Twin Swords
twin swords.description: Why waste time with a shield? Just get two swords!

preppy blonde hair.name: Preppy Blonde Hair
preppy blonde hair.description: I think you've got just enough gel in there to go to the sock hop with Buffy!

pet slime.name: Pet Slime
pet slime.description: Nothing cuter than a sentient ball of slime that follows you around!

strawberry slime.name: Strawberry Slime
strawberry slime.description: So much tastier than mucus flavor!

angry unicorn block.name: Angry Unicorn Block
angry unicorn block.description: This block is angry, and prominently features a unicorn.

legal briefs.name: Legal Briefs
legal briefs.description: Not only are these comfortable undergarments for everyday use, they also have a legal use: put them on when you are in trouble for Malpractice, and you'll be freed from your punishment! This uses up the Briefs.

ring of smithing.name: Ring Of Smithing
ring of smithing.description: To be honest, this ring doesn't really do anything. Well, that is unless you want to smith something. Then you're definitely gonna need to wear this!

anvil.name: Anvil
anvil.description: You can forge astounding weapons on this, if it's next to a Forge that's been heated to 1,000 degrees, and you have Smithing Tools, and wear a Ring of Smithing and a Blacksmith's Apron. Oh, and have some item you want to smith. If you've got all that, go ahead and use the item on the anvil!

blacksmith's apron.name: Blacksmith's Apron
blacksmith's apron.description: This apron is made of heavy leather, making it very effective for protecting you from stray sparks when forging things.

crystal smithing tools.name: Crystal Smithing Tools
crystal smithing tools.description: These tools are so gentle they break after 1 use! Use them wisely!

blade fragment.name: Blade Fragment
blade fragment.description: This is a broken piece of a sword blade. It's of a low-quality steel and could stand to be tempered.

shield fragment.name: Shield Fragment
shield fragment.description: This is a broken piece of a shield. If you had enough of these, you could probably forge them into a new shield!

tempered steel fragment.name: Tempered Steel Fragment
tempered steel fragment.description: This is a beautiful steel fragment of a sword blade. If you had enough of these, you could probably forge them into a new sword blade!

sword pommel.name: Sword Pommel
sword pommel.description: This is a lovingly crafted sword pommel. If only there were a blade to attach it to!

sword blade.name: Sword Blade
sword blade.description: This is a lovingly crafted sword blade. If only there were a pommel to attach it to!

warrior's shield.name: Warrior's Shield
warrior's shield.description: This is a loving crafted shield. But you can't punch block with a shield. Maybe you can combine this with a weapon to make a complete set?

forge.name: Forge
forge.description: You can use this to forge astounding weapons, if you have an Anvil next to it. You'll also need to fuel it with something really hot.

nuclear fuel.name: Nuclear Fuel
nuclear fuel.description: You can feel your cells mutating just being near this lump of radioactive garbage. About the only thing this is good for is firing up a forge to ridiculous levels of heat.

gift of the unicorn.name: Gift of the Unicorn
gift of the unicorn.description: The unicorn has gifted you great wisdom! The wisdom is thus: If you stick this wisdom, 2 Sword Pommels, and 2 Sword Blades, into a Laboratory and SCIENCE them... well, let's just say it'll be super cool.

giving tree.name: Giving Tree
giving tree.description: Borrowed" from the Growch's private reserve, this magnificent tree will give you a gift every 4 hours for the duration of WinterFest!

giving tree stump.name: Giving Tree Stump
giving tree stump.description: This will regrow into a Giving Tree in a while.

tree decorations.name: Tree Decorations
tree decorations.description: All sorts of baubles and gewgaws to adorn your Giving Tree in true Winterfest style! One decoration won't do much, but you can toss up to 100 decorations on each tree! More decorations will logically result in better gifts, but taking the gift will remove all the decorations with it!

lumber axe.name: Lumber Axe
lumber axe.description: This axe is precisely balanced to chop down trees in just a single hit! Now, you might not be impressed since you can do that with your bare hands already. But wait - this axe can chop down the GROWCH'S trees! Of course, doing that will shatter it. They're very special trees.

axe fragment.name: Axe Fragment
axe fragment.description: This is a broken piece of an axe blade. It's not very high quality, perhaps it could be tempered.

icy heart of winter.name: Icy Heart Of Winter
icy heart of winter.description: You've found the Growch's icy heart! No wonder he's so mean - it's not even in his body! That's a major medical problem that would upset anyone.

icy heart pickup.name: Icy Heart Pickup
icy heart pickup.description: Players pick up an Icy Heart of Winter by touching this.

axe of winter.name: Axe Of Winter
axe of winter.description: Mittens are recommended when wielding this icy monstrosity, which does extra damage to blocks.

moose cap.name: Moose Cap
moose cap.description: This beautifully styled hat, suitable for all formal occasions, has the unique property of attracting wild meese to follow you around.

candy cane bait.name: Candy Cane Bait
candy cane bait.description: This is a bait for fishing. Equip a fishing rod and then use this bait on water that you are standing next to in order to start fishing. This is the only bait that is its own hook! It catches unique seasonal fish that other bait doesn't appeal to.

neon squid.name: Neon Squid
neon squid.description: This squid glows in neon colors! What a fine holiday gift it would make.

antarctic icefish.name: Antarctic Icefish
antarctic icefish.description: These fish have the ability to survive in Antarctic waters because they actually have antifreeze in their blood! Its science, google it.

gingerbread fish.name: Gingerbread Fish
gingerbread fish.description: You know how you can dunk cookies in milk? This one was dunked in the ocean. Kinda gross.

swedish fish.name: Swedish Fish
swedish fish.description: This breed of fish is unique to the waters of Sweden, and it has a surprisingly sweet taste when eaten raw. Don't eat yours though, it's a pet.

snowcone.name: Snowcone
snowcone.description: Yum, fruit flavours poured into ice! At least it's yum until all the flavouring gets sucked out.

toboggan.name: Toboggan
toboggan.description: This sled was called "Onion Bulb" by its original owner, but you can call it whatever you want. It comes with a free purple blanket to keep your legs warm!

winter wind.name: Winter Wind
winter wind.description: Place this anywhere you want the wind to come ripping through and push players around! The wind blows in the direction that you would blow air when placing it, so you can place it either way.

snowflake block.name: Snowflake Block
snowflake block.description: Just one exceptionally large snowflake, perfectly preserved in Lucite. I don't know how they did it, but it's nice and slippery!

winter robe.name: Winter Robe
winter robe.description: Be the King of Winter in this luxurious satiny robe! Note: this is a "chest item", like a necklace, so you can wear any shirts and back items you want underneath it.

magical carrot.name: Magical Carrot
magical carrot.description: With just a touch of winter magic, it's really not that hard to bring a snowman to life. I don't know why more people don't do it!

hot chocolate.name: Hot Chocolate
hot chocolate.description: Mmm, sweet and toasty, with marshmallows! This not only warms your insides, but it also contains a massive dose of delicious iodine to clear out any radiation you're currently suffering from. Inexplicably it also charges up Geiger Counters when consumed. I can't explain that one.

tempered axe fragment.name: Tempered Axe Fragment
tempered axe fragment.description: This is a broken piece of an axe blade, tempered to polished steel! With enough of these, and a suitable source of enraged winter fury, you could forge an amazing Icy Axe Blade.

icy axe blade.name: Icy Axe Blade
icy axe blade.description: This blade is enchanted with winter magic! You could build an awesome weapon with a pair of these and a handle... well, it'd be awesome if you could hold it. Maybe you need something to protect your hands when holding it.

steel axe handle.name: Steel Axe Handle
steel axe handle.description: This thing has a nice heft, and handy notches for inserting up to two axe blades. The only real downside is that it's made entirely of metal, so if you were to place, say, magical ice blades in it, the cold would be transmitted right to your hand, and you wouldn't be able to hold it.

grip tape.name: Grip Tape
grip tape.description: This is handy for wrapping around the handle of a weapon or tool. It can improve your grip, as well as protect you from cold metal handles.

riding winter wolf.name: Riding Winter Wolf
riding winter wolf.description: It's just like a horse... except soft and fuzzy!

weather machine - snowy night.name: Weather Machine - Snowy Night
weather machine - snowy night.description: Man, the weather outside is frightful! And dark!

elf stockings.name: Elf Stockings
elf stockings.description: This is just really long underwear. You probably should wear pants over them, but hey, Growtopia doesn't support that, so you'll just have to be cold!

sock on the wall.name: Sock On The Wall
sock on the wall.description: You'll need to wash your socks. This one stuck to the wall!

steam gear.name: Steam Gear
steam gear.description: This is a cog in a vast steam machine. Or can it be, if you build one, with this in it! This links up to other Steam blocks and can conduct steam power.

steam tubes.name: Steam Tubes
steam tubes.description: Tubes for directing steam power. This links up to other Steam blocks and can conduct steam power. Steam flows straight when possible, otherwise it turns right (and turns left if it can't do that!)

steam piston.name: Steam Piston
steam piston.description: Steam power makes it go whump whump whump. This links up to other Steam blocks and can conduct steam power.

steam lifter piston.name: Steam Lifter Piston
steam lifter piston.description: Steam power makes it go whump whump whump up and down. This links up to other steam blocks and can conduct steam power.

steam bellows.name: Steam Bellows
steam bellows.description: Steam power makes it go eenk-oonk-eenk (pardon the technical terminology). This links up to other Steam blocks and can conduct steam power.

steam riser bellows.name: Steam Riser Bellows
steam riser bellows.description: Steam power makes it go eenk-oonk-eenk up and down (pardon the technical terminology). This links up to other Steam blocks and can conduct steam power.

steam stomper.name: Steam Stomper
steam stomper.description: Jump on this to shoot steam below it! Use the other Steam Blocks to direct the steam when you need it. The Steam code prohibits more than 20 Steam Stompers in a world.

growtopia fan shirt.name: Growtopia Fan Shirt
growtopia fan shirt.description: This amazing psychic shirt can actually display your thought with spectacular new morphing Ink technology. Note: Yeah, it just says the one thing, but you know you're thinking it.

t-shirt cannon.name: T-Shirt Cannon
t-shirt cannon.description: Powered by a Fuel Pack on your back, this gun can launch free T-shirts at your fellow Growtopians! Don't waste shots at anything else, it still burns fuel!

ghost fan shirt.name: Ghost Fan Shirt
ghost fan shirt.description: You like ghosts? No? Sure looks like you do.

steam valve.name: Steam Valve
steam valve.description: This links up to other Steam blocks and can conduct steam power. If steam enters this block from the top or bottom, it will go out the bigger side, and the valve will flip for the next time.

steam organ.name: Steam Organ
steam organ.description: This links up to other Steam blocks and can conduct steam power. When steam passes through this block, it plays a beautiful music! Use your wrench to adjust what note comes out.

steam vent.name: Steam Vent
steam vent.description: This links up to other Steam blocks and can conduct steam power. When steam passes through this block, it vents some out with intense heat! Do not touch this for 3 seconds after steam has been through.

steam door.name: Steam Door
steam door.description: Punch it to open it or shut it. But even if you don't have access to do that, you can still open and shut it with steam power!

steampunk corset.name: Steampunk Corset
steampunk corset.description: Tired of always choosing the survival of your internal organs over looking skinny? The corset is the thing for you!

steampunk skirt.name: Steampunk Skirt
steampunk skirt.description: Multiple layers of petticoats keep you warm!

steampunk top hat.name: Steampunk Top Hat
steampunk top hat.description: Keep an extra pair of googles up there. You never know when you'll need them.

steampunk waistcoat.name: Steampunk Waistcoat
steampunk waistcoat.description: This perfect garment for housing a pocketwatch, monocle, and perhaps taxidermy needles. Definitely some weird stuff in those pockets.

steampunk leggings.name: Steampunk Leggings
steampunk leggings.description: Works equally well for a steampunk or a pirate! Or maybe a dancer from the 80's.

steampunk trenchcoat.name: Steampunk Trenchcoat
steampunk trenchcoat.description: Keep warm on those frosty London evenings in this stylish piece by Grow Couture! Note: this is a "Chest item", like a necklace so you can wear any shirts and back items you want underneath it

party blaster.name: Party Blaster
party blaster.description: Take the party with you everywhere you go!

tempered party tunes.name: Tempered Party Tunes
tempered party tunes.description: This is a highly polished bit of music. So shiny! Enough of these might be able to forge a relic from ancient times past...

80's tape deck.name: 80's Tape Deck
80's tape deck.description: Wow, this is some seriously old technology. It's no good without a suitable power source and some speakers to rock out of.

d battery.name: D Battery
d battery.description: A portable source of a tiny amount of power.

da vinci wings.name: Da Vinci Wings
da vinci wings.description: Da Vinci actually thought he could fly with these. He was totally wrong - they only let you double jump and glide.

steampunk sprocket.name: Steampunk Sprocket
steampunk sprocket.description: There's not a lot of difference between a sprocket and a gear. But this is a sprocket.

steampunk gearbox.name: Steampunk Gearbox
steampunk gearbox.description: It's a box full of sprockets and gears and whatnots! It's probably part of an awesome steampunk creation.

stretched canvas.name: Stretched Canvas
stretched canvas.description: It's not the prettiest decoration for your world, but it's probably got some other good uses.

silkworm.name: Silkworm
silkworm.description: A cute little pet for you to feed and care for! They'll eat almost anything, but don't forget to give them water too. Use your wrench to change your pet's name.

silk thread - red.name: Silk Thread - Red
silk thread - red.description: A single thread isn't very useful. Get 100 of these to stitch a bolt together!

silk thread - green.name: Silk Thread - Green
silk thread - green.description: A single thread isn't very useful. Get 100 of these to stitch a bolt together!

silk thread - blue.name: Silk Thread - Blue
silk thread - blue.description: A single thread isn't very useful. Get 100 of these to stitch a bolt together!

silk thread - black.name: Silk Thread - Black
silk thread - black.description: A single thread isn't very useful. Get 100 of these to stitch a bolt together!

silk thread - white.name: Silk Thread - White
silk thread - white.description: A single thread isn't very useful. Get 100 of these to stitch a bolt together!

silk thread - grey.name: Silk Thread - Grey
silk thread - grey.description: A single thread isn't very useful. Get 100 of these to stitch a bolt together!

silk thread - yellow.name: Silk Thread - Yellow
silk thread - yellow.description: A single thread isn't very useful. Get 100 of these to stitch a bolt together!

silk thread - purple.name: Silk Thread - Purple
silk thread - purple.description: A single thread isn't very useful. Get 100 of these to stitch a bolt together!

silk thread - aqua.name: Silk Thread - Aqua
silk thread - aqua.description: A single thread isn't very useful. Get 100 of these to stitch a bolt together!

silk bolt - red.name: Silk Bolt - Red
silk bolt - red.description: Sew Silk items by using this in a Sewing Machine. It takes 3 Bolts of Silk to craft an item.

silk bolt - green.name: Silk Bolt - Green
silk bolt - green.description: Sew Silk items by using this in a Sewing Machine. It takes 3 Bolts of Silk to craft an item.

silk bolt - blue.name: Silk Bolt - Blue
silk bolt - blue.description: Sew Silk items by using this in a Sewing Machine. It takes 3 Bolts of Silk to craft an item.

silk bolt - black.name: Silk Bolt - Black
silk bolt - black.description: Sew Silk items by using this in a Sewing Machine. It takes 3 Bolts of Silk to craft an item.

silk bolt - white.name: Silk Bolt - White
silk bolt - white.description: Sew Silk items by using this in a Sewing Machine. It takes 3 Bolts of Silk to craft an item.

silk bolt - grey.name: Silk Bolt - Grey
silk bolt - grey.description: Sew Silk items by using this in a Sewing Machine. It takes 3 Bolts of Silk to craft an item.

silk bolt - yellow.name: Silk Bolt - Yellow
silk bolt - yellow.description: Sew Silk items by using this in a Sewing Machine. It takes 3 Bolts of Silk to craft an item.

silk bolt - purple.name: Silk Bolt - Purple
silk bolt - purple.description: Sew Silk items by using this in a Sewing Machine. It takes 3 Bolts of Silk to craft an item.

silk bolt - aqua.name: Silk Bolt - Aqua
silk bolt - aqua.description: Sew Silk items by using this in a Sewing Machine. It takes 3 Bolts of Silk to craft an item.

sewing machine.name: Sewing Machine
sewing machine.description: Use Silk Bolts on this machine to sew them together into finished products. You'll need 3 bolts of silk, and you'll have to sew them in the right order, using the right type of stitching!

patchwork mess.name: Patchwork Mess
patchwork mess.description: An experiment in sewing gone horribly wrong. This is just a bunch of silk stitched together in random directions.

silk vest - red.name: Silk Vest - Red
silk vest - red.description: A snappy vest suitable for any occasion.

silk vest - green.name: Silk Vest - Green
silk vest - green.description: A snappy vest suitable for any occasion.

silk vest - blue.name: Silk Vest - Blue
silk vest - blue.description: A snappy vest suitable for any occasion.

silk vest - purple.name: Silk Vest - Purple
silk vest - purple.description: A snappy vest suitable for any occasion.

silk vest - grey.name: Silk Vest - Grey
silk vest - grey.description: A snappy vest suitable for any occasion.

silk vest - black.name: Silk Vest - Black
silk vest - black.description: A snappy vest suitable for any occasion.

silk tie - red.name: Silk Tie - Red
silk tie - red.description: You will command respect in this power tie!

silk tie - yellow.name: Silk Tie - Yellow
silk tie - yellow.description: You will command respect in this power tie!

silk tie - black.name: Silk Tie - Black
silk tie - black.description: You will command respect in this power tie!

silk tie - blue.name: Silk Tie - Blue
silk tie - blue.description: You will command respect in this power tie!

silk tie - grey.name: Silk Tie - Grey
silk tie - grey.description: You will command respect in this power tie!

silk skirt - red.name: Silk Skirt - Red
silk skirt - red.description: A classic look, available in a variety of colors.

silk skirt - blue.name: Silk Skirt - Blue
silk skirt - blue.description: A classic look, available in a variety of colors.

silk skirt - aqua.name: Silk Skirt - Aqua
silk skirt - aqua.description: A classic look, available in a variety of colors.

silk skirt - black.name: Silk Skirt - Black
silk skirt - black.description: A classic look, available in a variety of colors.

silk skirt - white.name: Silk Skirt - White
silk skirt - white.description: A classic look, available in a variety of colors.

silk skirt - purple.name: Silk Skirt - Purple
silk skirt - purple.description: A classic look, available in a variety of colors.

country flag.name: Country Flag
country flag.description: Place this anywhere to proudly display your country's flag!

lovebird pendant.name: Lovebird Pendant
lovebird pendant.description: Pip pip! This little bird will follow you around forever, because it loves you. Or at least it loves that necklace, and possibly wants it back.

booty chest.name: Booty Chest
booty chest.description: Store your treasures inside by dropping them! When it's closed, the items are hidden. Punch to open it.

love potion #8.name: Love Potion #8
love potion #8.description: This potion isn't FDA approved for use on humans yet, maybe a later version will be. But spray a rock with it to upgrade it into a WAY better rock.

sour lollipop.name: Sour Lollipop
sour lollipop.description: Zing! This is one tart little lollipop.

sweet lollipop.name: Sweet Lollipop
sweet lollipop.description: Mmm! This is one sweet lollipop.

pink marble arch.name: Pink Marble Arch
pink marble arch.description: This rich marble comes from the hills of Cupidia, and our finest artisans have carved it into this sturdy arch.

silkworm toy.name: Silkworm Toy
silkworm toy.description: Whee! Silkworms love to play with these. Whatever they are.

steam collector.name: Steam Collector
steam collector.description: If steam enters this block, it will be held there for up to 20 seconds. The collector will hold as much steam as it takes to shoot it out of every output (except the one that the last steam entered from), and then shoot them all out. I hope that makes sense. Try it.

steam scrambler.name: Steam Scrambler
steam scrambler.description: This link up to other Steam blocks and can conduct steam power. If steam enters this block, it will exit in a random legal direction.

dark cult hood.name: Dark Cult Hood
dark cult hood.description: When you reach level 7 in the cult, like Jairrocket, your eyes get glowy.

serpent staff.name: Serpent Staff
serpent staff.description: St. Patrick wandered around Ireland with one of these. It scared away all the other snakes because they saw it and thought he was constantly strangling a snake.

roasted cobra.name: Roasted Cobra
roasted cobra.description: Deep fried on a stick! This tasty treat in found at your local county fair, obviously.

cobra statuette.name: Cobra Statuette
cobra statuette.description: This beautifully carved image of a cobra has two sockets for gems in the eyes.

yellow diamond.name: Yellow Diamond
yellow diamond.description: Flawlessly cut from our master gemologists, enjoy this transcendent jewel, an heirloom to last a lifetime.

potato couch.name: Potato Couch
potato couch.description: If you feel like a couch potato, there's no better place to relax than a potato couch.

potato.name: Potato
potato.description: There's no end of ways to make these tasty... fry em, bake em, roast em, grill em. Just don't forget the salt!

lucky pendant.name: Lucky Pendant
lucky pendant.description: This pendant symbolizes two snakes eating themselves. Whatever that means, it also causes a luck dragon to follow you around! Note: it's the dragon that's lucky, not you. I guess you're just lucky to hang around with it!

catch-of-the-day bait.name: Catch-of-the-Day Bait
catch-of-the-day bait.description: This is bait for fishing. Equip a fishing rod and then use this bait on water that you are standing next to in order to start fishing. This bait won't catch anything but the Catch of the Day, which changes each day. Fish have a chance to escape, though! Bonus: Fish caught this way can be larger than the normal maximum size!

rainbowfish.name: Rainbowfish
rainbowfish.description: Nobody knows where the name of this fish came from, it's quite mysterious.

totally legit bunnyfish.name: Totally Legit Bunnyfish
totally legit bunnyfish.description: Amazing! You have caught the incredibly rare and elusive, and completely real, Bunnyfish! There's nothing fake about this fish at all!

seahorse.name: Seahorse
seahorse.description: This rare fish is very hard to keep in an aquarium, requiring careful feeding and cleaning, and a constantly maintained temperature. Lucky for you, this is a videogame, and you can just dump it in and forget about it.

mutant fish.name: Mutant Fish
mutant fish.description: Looks like the comet's radiation has caused unfortunate mutations in the wildlife. You gotta wonder what it's doing to you...

riding bumblebee.name: Riding Bumblebee
riding bumblebee.description: You're too heavy for this bee to fly, but it can help you jump an extra time.

spring crown.name: Spring Crown
spring crown.description: Keep it watered or you'll end up with a crown of thorns instead of the Heralded Crown Of Spring.

weather machine - spring.name: Weather Machine - Spring
weather machine - spring.description: Punch this to enjoy springtime weather, anytime! This sensitive technology will not function while damaged.

lobster trap.name: Lobster Trap
lobster trap.description: Put this in deep water, load it up with 5 of any type of bait, and wait... Come back and check the trap by punching it occasionally. It may be days before an animal will wander in! You just better hope they don't wander back out with your bait.

lobster.name: Lobster
lobster.description: Who ever decided that a giant ocean spider would be something tasty to eat? Shudder.

alaskan king crab.name: Alaskan King Crab
alaskan king crab.description: Strange thing about this crab: Alaska isn't actually a monarchy.

dungeonist crab.name: Dungeonist Crab
dungeonist crab.description: This crab comes armed for dungeon exploration!

crawdad.name: Crawdad
crawdad.description: Whether you call them crawfish, crayfish, crawdads, or even mudbugs, it's really just a little tiny lobster.

brainflower.name: Brainflower
brainflower.description: Flower power! This flower's roots growing down into your brain make you smarter at finding Magic Eggs in an Egg-Hunting Basket. Who knows, you might even find two sometimes!

mermaid tail.name: Mermaid Tail
mermaid tail.description: You don't need to trade your voice for a pair of legs... just take this off and you're all set! But this tail does make you move faster in the water, and slower on land.

sushi knife.name: Sushi Knife
sushi knife.description: This razor-sharp blade has the unique ability to slice up fresh chunks for sushi! Just drop a fish item on a Cutting Board, then attack it with the Sushi Knife!

fish chunk.name: Fish Chunk
fish chunk.description: Gross, it's a slimy bit of fresh fish.

cutting board.name: Cutting Board
cutting board.description: Place poor innocent fish on this and then slice them up with Sushi Knife!

rice.name: Rice
rice.description: The most popular food on Earth has finally come to Growtopia!

maki roll.name: Maki Roll
maki roll.description: Dude, you know that fish is raw, right?

spring bouquet.name: Spring Bouquet
spring bouquet.description: Aw, a lovely bunch of flowers to share!

paint bucket - red.name: Paint Bucket - Red
paint bucket - red.description: Brush this rosy shade onto blocks with a paintbrush to customize your world's appearance!

paint bucket - yellow.name: Paint Bucket - Yellow
paint bucket - yellow.description: Brush this lemony shade onto blocks with a paintbrush to customize your world's appearance.

paint bucket - green.name: Paint Bucket - Green
paint bucket - green.description: Brush this verdant shade onto blocks with a paintbrush to customize your world's appearance!

paint bucket - aqua.name: Paint Bucket - Aqua
paint bucket - aqua.description: Brush this aquatic shade onto blocks with a paintbrush to customize your world's appearance!

paint bucket - blue.name: Paint Bucket - Blue
paint bucket - blue.description: Brush this cerulean shade onto blocks with a paintbrush to customize your world's appearance!

paint bucket - purple.name: Paint Bucket - Purple
paint bucket - purple.description: Brush this majestic shade onto blocks with a paintbrush to customize your world's appearance!

paint bucket - charcoal.name: Paint Bucket - Charcoal
paint bucket - charcoal.description: Brush this ebony onto blocks with a paintbrush to customize your world's appearance!

paint bucket - varnish.name: Paint Bucket - Varnish
paint bucket - varnish.description: Brush this caustic fluid onto blocks with a paintbrush to wipe off any color you've painted onto them.

paintbrush.name: Paintbrush
paintbrush.description: Paint the town a variety of delightful colors with this here brush! Paint not included.

steam revolver.name: Steam Revolver
steam revolver.description: Run through this to shoot steam downward! Use the other Steam Blocks to direct the steam where you need it. This is a steam generator.

steam launcher.name: Steam Launcher
steam launcher.description: Stomp on this and... nothing happens! But pump steam into it first to charge up, and it becomes a steam-powered trampoline!

red crayon.name: Red Crayon
red crayon.description: This is truly an epic crayon. A little tough to manipulate, though.

yellow crayon.name: Yellow Crayon
yellow crayon.description: This is truly an epic crayon. A little tough to manipulate, though.

green crayon.name: Green Crayon
green crayon.description: This is truly an epic crayon. A little tough to manipulate, though.

aqua crayon.name: Aqua Crayon
aqua crayon.description: This is truly an epic crayon. A little tough to manipulate, though.

blue crayon.name: Blue Crayon
blue crayon.description: This is truly an epic crayon. A little tough to manipulate, though.

purple crayon.name: Purple Crayon
purple crayon.description: This is truly an epic crayon. A little tough to manipulate, though.

raspberry beret.name: Raspberry Beret
raspberry beret.description: This is the kind you find at a second-hand store.

artist's smock.name: Artist's Smock
artist's smock.description: Looks like you spilled a little there. No, over there. And there. And the first place you thought I meant.

goatee.name: Goatee
goatee.description: You're either a hipster or an evil twin. Or perhaps... a hipster's evil twin? How would you know which one is evil!?

writing desk.name: Writing Desk
writing desk.description: Nowadays people prefer laptops, but sometimes a good old ink and quilt is what you need. Those items were all hundreds of years ago, of course.

arrow placard.name: Arrow Placard
arrow placard.description: This sign includes a bit of added information - an arrow! The arrow points whichever direction you are facing when you place the sign.

scroll bulletin.name: Scroll Bulletin
scroll bulletin.description: Lets people communicate by leaving messages to each other.

gilded frame.name: Gilded Frame
gilded frame.description: Surround your art with a beautiful frame! Comes with a blank canvas inside if you don't have any art. Note: if your art is made of background blocks, you'll need to apply Block Glue to it to make the frame surround it.

painting easel.name: Painting Easel
painting easel.description: Wrench this to paint your favorite item on it!

orange shirt.name: Orange Shirt
orange shirt.description: I know you dreamed about this since Day 1 of Growtopia. It is finally here. For real. Yes - there is an Orange Shirt, and it's not just a block, you can WEAR IT.

funtime block.name: Funtime Block
funtime block.description: Wheeeee! This block spins wildly when somebody steps on it.

weather machine - howling sky.name: Weather Machine - Howling Sky
weather machine - howling sky.description: Howling in shadows, living in a lunar spell, he finds his heaven... This weather has up to 3 wolves in it, which is an incredible wolf-to-machine ratio you won't find anywhere else.

homeopathic medicine.name: Homeopathic Medicine
homeopathic medicine.description: Exactly 100% as effective as real-life Homeopathic Medicine! These sugar pills are sure to cure what ails you, or my name isn't Xjlgfkvhsnas.

howling wolf emblem.name: Howling Wolf Emblem
howling wolf emblem.description: Slap this emblem around your world to show you are one with the wolf!

charbroiled wolf emblem.name: Charbroiled Wolf Emblem
charbroiled wolf emblem.description: Why did you burn up your beautiful wolf emblem?

hero portrait - buddy.name: Hero Portrait - Buddy
hero portrait - buddy.description: Hey, that villain was carrying a picture of Buddy, the Growtopia mascot!

picasso triggerfish.name: Picasso Triggerfish
picasso triggerfish.description: Also known as Hawaii's state fish, the Humuhumunukunukuapua'a. Yes, that's one of my favorite words.

fish and chips.name: Fish And Chips
fish and chips.description: Deep fried goodness. Enjoy it with some malt vinegar!

battle pet cage.name: Battle Pet Cage
battle pet cage.description: This is the perfect place to starve and torture your pets, turning them into brutal engines of destruction! Wrench it to insert a pet. Note: you can never remove a battle pet - they've become too dangerous to be set loose! If you destroy a cage with a pet inside, the pet is destroyed.

axolotl.name: Axolotl
axolotl.description: This isnt a fish, it's actually a salamander. A cute little Mexican salamander!

battle leash.name: Battle Leash
battle leash.description: This amazing octahedron can actually contain two Battle Pets, primed and ready to strike. Unequip and re-equip to swap pet is active. Wrench a Battle Cage to load a pet into the Leash. Wrench another player with a Battle Leash to battle them! You must have 2 pets in the Battle Leash to battle.

pet trainer.name: Pet Trainer
pet trainer.description: This trainer's stepping on your turf. Take him down with your Battle Leash!

dark cave background.name: Dark Cave Background
dark cave background.description: This far-away dirt is speckled with shiny minerals. However, this dirt is in a dark cave (I don't care where you put it, IT IS IN A DARK CAVE!!). Players can only see what's on this tile if it's in their line of sight, or they have special tools.

steam engine.name: Steam Engine
steam engine.description: Feed Nuclear Fuel to heat this above 500 degrees, and it will generate steam toward the left or right (depending on how it's placed)! Use the other Steam Blocks to direct the steam where you need it. This is a steam generator.

lock mover.name: Lock Mover
lock mover.description: Use this fabulous device anywhere in a world you have world-locked to move the World Lock to a new location. There must be an empty space where you tap for this to work.

cave blast.name: Cave Blast
cave blast.description: This devastating bomb will create a brand new underground cave world, full of darkness and creepy surprises!

cave dirt.name: Cave Dirt
cave dirt.description: Yep, it's dirt. In a cave.

cave column.name: Cave Column
cave column.description: Cave Dirt hooks into this like it's got Block Glue on it, so you can build seamless caverns. These are just fun pillars to hide behind in a cave!

stalagmite.name: Stalagmite
stalagmite.description: These dangerous spikes grow from the GROUND (StalaGmite!) as water drips down and accumulates minerals. Cave Dirt will blend into them seamlessly.

stalactite.name: Stalactite
stalactite.description: These dangerous spikes grow from the CEILING (stalaCtite!) as water deposits minerals on its way to dripping down. Cave Dirt will blend into them seamlessly.

cave platform.name: Cave Platform
cave platform.description: Handy rock platforms. These connect seamlessly to Cave Dirt and can sit atop Cave Columns as well.

spelunker's headlamp.name: Spelunker's Headlamp
spelunker's headlamp.description: This hardhat protects you from falling rocks, while the headlamp lights up the dark caverns.

night vision goggles.name: Night Vision Goggles
night vision goggles.description: Equipping this lets you disregard darkness completely! If you're not in a world you own, they consume 1 D Battery for every minute you wear them. You can wear them without a battery if you just want to look cool, though.

hand torch.name: Hand Torch
hand torch.description: British people would call this a flashlight, but this is an actual torch, for your hand. As opposed to an Adventure Item or wall torch. Carrying this lights up dark caves. Torches burn out at unpredictable moments, so carry several.

purple cave crystal.name: Purple Cave Crystal
purple cave crystal.description: These crystals grow naturally in caves. They don't actually glow - bioluminescent organisms feed on them and emit light. Also heat - be careful!

golden cave crystal.name: Golden Cave Crystal
golden cave crystal.description: These crystals grow naturally in caves. They don't actually glow - bioluminescent organisms feed on them and emit light. Also heat - be careful!

aqua cave crystal.name: Aqua Cave Crystal
aqua cave crystal.description: These crystals grow naturally in caves. They don't actually glow - bioluminescent organisms feed on them and emit light. Also heat - be careful!

climbing wall.name: Climbing Wall
climbing wall.description: Install this right next to walls. It will add bumps and grooves for Climbing Boots to latch onto, so people can climb wall with the right tools!

climbing picks.name: Climbing Picks
climbing picks.description: These handy pick allow you to climb Climbing Wall.

climbing boots.name: Climbing Boots
climbing boots.description: These handy boots allow you to climb Climbing Walls. Just jump and hold the arrow towards the wall!

steam pipe.name: Steam Pipe
steam pipe.description: This links up to other Steam blocks and can conduct steam power. The big difference is it's behind you so you can walk over it!

pinata pal.name: Pinata Pal
pinata pal.description: When you are feeling down and lonely, nothing cheers you up like a rainbow-colored friendly burro filled with candy!

festive banner.name: Festive Banner
festive banner.description: Whatever occasion you have to celebrate, this banner is sure to make it more celebratory.

fish taco.name: Fish Taco
fish taco.description: Fresh Baja taste, with a guacamole cream sauce.

fiesta dress.name: Fiesta Dress
fiesta dress.description: Got a festive occasion to celebrate? Pop on this colorful number for a night on the town!

golden treasure hoard.name: Golden Treasure Hoard
golden treasure hoard.description: Ooh, smash that pile of gold, jewels and priceless treasure! There's probably something GOOD inside!

topaz block.name: Topaz Block
topaz block.description: Flawlessly cut by our master gemologists, enjoy this transcendent jewel, an heirloom to last a lifetime.

deep iron.name: Deep Iron
deep iron.description: Mine this to forge stuff out of Deep Iron.

deep iron ore.name: Deep Iron Ore
deep iron ore.description: This is raw ore, mined from the deep within the Earth. Surely there's something you can do with it!

deep iron ingot.name: Deep Iron Ingot
deep iron ingot.description: You've managed to process this ore into a pure, shining ingot, just by tossing it into a fire!

pick blade.name: Pick Blade
pick blade.description: This pick blade is forged from Deep Iron, which makes it particularly attuned to pickin' real darn good.

guardian pineapple.name: Guardian Pineapple
guardian pineapple.description: When activated (punch to activate), this jealous pineapple prevents anyone from using Consumable items in your world.

pineapple ring.name: Pineapple Ring
pineapple ring.description: Watch out, these are really slippery to stand on!

pineapple fish.name: Pineapple Fish
pineapple fish.description: This SHOULD be known as Hawaii's state fish!

pineapple daiquiri.name: Pineapple Daiquiri
pineapple daiquiri.description: Mmm, this non-alcoholic cocktail is sweet and fruity!

pineapple hair.name: Pineapple Hair
pineapple hair.description: This hair isn't made of pineapple, it's just been dyed and jelled to look like pineapple leaves.

pet trainer cap.name: Pet Trainer Cap
pet trainer cap.description: This hat says PT on it. You can wear it to show you're a Pet Trainer, but you could also use it to celebrate Physical Therapy, or Popcorn Time, or whatever you like!

silkworm leash.name: Silkworm Leash
silkworm leash.description: You wanna take your Silkworm for a walk? Use this on it! Note: The silkworm will become a permanent pet, no longer able to produce silk. Good news: it will also become immortal!

silkworm saddle.name: Silkworm Saddle
silkworm saddle.description: Use this on your silkworm to saddle up and ride! Note: The silkworm will become a permanent riding item, no longer able to produce silk. Good news: it will also become immortal!

riding silkworm - red.name: Riding Silkworm - Red
riding silkworm - red.description: The more legs your ride has, the smoother it is. Too bad centipedes don't grow this big.

riding silkworm - green.name: Riding Silkworm - Green
riding silkworm - green.description: The more legs your ride has, the smoother it is. Too bad centipedes don't grow this big.

riding silkworm - blue.name: Riding Silkworm - Blue
riding silkworm - blue.description: The more legs your ride has, the smoother it is. Too bad centipedes don't grow this big.

riding silkworm - black.name: Riding Silkworm - Black
riding silkworm - black.description: The more legs your ride has, the smoother it is. Too bad centipedes don't grow this big.

riding silkworm - white.name: Riding Silkworm - White
riding silkworm - white.description: The more legs your ride has, the smoother it is. Too bad centipedes don't grow this big.

riding silkworm - grey.name: Riding Silkworm - Grey
riding silkworm - grey.description: The more legs your ride has, the smoother it is. Too bad centipedes don't grow this big.

riding silkworm - purple.name: Riding Silkworm - Purple
riding silkworm - purple.description: The more legs your ride has, the smoother it is. Too bad centipedes don't grow this big.

riding silkworm - yellow.name: Riding Silkworm - Yellow
riding silkworm - yellow.description: The more legs your ride has, the smoother it is. Too bad centipedes don't grow this big.

riding silkworm - aqua.name: Riding Silkworm - Aqua
riding silkworm - aqua.description: The more legs your ride has, the smoother it is. Too bad centipedes don't grow this big.

crispr technology.name: CRISPR Technology
crispr technology.description: This is not a tasty potato chip. With this cutting-edge genetic technology, you can splice Battle Pets of different elements together! One CRISPR is used up for each cross-element splice you perform.

genetic resequencer.name: Genetic Resequencer
genetic resequencer.description: Wrench a Battle Pet Cage with a pet inside, and you can use this to resequence their DNA. It will rotate the order of their 3 powers, so that their 1st gene-spliced ability becomes their natural ability, and thus their appearance.

pet trainer medal.name: Pet Trainer Medal
pet trainer medal.description: Congratulations! You have been awarded a medal for defeating a Pet Trainer!

whale block.name: Whale Block
whale block.description: Whale whale whale, you'll really have to wail on this block to smash it. But you'll have a whale of a time doing it! And what a tail to tell it will be. I'm way ill from all of these puns, I'm gonna start blubbering. ORCA.

pet trainer whistle.name: Pet Trainer Whistle
pet trainer whistle.description: You know how to battle a Pet Trainer, right? You just put your lips together, and blow this whistle. You might want to have a fully stocked Battle Leash first though, because Pet Trainers won't stay around waiting to fight you forever!

thinking cap.name: Thinking Cap
thinking cap.description: They say two heads are better than one. We can't arrange that, but we can get you two of what's inside your head!

phlogiston.name: Phlogiston
phlogiston.description: This fantastic substance contains the very essence of living flame.

lock-bot.name: Lock-Bot
lock-bot.description: This robot works for Locke. He'll trade you fabulous items for locks! He'll only stick around in your world for 24 hours before he's needed elsewhere, though.

lock-bot remote.name: Lock-Bot Remote
lock-bot remote.description: This handy remote will call Lock-Bot to your world at the location you specify. It only works once, so choose wisely! Lock-Bot will leave after 24 hours.

toy lock-bot.name: Toy Lock-Bot
toy lock-bot.description: It's just like Lock-Bot, only tiny! And he doesn't trade locks, he SHOOTS them.

burnt leather.name: Burnt Leather
burnt leather.description: If this was a piece of a pig, you'd call a pork rind. But it's a cow rind. Strong material for crafting!

buckle design.name: Buckle Design
buckle design.description: This paper details a method for forging a buckle out of Deep Iron. If you forge 100 Deep Iron Ingots with this design in hand, you'll make an Iron Buckle instead of a Pick Blade.

iron buckle.name: Iron Buckle
iron buckle.description: This buckle would be good for holding straps together, if you need for such things!

weather machine - heatwave.name: Weather Machine - Heatwave
weather machine - heatwave.description: This amazing new weather machine emits a vortex of howling flame, but if you wrench it, you'll find adjustable settings to control the color of the flames! You can only have one of these per world.

riding phoenix.name: Riding Phoenix
riding phoenix.description: Whoa, you're really sitting on the ride now. There are only 500 of these in existence, so don't lose yours!

red flip flops.name: Red Flip Flops
red flip flops.description: Bright rubber to protect your feet from pointy shells on the beach!

green flip flops.name: Green Flip Flops
green flip flops.description: Bright rubber to protect your feet from pointy shells on the beach!

blue flip flops.name: Blue Flip Flops
blue flip flops.description: Bright rubber to protect your feet from pointy shells on the beach!

paper airplane.name: Paper Airplane
paper airplane.description: Toss it and see where it goes! It'll smash if it hits any blocks, so aim carefully. Tap the direction you want to throw it. The further from yourself you tap, the harder you throw.

b.o.o. shirt.name: B.O.O. Shirt
b.o.o. shirt.description: The official uniform of the B.O.O. - Battlers of the Otherworldly. Join today!

b.o.o. pants.name: B.O.O. Pants
b.o.o. pants.description: The official uniform of the B.O.O. - Battlers of the Otherworldly. Join today!

spectral goggles.name: Spectral Goggles
spectral goggles.description: The spectrally polarized lenses of these goggles allow you to actually see paranormal activity. Be warned: it is very spooky! But it's there whether you can see it or not... wouldn't you rather know?

b.o.o. helmet.name: B.O.O. Helmet
b.o.o. helmet.description: The trouble with poltergeists is that they're always pushing things off of shelves (side note: cats pose same problem). That's where the helmet comes in. Protect yourself from falling books and antiques!

neutron pack.name: Neutron Pack
neutron pack.description: This backpack contains a portable nuclear reactor. I know that sounds a bit unsafe, but... well, it is. It's a terrible idea. It has blinky lights, though. You'll need to wear a Neutron Pack to power a Neutron Gun.

neutron gun.name: Neutron Gun
neutron gun.description: This energy blaster looks impressive, but actually has no impact on our world. Rather, it creates a stream of neutrons that attracts spirits. Ghosts can't escape the beam. Which reminds me: Don't ever cross your beam with somebody else's! That would be bad.

rubber boots.name: Rubber Boots
rubber boots.description: These are tight-fitting boots made of a natural rubber that protects from slime while still allowing your feet to breathe.

ghost jar.name: Ghost Jar
ghost jar.description: Place this jar down and it will suck in a ghost that's above it. You will probably need some friends with Neutron Guns to keep the ghost contained or it will escape! A jar takes 2 seconds to activate, and then only collects spirits for 5 seconds, so time it carefully.

ghost-in-a-jar.name: Ghost-In-A-Jar
ghost-in-a-jar.description: Spooky! This jar contains a ghost! You can throw it to break the jar and unleash the ghost, or instead Drop it gently in front of a Spirit Storage Unit where you can keep the ghost for good.

spirit storage unit.name: Spirit Storage Unit
spirit storage unit.description: This incredible machine was invented a hundred years ago, and still runs on Steam power! Drop Ghosts-In-A-Jar in front of it, then provide it with Steam power to store the ghosts. Warning: If you overload the device, it may explode!

destroyed spirit storage unit.name: Destroyed Spirit Storage Unit
destroyed spirit storage unit.description: An SSU that exploded. No good for anything now.

ectoplasm sample.name: Ectoplasm Sample
ectoplasm sample.description: This is an important scientific discovery that could change our understanding of life itself! But you know what'd be fun? Throwing it at somebody.

crystallized ghost.name: Crystallized Ghost
