adventure's end.name: Adventure's End
adventure's end.description: Start your adventure at The Adventure Begins, and end it here! This resets all adventure items and announces to the world how well you did on the adventure.

tomb robber.name: Tomb Robber
tomb robber.description: Watch out! These guys will steal Adventure Items from you! If you own the Tomb Robber, smack him with a wrench to change his mind about what to steal.

adventure tomb gate.name: Adventure Tomb Gate
adventure tomb gate.description: These gates can be punched by the world owner to open or close them. But Tomb Robbers can change their status for a player who pays them - open ones will shut, shut ones will open.

diamond horn.name: Diamond Horn
diamond horn.description: This amazing horn transforms each time you unequip it. Try all 3 flavors! It also boosts your build range.

diamond horns.name: Diamond Horns
diamond horns.description: This amazing horn transforms each time you unequip it. Try all 3 flavors! It also boosts your build range.

diamond devil horns.name: Diamond Devil Horns
diamond devil horns.description: This amazing horn transforms each time you unequip it. Try all 3 flavors! It also boosts your build range.

super pineapple.name: Super Pineapple
super pineapple.description: WOW, it's a super pineapple! This is even better than a normal pineapple, you should just keep eating these nonstop!

super exploding pineapple.name: Super Exploding Pineapple
super exploding pineapple.description: Wait... this isn't any normal super pineapple! It looks like it's about to blow! STAND BACK!!!

can of beans.name: Can Of Beans
can of beans.description: This can contains a magical fruit.

mini-mod.name: Mini-Mod
mini-mod.description: When activated (punch to activate), this guy won't allow anyone to drop items in the world. Keep your place clean!

pet frog.name: Pet Frog
pet frog.description: Ribbit Ribbit. This frog hops along with you everywhere.

cherry.name: Cherry
cherry.description: Leaves your tongue a little red, and well the rest of your body for that matter!

pineapple turnover.name: Pineapple Turnover
pineapple turnover.description: Eating these makes you sticky, so you can get more YUM from your food! Food Buff: Get triple XP for using consumables.

pineapple finger ring.name: Pineapple Finger Ring
pineapple finger ring.description: This tasty pineapple ring is now stuck to your fingers. For some reason, a creepy pineapple spider keeps following you around!

pineapple glasses.name: Pineapple Glasses
pineapple glasses.description: Pineapples in your eyes! Who wouldn't want that? Gives sticky vision which is suspiciously similar to normal vision but more sticky.

jungle blast.name: Jungle Blast
jungle blast.description: Use this astounding device to create an entirely new jungle world. One free ziggurat included.

weather machine - jungle.name: Weather Machine - Jungle
weather machine - jungle.description: What's lurking in the depths of the jungle? This sensitive technology will not function while damaged.

adventurer's whip.name: Adventurer's Whip
adventurer's whip.description: Only a true adventurer can swing this with such style.

adventurer's sling bag.name: Adventurer's Sling Bag
adventurer's sling bag.description: Look stylish while on all your greatest adventures. Who knows what you can hold in this. Doesn't actually give any more backpack space.

jungle fern.name: Jungle Fern
jungle fern.description: Just an ordinary fern commonly found in the jungle.

statue block.name: Statue Block
statue block.description: It's a piece of a statue.

statue eye.name: Statue Eye
statue eye.description: It's a piece of a statue. Seems to be an eye.

statue headdress.name: Statue Headdress
statue headdress.description: It's a piece of a statue. Seems to be some form of crown...

statue nose.name: Statue Nose
statue nose.description: It's a piece of a statue. Seems to be a nose.

statue mouth.name: Statue Mouth
statue mouth.description: It's a piece of a statue. Seems to be a mouth.

rubble.name: Rubble
rubble.description: There isn't much left of these bricks to be used anyway.

jungle pillar.name: Jungle Pillar
jungle pillar.description: Looks like an ancient piece of some ruins. However, it is just a pillar, nothing special.

overgrown vines.name: Overgrown Vines
overgrown vines.description: These vines are everywhere. Great for hiding in your favorite game of hide and seek.

hanging snake.name: Hanging Snake
hanging snake.description: This deadly snake can be found lazing about in the growtopian jungles and is capable of instantly killing a Growtopian.

royal lock.name: Royal Lock
royal lock.description: This fabulous world lock has some special new options. Wrench it and become the king of your world! It also shows you where players are in your world with Peasant Radar!

silk bolt - floral.name: Silk Bolt - Floral
silk bolt - floral.description: Sew silk items by using this in a sewing machine. It takes 3 bolts of silk to craft an item.

floral lei.name: Floral Lei
floral lei.description: This particular one is lab-created, which you'd think is less classy, but they're much prettier.

zinc.name: Zinc
zinc.description: Protection from the sun. Well at least your nose will be safe.

frangipani.name: Frangipani
frangipani.description: Put a flower in your hair. All the girls are doing it this summer! Just don't let Jim catch you stealing flowers from his garden... He's Crazy!

short surfer hair.name: Short Surfer Hair
short surfer hair.description: You've got that windblown chlorinated surfer look. It either makes you look cool or a filthy beach bum. It's a fine line.

long surfer hair.name: Long Surfer Hair
long surfer hair.description: You've got that windblown chlorinated surfer look. It either makes you look cool or a filthy beach bum. It's a fine line.

phoenix crown.name: Phoenix Crown
phoenix crown.description: Be honoured to wear this beautiful crown. Light the way for all to see. No more than 500 of these exist in all of Growtopia.

balloon-o-matic.name: Balloon-O-Matic
balloon-o-matic.description: Convert all your random junk into balloons for the war. Beware, may overheat and explode. WARNING! Is public for anyone on your team to use.

destroyed balloon-o-matic.name: Destroyed Balloon-O-Matic
destroyed balloon-o-matic.description: Convert all your random junk into balloons for the war. Beware, may overheat and explode. WARNING! Is public for anyone on your team to use.

team entrance - punch.name: Team Entrance - Punch
team entrance - punch.description: The only people getting through this door are the ones who are on team Punch. Outside of Balloon Warz, this functions as a normal entrance.

team entrance - grow.name: Team Entrance - Grow
team entrance - grow.description: The only people getting through this door are the ones who are on team Grow. Outside of Balloon Warz, this functions as a normal entrance.

team entrance - build.name: Team Entrance - Build
team entrance - build.description: The only people getting through this door are the ones who are on team Build. Outside of Balloon Warz, this functions as a normal entrance.

balloon launcher.name: Balloon Launcher
balloon launcher.description: With this launcher you can throw balloons farther. Not much good for anything else, though.

balloon repellent.name: Balloon Repellent
balloon repellent.description: Drinking this will keep those pesky balloons away for a while! The bubble of protection is extremely fragile. One hit and your protection will be gone!

small war balloon.name: Small War Balloon
small war balloon.description: Toss these all over. Scores 1 team point per hit. Only counts if they aren't already colored. 0 points for hitting your own team; that's not cool.

medium war balloon.name: Medium War Balloon
medium war balloon.description: Toss these all over. Scores 2 team point per hit. Only counts if they aren't already colored. 0 points for hitting your own team; that's not cool.

large war balloon.name: Large War Balloon
large war balloon.description: Toss these all over. Scores 5 team point per hit. Only counts if they aren't already colored. 0 points for hitting your own team; that's not cool.

bucket of small war balloons.name: Bucket of Small War Balloons
bucket of small war balloons.description: This contains 100 Small War Balloons. Double-tap this in your inventory to convert it back to 100 Small War Balloons.

bucket of medium war balloons.name: Bucket of Medium War Balloons
bucket of medium war balloons.description: This contains 100 Medium War Balloons. Double-tap this in your inventory to convert it back to 100 Medium War Balloons.

bucket of large war balloons.name: Bucket of Large War Balloons
bucket of large war balloons.description: This contains 100 Large War Balloons. Double-tap this in your inventory to convert it back to 100 Large War Balloons.

balloon warz leaderboard.name: Balloon Warz Leaderboard
balloon warz leaderboard.description: Wrench this board to see how the Balloon Warz are going! Is your team ahead?

balloon filling station.name: Balloon Filling Station
balloon filling station.description: The ideal station for creating war balloons! Shame every Growtopian is out filling balloons, though - the water's running low and it'll take a while to fill yours!

team shorts - punch.name: Team Shorts - Punch
team shorts - punch.description: Red with victory. Wear your team colors proudly.

team shorts - grow.name: Team Shorts - Grow
team shorts - grow.description: Green with glory. Wear your team colors proudly.

team shorts - build.name: Team Shorts - Build
team shorts - build.description: Blue with bravery. Wear your team colors proudly.

team shirt - punch.name: Team Shirt - Punch
team shirt - punch.description: Respledent with redness. Wear your team colors proudly.

team shirt - grow.name: Team Shirt - Grow
team shirt - grow.description: Glory with greenness. Wear your team colors proudly.

team shirt - build.name: Team Shirt - Build
team shirt - build.description: Beautiful with blueness. Wear your team colors proudly.

team pennant - punch.name: Team Pennant - Punch
team pennant - punch.description: It's just flappin' in the breeze.

team pennant - grow.name: Team Pennant - Grow
team pennant - grow.description: It's just flappin' in the breeze.

team pennant - build.name: Team Pennant - Build
team pennant - build.description: It's just flappin' in the breeze.

bouncy balloon.name: Bouncy Balloon
bouncy balloon.description: Formulated with extra-bouncy plastic. Hold Jump as you land for maximum bounce!

super squirt gun jetpack.name: Super Squirt Gun Jetpack
super squirt gun jetpack.description: Use the power of pressurization to leap tall buildings in a single bound, then drift gently to Earth.

towel rack checkpoint.name: Towel Rack Checkpoint
towel rack checkpoint.description: If you die, you'll respawn at the last Checkpoint you touched! Also keeps you dry at a beach... or after eating a water balloon.

balloon jammer.name: Balloon Jammer
balloon jammer.description: Prevents war balloons from being thrown in your world when activated (punch to activate). Has a 5 second countdown when activating/deactivating.

team bunting - punch.name: Team Bunting - Punch
team bunting - punch.description: Deck the halls with team spirit. Made of biodegradable, water proof paper. I've no idea how that works but it's meant to be good for the environment.

team bunting - grow.name: Team Bunting - Grow
team bunting - grow.description: Deck the halls with team spirit. Made of biodegradable, water proof paper. I've no idea how that works but it's meant to be good for the environment.

team bunting - build.name: Team Bunting - Build
team bunting - build.description: Deck the halls with team spirit. Made of biodegradable, water proof paper. I've no idea how that works but it's meant to be good for the environment.

weather machine - balloon warz.name: Weather Machine - Balloon Warz
weather machine - balloon warz.description: This machine will send your entire world up into the clouds where the balloons fly. This sensitive technology will not function while damaged.

balloon fragment.name: Balloon Fragment
balloon fragment.description: This is a broken piece of a war balloon. If you feed enough of these into a Balloon-O-Matic, you're bound to get something good...

balloon warz gold trophy - punch.name: Balloon Warz Gold Trophy - Punch
balloon warz gold trophy - punch.description: Awarded for awesome balloon battling! Stick this in the trophy cabinet and show it off to all your friends!

balloon warz silver trophy - punch.name: Balloon Warz Silver Trophy - Punch
balloon warz silver trophy - punch.description: Second place ain't bad! Stick this in the trophy cabinet and show it off to all your friends!

balloon warz bronze trophy - punch.name: Balloon Warz Bronze Trophy - Punch
balloon warz bronze trophy - punch.description: There's no such thing as a loser in Balloon Warz, but... you lost. Ah, well - stick this in the trophy cabinet and show it off anyway!

balloon warz gold trophy - grow.name: Balloon Warz Gold Trophy - Grow
balloon warz gold trophy - grow.description: Awarded for awesome balloon battling! Stick this in the trophy cabinet and show it off to all your friends!

balloon warz silver trophy - grow.name: Balloon Warz Silver Trophy - Grow
balloon warz silver trophy - grow.description: Second place ain't bad! Stick this in the trophy cabinet and show it off to all your friends!

balloon warz bronze trophy - grow.name: Balloon Warz Bronze Trophy - Grow
balloon warz bronze trophy - grow.description: There's no such thing as a loser in Balloon Warz, but... you lost. Ah, well - stick this in the trophy cabinet and show it off anyway!

balloon warz gold trophy - build.name: Balloon Warz Gold Trophy - Build
balloon warz gold trophy - build.description: Awarded for awesome balloon battling! Stick this in the trophy cabinet and show it off to all your friends!

balloon warz silver trophy - build.name: Balloon Warz Silver Trophy - Build
balloon warz silver trophy - build.description: Second place ain't bad! Stick this in the trophy cabinet and show it off to all your friends!

balloon warz bronze trophy - build.name: Balloon Warz Bronze Trophy - Build
balloon warz bronze trophy - build.description: There's no such thing as a loser in Balloon Warz, but... you lost. Ah, well - stick this in the trophy cabinet and show it off anyway!

balloon warz mvp trophy - punch.name: Balloon Warz MVP Trophy - Punch
balloon warz mvp trophy - punch.description: You were MVP in the great Balloon Warz. Stick this in the trophy cabinet and show it off to all your friends!

balloon warz mvp trophy - grow.name: Balloon Warz MVP Trophy - Grow
balloon warz mvp trophy - grow.description: You were MVP in the great Balloon Warz. Stick this in the trophy cabinet and show it off to all your friends!

balloon warz mvp trophy - build.name: Balloon Warz MVP Trophy - Build
balloon warz mvp trophy - build.description: You were MVP in the great Balloon Warz. Stick this in the trophy cabinet and show it off to all your friends!

balloon throwing stand.name: Balloon Throwing Stand
balloon throwing stand.description: It's a classic photo op! Stand behind it and pretend you're getting splatted by a balloon. Fun for the whole family!

target.name: Target
target.description: Punch it to win. Fun for the whole family!

team headband - punch.name: Team Headband - Punch
team headband - punch.description: When there's a war on, sweat, water, and balloon fragments fly everywhere. This'll keep them all out of your eyes for more effective fighting!

team headband - grow.name: Team Headband - Grow
team headband - grow.description: When there's a war on, sweat, water, and balloon fragments fly everywhere. This'll keep them all out of your eyes for more effective fighting!

team headband - build.name: Team Headband - Build
team headband - build.description: When there's a war on, sweat, water, and balloon fragments fly everywhere. This'll keep them all out of your eyes for more effective fighting!

red facepaint.name: Red Facepaint
red facepaint.description: Looks like you've been punched in the face or have you? Nope, it's just face paint and a whopping dose of team spirit.

green facepaint.name: Green Facepaint
green facepaint.description: Blend in with the trees for a surprise attack like a true Grow supporter.

blue facepaint.name: Blue Facepaint
blue facepaint.description: Even Sir William Wallace would be envious of your team spirit. FREEEEDDDOOOOMMMMM! Wait! This is just a balloon war

red floaty balloon.name: Red Floaty Balloon
red floaty balloon.description: Hold on tight and hopefully you won't float up into the sky. There's a song with 99 red balloons, but sadly, this is only 1.

green floaty balloon.name: Green Floaty Balloon
green floaty balloon.description: Hold on tight and hopefully you won't float up into the sky. Make everyone green with envy when they see your beautiful balloon.

blue floaty balloon.name: Blue Floaty Balloon
blue floaty balloon.description: Hold on tight and hopefully you won't float up into the sky. The balloon might be blue, but you'll never be.

dark green wallpaper.name: Dark Green Wallpaper
dark green wallpaper.description: Kinda creepy, like you're trapped deep beneath the waves...

dark blue wallpaper.name: Dark Blue Wallpaper
dark blue wallpaper.description: Kinda creepy, like you're trapped deep beneath the waves...

super squirt gun jetpack pants.name: Super Squirt Gun Jetpack Pants
super squirt gun jetpack pants.description: Strap these to your hips and get ready for the ride of your life. Use the power of pressurization to leap tall buildings in a single bound, then drift gently to Earth.

solar chariot.name: Solar Chariot
solar chariot.description: Run at the speed of, well... horses. On FIRE!

silk corset.name: Silk Corset
silk corset.description: Missing Data. Please contact when you find description for this item.

gothic corset.name: Gothic Corset
gothic corset.description: Feeling fat? You could exercise... or you just cram your gut into one of these! Oh sure, you may end up with spinal deformities, but beauty demands pain!

unicorn hair.name: Unicorn Hair
unicorn hair.description: Like unicorns? Well, so does the rest of the internet, and now you can look like one, too!

emerald pickaxe.name: Emerald Pickaxe
emerald pickaxe.description: This tool is worth more than the stuff you mine with it!

sand shark.name: Sand Shark
sand shark.description: A shark with a vicious bite. Sand Sharks can live up to seven years old. See this shark in action in Hungry Shark World

megalodon.name: Megalodon
megalodon.description: Missing Data. Please contact when you find description for this item.

beanbag.name: Beanbag
beanbag.description: Flop down into a world of lazy wonder with this majestic sack o' beans!

black espadrille.name: Black Espadrille
black espadrille.description: Perfect for kicking back - or kicking butt! - in the tropical sun.

checkered espadrille.name: Checkered Espadrille
checkered espadrille.description: Perfect for kicking back - or kicking butt - in the tropical sun.

sports bra.name: Sports Bra
sports bra.description: Get running and show off your curves while you're at it!

pink aura.name: Pink Aura
pink aura.description: Missing Data. Please contact when you find description for this item.

blue aura.name: Blue Aura
blue aura.description: You are burning with brilliant energy! Also double-jump power.

wedding headdress.name: Wedding Headdress
wedding headdress.description: Everyone should look like a queen in their own wedding.

sarong.name: Sarong
sarong.description: Casual, comfortable, and affordable! What more could you want?

dress with smock.name: Dress with Smock
dress with smock.description: This light cotton dress is adorned with adorable stripes. Aww. How cute.

waistcoat and jacket.name: Waistcoat and Jacket
waistcoat and jacket.description: The perfect garment for housing a pocketwatch and monocle. Will also keep you warm during those long winter days.

orange.name: Orange
orange.description: A delicious sphere, complete with sweet, tingling citrus flavor.

orange juice.name: Orange Juice
orange juice.description: Oranges are great. Grind the hell out of them and they're still delicious! Only, like, wetter.

inside-out devil wings.name: Inside-Out Devil Wings
inside-out devil wings.description: You dont jump higher than with normal devil wings, but man, you DO look pretty cool, like an inside-out devil. Wait... doesn't that make you an angel?!

speed medallion.name: Speed Medallion
speed medallion.description: This amulet bestows you with speed energy, making you run so fast that lightning trails behind you! Grants Super Speed if you don't have it already.

skateboard.name: Skateboard
skateboard.description: Skate or die! Alternatively you can live by doing other things, like eating and breathing. Actually, do those even if you ARE skating.

antigravity generator.name: Antigravity Generator
antigravity generator.description: Disables gravity in your world when activated (punch to activate)! Well, it reduces gravity, and lets everybody jump as much as they want! This sensitive technology can't be used while damaged.

builder's lock.name: Builder's Lock
builder's lock.description: Locks 200 tiles around itself. Only allows either building or breaking of blocks inside - wrench it to decide which!

burning hands.name: Burning Hands
burning hands.description: Spew jets of flame from your hands!

riding turtle.name: Riding Turtle
riding turtle.description: It's not the fastest transportation around, but it's the bumpiest!

weather machine - background.name: Weather Machine - Background
weather machine - background.description: Missing Data. Please contact when you find description for this item.

playful fire sprite.name: Playful Fire Sprite
playful fire sprite.description: Looks like a little blob of fire following you! Makes sense.

playful wind sprite.name: Playful Wind Sprite
playful wind sprite.description: Looks like a little blob of wind following you! Makes sense.

playful wood sprite.name: Playful Wood Sprite
playful wood sprite.description: Looks like a little blob of wood following you! Makes sense.

playful water sprite.name: Playful Water Sprite
playful water sprite.description: Looks like a little blob of water following you! Makes sense.

plate greaves.name: Plate Greaves
plate greaves.description: Tired of being kicked in the shins? Aren't we all?

flaming horsie.name: Flaming Horsie
flaming horsie.description: There was a saddle here, but it burned up. Eh, you can probably ride bareback.

flaming horse chunk.name: Flaming Horse Chunk
flaming horse chunk.description: This is fairly morbid. Also hot.

newspaper.name: Newspaper
newspaper.description: Great for checking the daily gazette. Equip to read.

riding chicken.name: Riding Chicken
riding chicken.description: A feathered friend to carry you to and fro! Best part? He'll never peck you to death with hordes of his angry pals!

prismatic aura.name: Prismatic Aura
prismatic aura.description: A fantastic aura of prismatic energy pulses around you, turning heads and bending the laws of gravity to your will.The power to double jump - and look awesome - will be yours!

chicken plow.name: Chicken Plow
chicken plow.description: Ancient magic has unlocked the secrets of advance chicken farming! Now, for the first time, your chicken will PLANT seeds instead of eating them! (When equipped, will plant whatever seed you have selected as you move!)

fire essence.name: Fire Essence
fire essence.description: The blazing heart of blockdom. Ow! Ow! Spicy.

water essence.name: Water Essence
water essence.description: The slippery, liquid soul of blocks. Not only looks nice - it's also refreshing!

earth essence.name: Earth Essence
earth essence.description: Titanic forces of dirt and stone have ground together to forge this pure piece of earth. Also makes for a nice paperweight.

wind essence.name: Wind Essence
wind essence.description: Fluffy clouds and raging storms howl within this airy essence. Weighs a ton, surprisingly enough. Probably something to do with physics.

fissure.name: Fissure
fissure.description: Punch it to open or shut it. Anyone unlucky enough to be caught inside when it closes becomes one with the soil. Really handy for gravediggers, too!

waterfall.name: Waterfall
waterfall.description: Falling water is one of the strangest natural phenomena in Growtopia. You can't jump up through it, since you're not a salmon. You can, however, drop down, since you're like everything else.

hidden door.name: Hidden Door
hidden door.description: Looks like an Art Deco Block, but with extra friendship - you can use this to allow access to others! Just, y'know, keep it secret. Hidden doors are only cool if they're secret.

anemone.name: Anemone
anemone.description: Stinging denizen of the deep! It won't kill you, but it'll hurt somethin' FIERCE. Unless you're a clown fish, I guess, but they have other things to worry about.

aurora.name: Aurora
aurora.description: Dancing celestial light, compressed into handy block form! Fun Fact: Auroras are actually caused by collisions between electrically charged particles from the sun as they enter a planet's atmosphere! ...wait, that wasn't very fun was it?

obsidian.name: Obsidian
obsidian.description: Missing Data. Please contact when you find description for this item.

lava lamp.name: Lava Lamp
lava lamp.description: Missing Data. Please contact when you find description for this item.

fire asteroid.name: Fire Asteroid
fire asteroid.description: Tearing through the atmosphere, this chunk of rock has ignited with whirls of flame! Now, thanks to magnets or something, it will float and burn forever!

water asteroid.name: Water Asteroid
water asteroid.description: Laced with unobtainium, this floating rock comes complete with lovely cinematic waterfalls! The perfect touch to elevate a zen garden, or at least make your neighbors really jealous

earth asteroid.name: Earth Asteroid
earth asteroid.description: You might think most asteroids are made of earth already, but this one has EXTRA earth for the dirtiest, most magnificently rocky experience to be found in a floating piece of the heavens.

wind asteroid.name: Wind Asteroid
wind asteroid.description: The howling winds that came down with this asteroid have became a permanent part of it! Now it will float forever, whispering the secrets of space to you as it does. (NOTE: Secrets of space may not actually be secret. Or audible.)

inferno gate.name: Inferno Gate
inferno gate.description: These blazing magical doors connect all the worlds in Growtopia. Place one and then use your Wrench on it to set the destination. Ow, hot!

tidal gate.name: Tidal Gate
tidal gate.description: These rippling magical doors connect all the worlds in Growtopia. Place one and then use your Wrench on it to set the destination. Ah, refreshing!

typhoon gate.name: Typhoon Gate
typhoon gate.description: These windy magical doors connect all the worlds in Growtopia.

verdant gate.name: Verdant Gate
verdant gate.description: These lush magical doors connect all the worlds in Growtopia. Place one and then use your Wrench on it to set the destination. Wow, tropical!

ancient hinge.name: Ancient Hinge
ancient hinge.description: Creaking with legendary power, this must be the piece of something far greater. And doorlike. Maybe.

ancient pin.name: Ancient Pin
ancient pin.description: Eons have not sulled the point of this pointy treasure. Careful! It's supernaturally pokey!

ancient bracket.name: Ancient Bracket
ancient bracket.description: Superb craftmanship has kept this pristine across the ages. Once part of some grand design, it can be again... if you can figure out what it will make!

ancient lens.name: Ancient Lens
ancient lens.description: Forged with long-lost sorceries, this glass remains unscratched after untold centuries! What could it reflect? Peer through it and into a time long past...

crystallized reality.name: Crystallized Reality
crystallized reality.description: Missing Data. Please contact when you find description for this item.

crystallized wealth.name: Crystallized Wealth
crystallized wealth.description: A pure piece of prosperity! The solidified richness surrounding it could certainly be used for something spectacular... or set on a shelf to look pretty.

crystallized brilliance.name: Crystallized Brilliance
crystallized brilliance.description: Missing Data. Please contact when you find description for this item.

crystallized nature.name: Crystallized Nature
crystallized nature.description: A fragment of Gaia's beating heart! The unstoppable life force surrounding it could certainly be used for something spectacular... or set on a shelf to look pretty!

ancestral totem of wisdom.name: Ancestral Totem of Wisdom
ancestral totem of wisdom.description: Incredible forces of willpower and mental strength have been combined with the building blocks of creation to forge this totem. Equip it and ancient knowledge will be yours...

ancestral tesseract of dimensions.name: Ancestral Tesseract of Dimensions
ancestral tesseract of dimensions.description: Astonishing whirls of space and time have been combined with the building blocks of creation to forge this tesseract. Equip it and watch your hoard grow..

ancestral seed of life.name: Ancestral Seed of Life
ancestral seed of life.description: Fantastic powers of verdant might have been combined with the building blocks of creation to forge this seed. Equip it and the bloom of life will bend to your will..

ancestral lens of riches.name: Ancestral Lens of Riches
ancestral lens of riches.description: Unrelenting luck and luxury have been combined with the building blocks of ceration to forge this lens. Equip it and unstoppable fortune will be yours... but do be careful. Power tends to be corrupt, after all.
